(2349, 'en_US', 'O\'kaki Robata Grill & Oyster', 'Grab the Chablis and enjoy the Fresh oysters with various selection!', 'Gillardeau Oysters, Truffle Mushroom Spaghetti, Truffle Roasted Eggplant, Iberico Spaghetti', '', 'O\'kaki Robata Grill & Oyster is located in Tin Hau which have a lots of stunning restauants. It has different varieties of fresh oysters, seafood, and wines for your selection. It also provides a wide range of both robata grill and hot plates. Grill Oyster is perfect for winter dining.', '5 -min walk from MTR Tin Hua station Exit B', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2350, 'en_US', 'Wheatfield Kitchen', 'Taste the Shanghai style Russian Cuisine in Wheatfield Kitchen in Causeway Bay!', 'Borscht, Rossiya Blini with Caviar, Grilled Salmon', '', 'Wheatfield Kitchen located in Causeway Bay which is a Shanghai style Russian Restaurant. Their signature dish – Borscht, has been cooked more than 36 hours. You can taste the richness and the ingredient real flavor in the soup. Chef Yip is the experienced chef who cooked Russian food for more than 40 years. His son Chef Andrew follow his traditional receipts and you can taste it in Wheatfield Kitchen! 
