(2396, 'en_US', 'Kinnokura (Quarry Bay)', 'Traditional Izakaya, Skewed BBQ and Ramen', 'Golden Ramen, Foie Gras', '', 'Customers enjoying our foods is our highest pleasure. This is our faith of doing our business. Having gone to Japan to learn is a very important experience of us. Other than boosting up our cooking skills, we also learnt their diligent way of choosing cooking ingredients. Kinnokura encourages its own staff to try different kind of restaurant and cuisine in order to imitate their service attitude. We have been trying to learn the good from restaurant\'s cooking skill and present the best to our customers. When most people choose to consistently do something  that  is considered right, we call that persistence. When most of the world consider something is crazy to do but still do it, we call it obsession. Under current manufacturing liked food and beverage culture, Kinnokura wish to preserve its own obsession... At this small corner, are we nuts at Kinnokura? Yes indeed.', '3 -min walk from MTR Quarry Bay Station Exit B', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2397, 'en_US', 'Kinnokura (Tai Hang)', 'Traditional Izakaya, Skewed bbq and ramen', 'Golden Ramen, Foie Gras', '', 'Customers enjoying our foods is our highest pleasure. This is our faith of doing our business. Having gone to Japan to learn is a very important experience of us. Other than boosting up our cooking skills, we also learnt their diligent way of choosing cooking ingredients. Kinnokura encourages its own staff to try different kind of restaurant and cuisine in order to imitate their service attitude. We have been trying to learn the good from restaurant\'s cooking skill and present the best to our customers. When most people choose to consistently do something  that  is considered right, we call that persistence. When most of the world consider something is crazy to do but still do it, we call it obsession. Under current manufacturing liked food and beverage culture, Kinnokura wish to preserve its own obsession... At this small corner, are we nuts at Kinnokura? Yes indeed.', '6 -min walk from MTR Tin Hua station Exit B', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2276, 'en_US', 'Otto Restaurant & Bar', 'Italian classic dishes', 'Crab Meat and Lobster Risotto with Black Truffle, Beef Carpaccio', '', 'Otto Restaurant & Bar just one step distance from the crowded Causeway Bay, relax and fine Italian dining ambience. Otto Restaurant serving the finest Italian seafood & grilled items with a excellent selection of new & old world wines. Private parties, weddings, corporate functions or other special events are welcome, Otto Restaurant will help to create the most memorable and special day for you and your special guests.', '3-min walk from MTR Causeway Bay station Exit D1', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2587, 'en_US', 'Bistro Du Vin', 'Authentic French cuisine in Sai Wan, you can experience the French home style food', 'Bouillabaisse, Braised Beef Cheeks, Crispy Suckling Pig Confit, Grand Marnier Souffle', '', 'From rustic, home-style provincial French cuisine to unpretentious bistro décor, table settings and ‘Edith Piaf’ background music, no effort was spared in Bistro du Vin to create the ambience reminiscent of an authentic Parisian bistro.
The food served is unpretentious, paying homage to the rustic, earthy dishes cooked in classic French-style. Signature dishes range from homemade pork and duck pates and farmhouse-style duck rillettes to classic stews like bouillabaisse and braised beef cheek, suckling pig confit, plate-grilled baby squid and Grand Marnier soufflé with vanilla ice cream.
The wine selection focuses on wines made by terroir-driven growers, because the minerality and freshness found in such wines compliment the dishes on the menu well. The owner’s passion for wines from the Burgundy region is translated onto the wine list, making Bistro du Vin a great place to try a variety of wines this region has to offer.', '3 -min walk from MTR Kennedy Town station Exit C', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3366, 'en_US', 'Shelter Italian Bar & Restaurant', 'offer visitors a tranquil escape far removed from the hyper pace and urban sprawl typically associated with Causeway Bay', 'Baccalà, Strozzapreti, Vongole e Carciofi, Mojito Semifreddo', '', 'The garden adds another level of social excitement to the dining experience, an element of such scope and scale rarely seen at restaurants located in areas as dense and urbanized as Causeway Bay. The restaurant’s interior decked out in nature-inspired designs and colours, cultivates a serene ambience to offer visitors a tranquil escape far removed from the hyper pace and urban sprawl typically associated with Causeway Bay. (Content Reference Source: Website) (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2259, 'en_US', 'The Herbivores - Hysan Place', 'Vegetarian food that will stun you taste bug', 'Mash & Cheese, Mango Risotto, Herbivores Bomb', '', 'The Herbivores is an adventurous bunch and thrive on crafting and improving recipes, never letting their team be boring. Herbivores is staffed by a young, talented, and dedicated group of energetic employees who truly appreciate the vision of vegetarianism. Coupled with enthusiasm to work with vegetarian food, its\' goal is to introduce creative vegetarian cooking that will make customers gobsmacked!', '2 -min walk from MTR Causeway Bay station Exit F2', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2275, 'en_US', 'The Gazebo Restaurant - Charterhouse', 'Authentic South-East Asian buffet in Causeway Bay', 'Authentic Hainanese Chicken Rice, Singapore Shrimp Noodles, Red Oven Pancakes, Spicy La Salle, Banana Cake, Blueberry Cheese Cake', '', 'The Gazebo Restaurant has lined up a series of festive program to celebrate Christmas!  Santa Claus, Funny Balloon Twister and Christmas Bass Band will be on stage at the Gazebo Restaurant to deliver dazzling moment with a stunning Christmas atmosphere.  Boasting an international ambience, the special highlights of the Christmas delicacies includes “Roasted Turkey Breast Pizza” and “Roasted Tom Turkey”. Desserts are always the centerpiece of buffet while patrons with sweet tooth will be surprised by our tailor-made desserts such as “Christmas Pudding” and “Macaroon Tower. To cheer the party up, besides offering free flow of soft drinks, selected beers and party favors, a complimentary “Baked Lobster Cheese” will also be offered to each dinner guest for enjoyment.  We will definitely bring an impressive and unforgettable night for you and your friends.', '12-min walk from MTR Causeway Bay station Exit A', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2315, 'en_US', 'Ron’s Kitchen', 'Great food companies with great view, must try the signature dish - Crispy Pork Knuckle', 'Beef Ribs, Cripsy Pork Knuckle, Steak Sandwich', '', 'Its signature dish is Crispy Pork Knuckle: using thin pork knuckle from Canada marinated with fried lemongrass, mustard seeds and a dozen of spices for two days, followed with boiling and then baking for 15 minutes and frying. The whole cooking process makes the meat tender and the skin remains crispy. Sweet honey mustard sauce accompanies it to balance the oily taste.', 'Bus Station - Hong Kong Science Park', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2331, 'en_US', 'Taka 18', 'Japanese fused with Western style teppenyaki, enjoy the seasonal seafood here!', 'Roasted Beef Strip, Slow Cooked Salmon', '', 'Taka 18 is located in Jordan which offer Japanese and Western cuisine. You can enjoy the Teppanyaki, Sashimi at Taka 18! You can find some seasonal seafood in Taka 18 too! There are different price range of set menu to fit your needs no matter romance, business bits or friends gathering.
