(2419, 'en_US', 'Prompt - Le Méridien Cyberport', 'Brunch buffet,tea time buffet, dinner buffet company with pool side view', 'Oyster, Salad, Crab Legs', '', 'Expect the unexpected within minutes from the heart of the city. Nestled amongst a backdrop of greenery while overlooking the South China Sea, the hotel is dramatic in décor and chic in design. The airy, relaxed setting of this modern restaurant, including romantic alfresco dining, offers the ideal ambiance for delightful meals created in the bright, open-gallery kitchen, and an extensive wine lists to choose from.', 'Bus Station - Cyberport Road', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2333, 'en_US', 'Ivan The Kozak', 'Eastern European style cuisine, can\'t find elsewhere in Hong Kong', 'Venison Stew, Russia Assorted Salad, Apple Duck', '', 'Ivan the Kozak is a Russian restaurants located in Central Soho area. You can experience the real Russian Winter in their Snow Room with Russian & Ukrainian vodka!! The Owner – Ivan is very friendly and you can enjoy his warm hospitality like home and the home style Russian cuisine in this restaurant. 
