(2351, 'en_US', 'Gaylord Indian Restaurant', 'Indian cuisine with live Jazz music', 'Grilled Jumbo Prawns, Chessy Spinach, Butter Braised Chicken, Roasted Herb Lamb, Chicken Fried Rice with Indian Spice', '', 'Gaylord Indian Restaurant is a secret paradise located in the heart of Tsim Sha Tsui. Recommended by Michelin Guide and recognized for its authentic and traditional Indian dishes since 1972, it continues to capture the hearts and taste buds of diners both local and abroad. Comfortable alcoves, elegant ambience, and nightly live Indian music add to its exotic charm, making it the place to go for a real Indian experience in Hong Kong.', '5 -min walk from MTR East Tsim Shai Tsui station Exit L5', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2018, 'en_US', 'Palm Court - Metropark Hotel Kowloon', 'International lunch and dinner buffet in Mong Kok', 'Lamb Rack, Salmon, Sashimi, Abalone', '', 'Palm Court offers worldwide delicacies that you cannot resist. Besides the lavish international lunch and dinner buffets are featured daily with a spectacular array of Asian and Continental specialties, international delicacies are also available from the comprehensive a la carte menu.
The hotel Executive Chef, Chef Yim Siu Wai, is a member of the \'Chaîne de Rôtisseurs\' and Master Chef of \'Les Amis d\' Escoffier Society\'.', '12-min walk from MTR Mong Kok East Station Exit B', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2019, 'en_US', 'House of Tang - Metropark Hotel Kowloon -', 'Stunning Chinese restaurant that is best for family gathering', 'Stir Fried Scallop, Spicy Tofu with Sea Cucumber, Dim Sum', '', 'House of Tang\' is the \"Quality Restaurant\" recognized by the Hong Kong Tourism Board. The award-winning chefs carefully prepare the delicate Chinese delicacies and dim sums that satisfy the most discerning diners. With the graceful atmosphere, it provides an ideal venue for family, social and business gatherings. Free parking service and wireless boardband Internet service are available.', '12 -min walk from MTR Mong Kok East Station Exit B', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2036, 'en_US', 'forte - L’hotel elan -', 'Enjoy the luxury 10-inch King Prawn in forte!', 'Steak with Foie Gras, Oyster, Sashimi', '', 'Nobody does it better. Discover international cuisine with a casual vibe as business meets pleasure in this relaxed and inviting setting. Our a la carte, set menus and seasonal tasting menus present guests with a wide variety of culinary options through the convenience of our unique eMenu offered on an iPad.
At forte, fresh produce are our specialties bringing an added dimension to your dining pleasure. Innovative cocktails, as well as a choice of sake and new world wines round out the offerings. For those special get-togethers, guests may also choose the convenience and comfort of dining in a semi-private room.', '6-min walk from  MTR Ngau Tau Kok station Exit B6', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2037, 'en_US', 'LIS Café - L’hotel Island South', 'Creative and special fresh seafood buffet', 'Alaska King Crab Leg with Sake Garlic Sauce, French Style Seafood Soup, Steam Grouper with Ginger and Scailion', '', 'Come discover LIS, Island South’s new stylish dining destination. True to neighbourhood traditions where sampans and fishing junks around, LIS features an abundant choice of fresh fish, shrimp, crab and shellfish at our signature Island South Dinner Buffet.
Put your cares to rest in LIS, the-all-day retreat of modern and creative culinary delights. Sample world-class gourmet dining in a relaxed contemporary setting as our team provides a unique blend of attentive yet discreet care for a truly gastronomic experience.', 'Bus Station - Yip Hing Street / Wong Chuk Hang Road', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2040, 'en_US', 'canton pot - Lodgewood by L’hotel MongKok Hong Kong', 'Healthy style hotpot with various selection stock', 'Korean Style Beef Bone Truffe Stock, Lobster Stock, Japanese A5 Sliced Beef, Truffle and Mushroom Combo', '', 'Representing a new definition of pot cuisine.
Canton pot features over 100 carefully selected hot pot ingredients with a variety of luscious soup bases, condiments and sauces. Never miss the signature Miyazaki A5 beef Chuck, Kurobuta pork and deluxe mushroom platter. Finish your meal with our mouth-watering desserts, organic and fragrant teas for a complete experience of contemporary hot pot dining. Our menu also includes hot pot set for one and pot cuisines in healthy cooking method with your choices of steamed, oven baked and light selections. To experience the city that never sleeps, savour our midnight munchies to enjoy Hong Kong’s vibrant dining culture. Canton pot comprises an expansive main dining area plus seven private rooms. Discover the culinary joys of a green, healthy pot cuisine in a casual contemporary ambience.', '7-min walk from  MTR Mong Kok Station Exit A2', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2386, 'en_US', 'Katte Shabushabu', 'Individual hot pot, don\'t need to fight for what kind of soup base you want!', 'Japanese Style Fried Chicken, Sake Clams, Minced Chicken Stick', '', 'KATTE is located in Causeway Bay which is a Japanese Shabu-shabu restaurant. KATTE, means “Kitchen” and “up to you” in Japanese. Guests can enjoy their own hotpot with special prepared ingredient. You can found A5 Saga Japanese Waygu, Miyazaki chicken and seafood imported from Japan! 
