(2497, 'en_US', 'Koh Thai Restaurant - Wan Chai', 'The traditional Thai cuisine in Central, you can sit at the outdoor and enjoy the view of mid-level Central', 'Coconut Seafood Curry Rice, Tom Yum Kung, Pad Thai', '', 'Set in the exclusive J-Senses development, and surrounding a Listed Building, Koh Thai Wanchai raises the bar when it comes to Thai dining in the area. With a huge outdoor terrace and a large open kitchen, guests can watch our Thai chefs work their magic, while being looked after by our ever-attentive, friendly staff. Serving stunning Thai food with a wine list to match this is a true escape in the heart of Wanchai.', '5-min walk from MTR Wan Chai station Exit A3', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2509, 'en_US', 'Crab Noodles Private Kitchen', 'Crabs fever! Food are made with fresh crab meat and whole crab', 'Crab Congee, Wanton with Crab Meat', '', 'Crab Noodles located in Central district, you can enjoy their signature everyday store-made crab stock with different variety noodles and ingredient for lunch. Crab Noodles will become a private kitchen for dinner. You can find different crab theme tasting menu with the most seasonal dishes every month. Don’t miss it!', '4-min walk from  MTR Central station Exit D1', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2555, 'en_US', 'La Bon Restaurant & Lounge', 'Private Italian kitchen in Causeway Bay, enjoy your meal in this cozy place', 'Lobster Soup, Chocolate Lava Cake, New Zealand Rib Eye Steak with Red Wine Sauce', '', 'A new breed of continental cuisine, the restaurant is located in the heart of Causeway Bay, a great location. Comfortable and stylish restaurant environment. We undertake all types of customers for the company meetings, parties, private parties, graduation dinners, lectures. Our customers can tailor different menus to meet the needs of various customers.', '5 -min walk from MTR Causeway Bay station Exit A', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2556, 'en_US', 'STACK', 'Creative pancakes dishes in High Street, foodies must go in this lazy cozy place', 'Red Koddo, Running Honey', '', 'Creative pancakes dishes, bottled cocktails and a selection of yummy sides! You can find nowhere for these innovative pancakes creation in STACK. The concepts of STACK are come from the owner of Twins Kitchen, a industrial-chic restaurant by twins Josh and Caleb Ng. Enjoy this cozy and special place in the high street. Book ahead to avoid disappointment!', '3 -min walk from MTR Sai Ying Pun station Exit C', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2572, 'en_US', 'Gianni\'s Trattoria Italiana', 'Home comfort Italian food that can be sampled without the need to or before going to South Italy.', 'Homemade Linguine with Clam and Southern Italian Tomato sause, Cuttlefish Salad, Baked parama ham with cheese', '', 'Gianni\'s Trattoria Italiana offers you the home style Southern Italian cuisine. It is located in the heart of Central Soho. The deco of this restaurant is full of the painting of Venice in Italy. Gianni\'s Trattoria Italiana opened in Jan 2013, the restaurant has proved a must destination lounge for food connoisseurs residing in Hong Kong and visitors from overseas. The restaurant features home comfort Italian food that can be sampled without the need to or before going to South Italy.
