(2583, 'en_US', 'Wooden Boat', 'Enjoy your meal on the Wooden Boat at sea!', 'Grilled Lobster with Butter and Cheese, Garlic Threadfin in Pot, Stir Fried Spicy Crab with Garlic and Chili', '', 'Wooden Boat is located in the center of the Castle Peak Bay sea boat seafood restaurant and bar. 
 There are total of three Wooden Boat, the first just sightseeing boat, which offers boat cruises service, enjoy breathtaking sunsets view. The second boat is an on board seafood restaurant with romantic style which suitable for 2-12 people; the third boat is a music boat which provide live band music, guests can also sing a song there. \"Wooden Boat\" aims to offer guests an unforgettable experience on board, in addition to the delicious food, the most important thing is to memorize the wonderful moment, when years pass, you will remember that beautiful night with romantic ride in a small wooden boat ......', 'Bus Station - Castle Peak Bay', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2584, 'en_US', 'Amore Di Italian Restaurant', 'Romantic ambience with Italian food in Causeway Bay', 'Amore Di Chocolate Lava Cake, Home Made Italian Ravioli, Pan Seared Foie Gras, Black Truffle Cream Soup', '', 'Amore Di Italian Restaurant is located in the downtown of Causeway Bay. You can enjoy the classic Italian cuisine here. “Amore Di” means “love” in Italian and the restaurants want you to “love” and feel their passion of food. The restaurant\'s environment is very elegant and romantic. Don’t miss their Home Made Italian Ravioli!', '1 -min walk from MTR Causeway Bay station Exit C', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2586, 'en_US', 'La Terra', 'Superb Italian mix Spanish restaurant on High Street', 'Crab Meat Avocado Salad, Pavlova', '', 'La Terra is an Italian/Spanish restaurant, and is located in the High Street which is the heart of Hong Kong. A medium-sized restaurant among many other restaurants in High street.
