(2590, 'en_US', 'Small potato (Po Ming Building)', 'Best lazy and cozy cafe in Causeway Bay for you and your friends gathering', 'Quebec Poutine with Honey BBQ Pork Ribs, Stuffing Eggplant with Beef & Cheese, Deep Fried Prawn with Sweet Chili and Sauver Sauce', '', 'Small Potato is the perfect place of getting yourself a break. With quality service, couches and sofa chairs, cheerful music and soft lighting, all we want is to bring you a sweet, cheerful and homey environment. And that\'s what we are here for.\n\nJust as we always believe that home is the best place to indulge ourselves, Small Potato is undoubtedly the second best. And we try our very best to convince you with that too. For those who come for the first time in, their gaze will be immediately transfixed by the mega-size Foosball Table. Here you\'re invited to experience how fabulously simple it could be to indulge yourself. For those who are looking for excitements, the Foosball Table, TV Games, Card Games and Comics are all ready to wash your stress away. If you just want to soothe your mind and have a chatty, friendly gathering, you and your gang may simply throw yourselves into the fluffy couches and enjoy your delicious refreshments', '5 -min walk from MTR Causeway Bay station Exit A', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2591, 'en_US', 'Lotus Courtyard Restaurant', 'Enjoy mother nature in this fine Western style restaurant', 'Sirloin Steak, New Zealand Lamb Rack, Foie Gras', '', 'Lotus Courtyard Restaurant is a Chinese garden style restaurant located in Lam Tseun Valley with a beautiful environment. It has outdoor and indoor seating, a total of about two hundred seats surrounded by nature, plus there is an outdoor piano room and pool, make it perfectly for wedding or party purposes. Lets take a break and enjoy a moment of quiet with your friends at Lotus Courtyard! 
