(2592, 'en_US', 'Good Place', 'Comfortable environment and healthy food selection in Tsim Sha Tsui', 'Chicken with Black Vinegar Sauce, Stuffed Chicken Wings with Potato and Green Curry, Marinated Chicken Wings with Tomato Udon Soup', '', 'We cook with all our heart. From choosing the fresh ingredients, cooking in simple and healthy as we always do at home. We hope to serve you a very nice meal which you can taste the freshness and natural tastes.
No GMS, Less oil, salt and sugar, more vegetable, just like meals at home, simple, healthy, fresh and delicious. Raw wood tables and chairs, decorated with delightful flowers, elegent interior, provide you and your family, friends a warm and peaceful space to enjoy a nice home cooking meal in our \"Good Place\".', '3 -min walk from MTR Tsim Shai Tsui station Exit D2', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2593, 'en_US', 'Taste Cafe', 'Next to Club Marina Cove, European style restaurant, best place for your holiday in Sai Kung!', 'South Pacifiic Prawn Sashimi, Black Truffle Mushroom Soup, Baked Lamb Rack', '', 'Taste cafe is just located next to the Club Marina Cove in Sai Kung. It is a cozy place for you to spend your holiday there. Enjoy the Fresh Oyster, French Blue Lobster, Homemade Lemon Tart etc. there. You will find the real taste of seafood and many kind of food are waiting you to come. Hurry up, Don\'t miss it.', 'MTR Hang Hau Station, change 101M mini bus', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2594, 'en_US', 'Kiwa Japanese Cuisine', 'Japanese imported ingredient, enjoy the special sake in Kiwa', 'Janpanese Style Steam Beef, Stewed Beef Tongue', '', 'It is extremely challenging to satisfy healthy dining and deliciousness, that\'s why Kiwa is strived to bring you both by introducing a brand new dinning experience - SEIRO MUSHI. 
SEIRO MUSHI is inspired by the renowned Kira restaurant in Tokyo. We select top A5 wagyu beef and fresh vegetables air-shipped from Japan and steamed the ingredients in a wooden box. With the unique and organic sources created by our chef, customers not only can taste the true flavor of the ingredients, but also keep a healthy and light dinning experience.
Kiwa also displays the refined elegance of Japanese culture in every dish, from the unique seiro mushi to other classic favorites including sashimi, yakitori and teppanyaki.
