6. Coupon code will be valid for your next dining at any restaurants with Checkout service and is valid for 30 days.', '5 -min walk from MTR Austin station Exit A', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4420, 'en_US', 'shelter lounge', 'A leisurely restaurant, enjoy the afternoon tea set and seafood here!', 'Panna Cotta, Homemade Pasta, The Shelter Lounge ARTernoon Tea Set', 'Closed on Monday', 'shelter lounge is a modern bistro and lounge located in the Sheung Wan district of Hong Kong. It’s an all-day kind of place where you can drop in to enjoy seriously good food.
[ The Shelter Lounge ARTernoon Tea Set ]\nFeatures delicate finger bites and sandwiches, home-made scones, home-baked pastries and mouth-watering sweet treats, along with premium tea and special blend coffee. All bites will be innovated by our chef with the freshest ingredients we\'ve found on the day upon your reservation. You may find different treats each time you come. Guests can choose to dine in the spacious room with high ceiling at our ground floor, an ideal place for those seeking a cozy and private space to chitchat and unwind yourself with friends over weekends. 
Available from Tuesday to Saturday 3pm to 5pm.', '5-min walk from MTR Sai Yin Pun Exit A1.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4421, 'en_US', 'C.O.W. Dining', 'Enjoy the slow cooked dishes in C.O.W. Dining which is tucked away in Kwan Tong', 'Slow Cooked Fresh Spinach Carrot Salad, Slow Cooked Salmon, Sous Vide SteakItalian bacon and black vinegar', '', 'C.O.W. Dining is an Italian Private Kitchen tucked in the industrial district - Kwun Tong Hong Kong. You can enjoy the daily in-house made pasta here. The chef in C.O.W. Dining are good at sous vide dishes which means slow cooked the food in a vacuum plastic bags and place in a water bath, you can taste the “real” flavor of the ingredient!', '10-min walk from MTR Kwum Tong Station A2 Exit.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4425, 'en_US', 'La lune', 'La Lune - meaning the Moon in French, serving you fantastic French cuisine.', 'Angus Rib Eye Steak, Masala Roasted Lamb Rack with Fresh Mint Dip', '', 'La Lune --- meaning the Moon in French, leads us to imagine the French romance under the moonlight.
A bistro located in a pedestrian street on the junction of Wing Woo Street, near Queen\'s Road Central and Des Voeux Road, La Lune injects European sentiments into the hustle and bustle of the city. The roadside café and bistro brings a relaxed holiday atmosphere to the busy downtown district. 
La Lune’s interior layout is very poetic, just like the fascinating character of a whiskey bar. The food quality is also much more mature than a bistro. The high quality ingredients integrate with the chef\'s skills and the environment. 
Wall paintings are artistic works of a local reputable photographer, Platini Leung, who seeks to blend the mood of his photographs and the design of the bistro together. Since the owner of La Lune is art lover, he plans to organize various workshops for local artists to exchange ideas. Thus, La Lune aims to provide an interactive platform for artists to enhance the artistic temperament of Hong Kong.', '4-min walk from MTR Sheung Wan Station A1 Exit.', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2614, 'en_US', 'Caprice - Four Seasons', 'Michelin two-star restaurant, Caprice offers contemporary French cuisine.', 'Japanese cattle with mushroom, Warm Duck Foie Gras, Fennel Confit and Strawberries in Sweet Spices Sauce, Pan, fried sea bass with garlic', '', 'With stunning views over Victoria Harbour, Michelin two-star restaurant, Caprice offers contemporary French cuisine accompanied by an extensive selection of wines from the Bordeaux and Burgundy regions. Something cultural pavilions, old and new convergence echoed in the city.This blend of commerce and culture to suit different needs to enjoy a memorable experience (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit E1, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2615, 'en_US', 'Lung King Heen - Four Seasons', 'Lung King Heen was the first Chinese restaurant to be awarded 3 Michelin Stars.', 'Crispy Spring Rolls with Crab Meat and Black Truffle, Barbecued Pork with Honey and Crispy Scallop with Fresh Pear, Lung King Heen Lobster Fried Rice with Seafood', '', 'This Michelin three-star Chinese restaurant is led by Executive Chef Chan Yan Tak. As the first Chinese chef to receive three Michelin stars, Chef Chan is the master behind the intricately designed menu at Lung King Heen. Chef Chan combines textures and flavours with inventive presentations to excite your taste buds and satisfy even the most demanding epicure. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit E1, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2616, 'en_US', 'Inagiku Japanese Restaurant - Four Seasons', 'An expert in traditional Japanese cuisine, be sure to sample Chef Shigeru’s signature kaiseki.', 'Prawn tempura, Beef teppanyaki, Deluxe assorted sashimi platter', '', 'An expert in traditional Japanese cuisine, be sure to sample Chef Shigeru’s signature kaiseki. Another restaurant specialty, tempura, is known for its authentic ingredients – notably, a secret sesame oil blend imported directly from Japan. Each piece is artfully prepared to your preference and served in the traditional way. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit E1, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2617, 'en_US', 'Inagiku Japanese Restaurant - The Royal Garden, Kowloon', 'An expert in traditional Japanese cuisine, be sure to sample Chef Shigeru’s signature kaiseki.', 'Prawn tempura, Beef teppanyaki, Deluxe assorted sashimi platter', '', 'An expert in traditional Japanese cuisine, be sure to sample Chef Shigeru’s signature kaiseki. Another restaurant specialty, tempura, is known for its authentic ingredients – notably, a secret sesame oil blend imported directly from Japan. Each piece is artfully prepared to your preference and served in the traditional way. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2618, 'en_US', 'Sabatini Ristorante Italiano - The Royal Garden, Kowloon', 'The original Sabatini Ristorante Italiano restaurant opened in Rome in 1954. This fine dining room is one of the two restaurants opened around the world.', 'Risotto, Parma ham with Melon, Tiramisu', '', 'The original Sabatini Ristorante Italiano restaurant opened in Rome in 1954. This fine dining room at The Royal Garden is one of the two restaurants opened around the world. A traditional “Roman cuisine” menu is overseen by the Sabatini brothers and is served in a picturesque “countryside” setting. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2619, 'en_US', 'Dong Lai Shun - The Royal Garden, Kowloon', 'Founded in Beijing and renowned for authentic “Shuan Yang Rou”.The restaurant ‘s design is seem like Beijing House.', 'Crab tofu with casserole, Rinse lamb, Salted duck', '', 'Founded in Beijing and renowned for authentic “Shuan Yang Rou”. Huaiyang cuisines are also offered to widen your choices at Dong Lai Shun restaurant in Hong Kong. It has been crowned as the one Michelin star restaurant in the Michelin Guide Hong Kong Macau 2013. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2620, 'en_US', 'Royal Garden Chinese Restaurant   \n - The Royal Garden, Kowloon', '“Home” cooked, seasonal Cantonese cuisine and daily fresh seafood are the order of the day. It is a popular venue for lunch time dim-sum and evening dining with friends and business associates.', 'Two taste of “East Star spot” fish, Golden frying noodles, Steamed red crab with Chanterelle and rice wine', '', 'At The Royal Garden Chinese Restaurant one can live like a Mandarin. Modeled on a Chinese official\'s formal water garden of yesteryear, this gourmet restaurant has won many awards and distinctions. Here, “home” cooked, seasonal Cantonese cuisine and daily fresh seafood are the order of the day. It is a popular venue for lunch time dim-sum and evening dining with friends and business associates. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2621, 'en_US', 'Le Soleil - The Royal Garden, Kowloon', 'Le Soleil offers Vietnamese cuisine with a touch of Asian-fusion.', 'Roasted quail, Prawn curry, Signature roasted Lobster', '', 'A Hong Kong branch of the popular award-winning San Francisco restaurant. Located on the hotel\'s third floor mezzanine level and overlooking the atrium\'s greenery and water features, the restaurant offers Vietnamese cuisine with a touch of Asian-fusion. It offers a medley of tastes and flavors. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2622, 'en_US', 'The Greenery - The Royal Garden, Kowloon', 'The Greenery offers an \"international\" menu for all-day, casual dining in a garden-like setting.', 'Hainanese Chicken Rice, Seafood platter, Sashimi and roasted sushi', '', 'The Greenery offers an \"international\" menu for all-day, casual dining in a garden-like setting, surrounded by the atrium’s lush foliage and burbling water features and – in the evenings, the melodies of a live pianist. Lunch and dinner buffets feature jet-fresh seafood and regional specialties and constantly changes with seasonal items supplementing the already extensive and value-for-money buffet table. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2623, 'en_US', 'Gaddi\'s - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'Gaddi\'s has long held an impeccable reputation as a superb restaurant.', 'Vendéen pigeon breast roasted with Muscovado sugar, its stuffed leg and glazed root vegetables, Piece of wild turbot from the Brittany coast with celery and black truffle, Chocolate pavlova with espresso cream, caramel ice cream', '', 'Gaddi\'s has long held an impeccable reputation as a superb restaurant. With Chef van Peteghem\'s French heritage, a wealth of experience at prestigious gastronomic restaurants in France and his culinary dexterity, his cuisine legere pays homage to Gaddi\'s traditions with a light contemporary twist. Besides, Gaddi\'s is home to some of the hotels most prized collectables, including Christofle candelabras brought to The Peninsula from Shanghai in the 1920’s and a number of fine art pieces. (Source : official website) (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2624, 'en_US', 'Felix - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'Serving cosmopolitan cuisine with the freshest ingredients, the restaurant offers breathtaking views of Hong Kong.', 'Smoke beef filet, Perch and green onion prawn mousse with champagne butter sauce, Hazel Italy Cheese Cake, Pan fried goose liver with pear, pink pepper and vanilla', '', 'Located on the 28th floor of The Peninsula tower, Felix is the creation of the world-famous avantgarde designer, Philippe Starck. Serving cosmopolitan cuisine with the freshest ingredients, the restaurant offers breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour, Hong Kong Island and Kowloon. Other features include a Wine Bar, The Balcony, American Bar and The Crazy Box, a small discotheque. The restaurant including The Balcony 、 American Bar 、 Wine Bar及 The Crazy Box. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2625, 'en_US', 'Chesa - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'Chesa is a haven for lovers of raclette and cheese fondue.', 'Gruyère and Vacherin Fribourgeoise cheese fondueserved with baguette, Whole roasted spring chicken with mixed herbs, Crab meat pancake', '', 'Close to the heart of Hong Kong diners for over 40 years, Chesa boasts three generations of loyal customers. This bijou and romantic Alpine chalet is where welcoming and cosy meet delectable in an unpretentious and relaxed setting. Chesa is a haven for lovers of raclette and cheese fondue, and the menu also features classic Swiss favourites, such as veal \"Zurichoise\", hand-made sausages with rosti, Spätzle and a host of delectable delights. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2626, 'en_US', 'Spring Moon - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'The Peninsula\'s Cantonese restaurant presents Chinese cuisine in its purest form.', 'Steamed crystal shrimp dumplings with spider crab legs, Baked crispy buns with minced Wagyu beef, onions and black pepper, Siu mai with scallops and wild mushrooms', '', 'The Peninsula\'s Cantonese restaurant presents Chinese cuisine in its purest form. Specialities include an array of seafood, dim sum and the acclaimed XO sauce made to a secret recipe. Dim sum at Spring Moon is a timeless classic, featuring expertly crafted favourites from steamed crystal shrimp dumplings with spider crab legs to baked crispy buns with minced Wagyu beef, onions and black pepper or siu mai with scallops and wild mushrooms, with a refined twist. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2627, 'en_US', 'Imasa - The Peninsula Hong Kong', '\"Attentive Service with great fresh sashimi”,You won\'t dare to miss it.', 'Roast beef with stone, Kaiseki, Deluxe Assorted sashimi', '', 'Imasa offers a Japanese culinary adventure for sushi and sashimi lovers and a welcome dining experience for Japanese food aficionados. Served with meticulous attention to detail and fresh ingredients imported daily, the staff is as adept at guiding the novice through the traditional yet contemporary menu as meeting and exceeding the expectations of the sophisticated and experienced diner. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2628, 'en_US', 'The Verandah - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'Hong Kong\'s very first fine buffet concept.', 'Scottish Oak Smoked Salmon, Strawberry Soufflé, The Café Club Sandwich', '', 'Hong Kong\'s very first fine buffet concept, The Verandah now offers an expanded gastronomic offering in glorified new surrounds. Originally opened in 1933, variety, quality and a wealth of culinary styles are the signatures of The Verandah, serving breakfast, lunch and dinner, as well as an array of cakes and sandwiches in the afternoon. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2629, 'en_US', 'The Lobby - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'There is nothing more quintessentially iconic of Hong Kong than experiencing the acclaimed Peninsula Classic Afternoon Tea.', 'Peninsula Afternoon Tea, Peninsula features a thin steak and grilled cheese sandwiches, Indonesian fried noodles with chicken and shrimp', '', 'There is nothing more quintessentially iconic of Hong Kong than experiencing the acclaimed Peninsula Classic Afternoon Tea. Served daily in The Lobby, which has long been recognised as one of the most elegant meeting places in Hong Kong, this revered tradition is accompanied by The Lobby Strings, playing live daily. An à la carte menu showcasing authentic Continental and Southeast Asian delights is served throughout the day. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2630, 'en_US', 'The Bar - The Peninsula Hong Kong', 'The Bar is the perfect place to unwind after work, cement business ties or enjoy a quintessential Martini', 'Quintessential Martini, Pink Dots Mocktail (non, alcoholic), The Joy Of Chocolate', '', 'The Bar at The Peninsula Hong Kong offers a stellar list of craft cocktails, rare single malt whiskies and vintage Armagnacs served in an exceptional setting. The Bar is the perfect place to unwind after work, cement business ties or enjoy a quintessential Martini, accompanied by the sounds of authentic jazz pianist Pierre Eugene, who brings life and song to the ambience of warm, understated elegance. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2631, 'en_US', 'Grand Hyatt Steakhouse - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', '160 labels of superlative international wines and over 600 bottles from around the world.', 'Canadian Angus Beef T, Bone, Seared Maryland Crab Cakes, Choclate Mud Pie', '', 'Being one of the best steak houses in Hong Kong, Grand Hyatt Steakhouse features prime cuts of beef from the US, Canada and Japan. Additional offerings include an oyster and seafood bar and an elaborate salad bar. An impressive selection of wine by the glass and an astute wine list from around the world. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2632, 'en_US', 'GRISSINI - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', 'Its contemporary interior design conjures up the feeling of a stylish New York restaurant.', 'Beef Carpaccio with Rucola Salad and Parmigiano Reggiano Taggiasca Extra Virgin Olive Oil, Baked Sea Bass with Fresh Tomatoes, Taggiasca Olives, Capers and Red Onion, Traditional Plin Ravioli stuffed with Braised Pork Cheek, Pork demi, glace and Fresh Rosemary', '', 'Grissini commands panoramic views of Victoria Harbour. Its contemporary interior design, Philippe Starck chairs and modern Tony Delapp paintings conjure up the feeling of a stylish New York restaurant. An extensive selection of Italian wines is displayed in the two-storey wine cellar with an impressive floor-to-ceiling Vinotheque. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2633, 'en_US', 'One Harbour Road - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', 'Tasting the cuisine of masterpiece by chef Mr. Lee , while enjoying breathtaking ocean views of Victoria Harbour.', 'Osmanthus sauce fried fresh mushrooms, Crispy “Cha Wong” Chicken, Sichuan shrimp Ball with Crab', '', 'One Harbour Road is best known for serving traditional homestyle Cantonese cuisine, lovingly prepared and graciously presented.The Chef’s Table private room inside the kitchen features exclusive innovative dishes and presents a rare glimpse into the workings of the kitchen. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2634, 'en_US', 'Tiffin - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', 'Its panoramic city and garden views, plush sofas and extra high ceiling makes it the perfect venue for a relaxing Sunday Brunch Buffet.', 'Champagne Cream Baked Boston Lobster, Frozen prawns and fresh conch, Norwegian salmon dill cream cheese roll', '', 'Tiffin’s afternoon tea set features a delicious spread of savoury and sweet items, while the lunch and dinner buffet presents a selection of western and European delicacies. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2635, 'en_US', 'Kaetsu - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', 'Fresh seafood and exclusive sake selection,let you have a good meal!', 'Grilled A3 Wagyu Beef in Houba Leaf, Homemade Sesame Beancurd, Fresh Seasonal Sashimi and Sushi', '', 'Kaetsu Japanese restaurant, whose name literally means the sounds that deer make when calling friends for a good meal. The menu features traditional Japanese favourites and seasonal specialities prepared with freshly flown-in ingredients from Japan. An exclusive selection of sake is also available, including some rare choices in town. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2636, 'en_US', 'Grand Cafe - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', 'This stylish art deco restaurant is an ideal venue for an enjoyable all-day dining experience, completed with great harbour and city views.', 'Hainanese Chicken Rice, Grand Cafe Salad with Grilled Salmon, Pan Fried Iberico Pork Chop', '', 'Informal yet elegant, the Grand Cafe features an international a la carte menu ideal for all-day dining, casual lunches and informal meetings. The afternoon tea buffet provides a spectacular array of sweet and savoury delights. In the evening, the restaurant offers a grand international dinner buffet, popular for family and friends gathering. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2637, 'en_US', 'The Grill  - Grand Hyatt Hong Kong', 'Outdoor poolside dining in the heart of bustling Hong Kong – The Grill offers an exceptional experience for its guests.', 'Pita Bread Pocket with Sauteed Lamb, Cucumber Yoghurt, Lettuce, Avocado and Tomato, Char, grilled Premium Meats & Seafoods, Greek Salad, Cucumber, Tomatoes, Young Spinach, Calamatta Olives, Green Peppers with Oregano and Grilled Feta Cheese', '', 'Set in the centre of a lush garden, The Grill offers alfresco dining for grilled specialities, home-made fruit and vegetable blends and speciality ice teas. The weekend brunch and barbecue dinner buffet is perfect for those who enjoy refreshing salads, grilled premium quality meat and seafood, and mouth-watering desserts. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2638, 'en_US', 'SPOON by Alain Ducasse - InterContinental Hong Kong', '2-Michelin Star SPOON by Alain Ducasse features contemporary French cuisine inspired by Alain Ducasse, one of the world’s most celebrated chefs.', 'Chocolate Dessert, France Lamb Rack, Foie Gras', '', '2-Michelin Star SPOON by Alain Ducasse features contemporary French cuisine inspired by Alain Ducasse, one of the world’s most celebrated chefs.The seductive menu and wine list showcase Mr. Ducasse’s flair, with French nuances also revealed in the restaurant’s sophisticated, yet casual-chic ambiance, enhanced by stunning views of Victoria Harbour. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit J, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2639, 'en_US', 'NOBU InterContinental Hong Kong - InterContinental Hong Kong', 'NOBU, the world’s most acclaimed Japanese restaurant, is renowned for its innovative new-style Japanese cuisine.', 'Toro tatar with caviar, Sea Lion Sashimi with spain pepper, Soft, shell Crab Roll, New, style sashimi', '', 'NOBU, the world’s most acclaimed Japanese restaurant, is renowned for its innovative new-style Japanese cuisine. Drawing upon Nobu Matsuhisa’s classical training as a sushi chef in Tokyo, his life abroad in Peru and Argentina and his travels around the world, NOBU InterContinental Hong Kong showcases Nobu’s signature dishes, as well as new creations using local ingredients. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit J, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2640, 'en_US', 'THE STEAK HOUSE winebar + grill - InterContinental Hong Kong', 'The 1-Michelin Star restaurant is a haven with prime cuts of the world\'s finest meat for meat lovers.', 'Chocolate fondant, Green Tea Chocolate Fondant, Rib Eye Steak, New Orleans Crab Cake', '', 'The 1-Michelin Star STEAK HOUSE winebar + grill is a haven for meat lovers with prime cuts of the world\'s finest meat, seared to perfection on Hong Kong\'s only charcoal grill. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit J, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2641, 'en_US', 'Yan Toh Heen - InterContinental Hong Kong', 'Awarded 2-Michelin Stars, Yan Toh Heen is recognized as one of the world\'s finest Chinese restaurants specializing in Cantonese cuisine.', 'Baked Roasted Duck and Taro Buns, Peking Duck, Crispy Pork Fillet with Mandarin Zest', '', 'Awarded 2-Michelin Stars, Yan Toh Heen is recognized as one of the world\'s finest Chinese restaurants specializing in Cantonese cuisine. Executive Chef Lau Yiu Fai uses refined Chinese cooking methods combined with the best ingredients and top quality fresh seasonal products. The restaurant features an extensive a la carte menu, plus set lunch and dinner options and special menus showcasing seasonal Cantonese specialties. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit J, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2642, 'en_US', 'Harbourside - InterContinental Hong Kong', 'Harbourside is reknowned for its elaborate buffets.', 'Lobster, Foie, Seafood', '', 'Perched directly at the harbour\'s edge, Harbourside offers casual all-day dining with both a la carte and buffet options, showcasing an elaborate selection of International dishes. Harbourside is acclaimed for its elaborate buffets, with chefs presenting a tempting array of Western and Asian dishes, a roast carving station with prime cuts of beef, action stations and decadent home-made desserts. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit J, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2643, 'en_US', 'Restaurant Petrus - Island Shangri-la Hong Kong', 'Perched high above the city with breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour, Restaurant Petrus epitomises the highest standard of excellence in French cuisine.', 'Layers of chocolate mousse, Whole roasted foie gras, Roasted duck breast', '', 'Perched high above the city with breathtaking views of Victoria Harbour, Restaurant Petrus epitomises the highest standard of excellence in French cuisine. The restaurant includes a wine cellar that features one of the most extensive wine lists in Asia. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2644, 'en_US', 'Nadaman Japanese Restaurant - Island Shangri-la Hong Kong', 'A classic japanese restaurant at Tsim Sha Tsui East.', 'Kaiseki Ryori, Grilled abalone in sea salt., Top, quality selection of the freshest sashimi.', '', 'Since 1830, the famous group of restaurants known as Nadaman has been treating discerning diners in Japan to fine kaiseki cuisine. Here in Hong Kong, Shangri-La has had the privilege of establishing the first Nadaman outside of Japan. Ever since, the elegant presentation and delicate tastes that comprise this historic dining tradition have attracted both new and loyal patrons. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2645, 'en_US', 'Summer Palace  - Island Shangri-la Hong Kong', 'Discover Summer Palace’s signature dishes and Chef Ip’s specialties for yourself.', 'Sliced barbecued suckling pig, Stewed spare, ribs in a clay pot, Chilled sago cream with mango juice and pomelo', '', 'At the Michelin two-star Summer Palace, Chef Ip Chi Cheung presents the best of Cantonese cuisine with award-winning culinary flair. The restaurant offers authentic Cantonese and seasonal favourites in a setting that evokes the grandeur of our Chinese heritage. Discover Summer Palace’s signature dishes and Chef Ip’s specialties for yourself. An extensive dim sum menu is also available for lunch daily. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2646, 'en_US', 'Lobster Bar and Grill - Island Shangri-la Hong Kong', 'Only the freshest produce is presented to diners at the Lobster Bar and Grill.', 'Lobster Bar and Grill Seafood Platter, Grilled French Sea Bass, Lobster Bisque', '', 'Head Chef Kevin Lee has over 20 years of fine culinary expertise under his belt. This wealth of experience has kept diners at the Lobster Bar and Grill delighted, and Chef Lee keeps things fresh with inventive takes on culinary classics. His seafood specialities are a must-try for any seafood lover. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2647, 'en_US', 'Cafe TOO - Island Shangri-la Hong Kong', 'Cafe TOO showcases for the best of international cuisines as well as stages for our chefs’ engaging performances.', 'Cafe TOO Antipasto Platter, Traditional Hainanese Chicken Rice, Freshly Baked Thin Apple Tart with Homemade Ice, Cream', '', 'The innovative cafe TOO brings a high level of creativity to casual dining. Our ten cooking theatres, each featuring a different culinary style, are showcases for the best of international cuisines as well as stages for our chefs’ engaging performances. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2648, 'en_US', 'Mandarin Grill + Bar - Mandarin Oriental Hong Kong', 'Using the finest organic ingredients and seasonally inspired produce, Mandarin Grill + Bar offers a one-of-a-kind fine dining experiences.', 'Oyster, Cote de Boeuf, BFG (dessert)', '', 'The Mandarin Grill + Bar, overseen by Executive Chef Uwe Opocensky, has retained its Michelin star for the sixth year running. Using the finest organic ingredients and seasonally inspired produce, Mandarin Grill + Bar offers a one-of-a-kind fine dining experiences. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2649, 'en_US', 'The Krug Room - Mandarin Oriental Hong Kong', 'Brilliantly creative tasting menus partnered with Krug champagne in a sophisticated, intimate restaurant.', 'Scallop Chip, Krug & Lobster, Tongue & Cheek', '', 'Offering a taste of progressive gastronomy, there is no menu in The Krug Room. Instead, each evening’s dinner varies between 10-14 courses and is created according to Uwe Opocensky’s inspiration. Alongside these dishes, guests can select from the largest collection of Krug champagne outside of France. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2650, 'en_US', 'Pierre - Mandarin Oriental Hong Kong', 'It is here that diners can experience outstanding modern French cuisine in a stunning environment.', 'La Bretagne, Le Homard de Trois Facons, Le Sirocco', '', 'This stunning Two-Michelin starred restaurant, situated on the 25th floor, is Pierre Gagnaire\'s pied a terre in Hong Kong, It is here that diners can experience outstanding modern French cuisine in a stunning environment. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2651, 'en_US', 'Clipper Lounge - Mandarin Oriental Hong Kong', 'Whether it\'s Sunday champagne brunch in Hong Kong or a 5-star dinner buffet with the family, the Clipper Lounge is your best choice.', 'Tandoori Prawn Salad, Miso Cod, Thai Green Prawn Curry', '', 'While popular for breakfast, lunch and dinner buffets, as well as our Sunday champagne brunch Hong Kong locals love, the Clipper Lounge is best known for afternoon tea. Elegantly presented on silver stands, the spread includes delicacies such as finger sandwiches, sweets, scones and our signature rose-petal jam. We also offer extremely popular seasonal themed teas, taking inspiration from the worlds of fashion, art and culture. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2652, 'en_US', 'Cafe Causette - Mandarin Oriental Hong Kong', 'Café Causette offers elegant all-day dining with something for everyone.', 'Hainan Chicken Rice, Classic burger, Slow Cooked Organic Salmon', '', 'Café Causette’s lively show-kitchens serve a range of dishes from all over the world. Discover Asian favourites such as Nasi Goreng and Hainan Chicken Rice on an extensive menu that also features classic international offerings such as The Mandarin Burger and pizzas that are considered by many to be the best in town. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2653, 'en_US', 'Man Wah - Mandarin Oriental Hong Kong', 'Man Wah is  referred as the most beautiful dining space in Hong Kong.', 'Golden taro puff, abalone, Stir fried lobster, egg white, caviar, scallop mousse, gold leaf, Beef tenderloin puff, black pepper sauce', '', 'Located on the 25th floor, our Michelin-starred Cantonese restaurant serves exquisite local and regional specialties. Often referred to as Hong Kong’s most beautiful dining space, Man Wah’s atmospheric decor and panoramic views of Victoria Harbour and the Hong Kong skyline provide the perfect setting for wonderfully delicious cuisine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2654, 'en_US', 'Oyster & Wine Bar - Sheraton Hong Kong Hotel & Towers', 'The Oyster & Wine Bar is a fabulous place to indulge in some of the best seafood in the city.', '20, 30 types of oysters all over the world, Oven Roasted Iowa Rack of Lamb, Napoleon of Balik Salmon', '', 'The Oyster & Wine Bar is a fabulous place to indulge in some of the best seafood in the city. Enjoy the luxuries of excellent seafood and wine while admiring the breathtaking view of Victoria Harbour and the spectacular Hong Kong skyline.The sophisticated atmosphere is enhanced with impressive wine cellars, colourful and contemporary furnishings, and a custom-designed oyster bar. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2655, 'en_US', 'Unkai Japanese Cuisine - Sheraton Hong Kong Hotel & Towers', 'Savor traditional Osaka cuisine and a superior sake collection at Unkai Japanese restaurant.', 'Grilled Lobsters, Sauteed Wagyu Beef with Ginger Sauce, Teppanyaki Foie Gras or Lamb Chop', '', 'Savor traditional Osaka cuisine and a superior sake collection at Unkai Japanese restaurant. Serene and tranquil, Unkai is a small oasis in the midst of Hong Kong’s hustle and bustle where you can savor Teppan grilled meats, sushi, and sake. Award-winning Unkai is divided into six main dining areas: open Teppan, private Teppan, sushi and sake bar, private rooms, main dining area and the Tatami room. Each offers a distinctive ambience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2656, 'en_US', 'Celestial Court Chinese Restaurant - Sheraton Hong Kong Hotel & Towers', 'The Celestial Court Chinese Restaurant features authentic Chinese cuisine, award-winning dim sum, and a wide selection of Chinese teas.', 'Roasted Suckling Pig, Shimeji & Mushrooms with Sliced Black Chicken & Frog, Braised Beancurd Skin Rolls filled with Assorted Vegetables &Mushrooms', '', 'The Celestial Court Chinese Restaurant features authentic Chinese cuisine, award-winning dim sum, and a wide selection of Chinese teas. Tastefully decorated with warm burlwood panels and raw silk wall coverings, Celestial Court exemplifies Oriental style.Seasonal menus offer a selection of crunchy vegetables, savory meats and succulent seafood, as well as a wide selection of teas. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2657, 'en_US', 'The Cafe - Sheraton Hong Kong Hotel & Towers', 'The ambience is casual and contemporary, and a specialty corner features the spices of India.', 'Black Tiger Prawns, Yabbies, Oysters', '', 'In this warm and relaxing all-day dining venue, a sumptuous buffet offers international cuisine with a focus on Chinese, Indian, and Western dishes. The ambience is casual and contemporary, and a specialty corner features the spices of India. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2658, 'en_US', 'Morton\'s of Chicago - Sheraton Hong Kong Hotel & Towers', 'You can enjoy your dinner with iconic harbour view from every table.', 'USDA Ribeye Steak, Single Cut Filet Mignon, Jumbo Lump Crab Cake', '', 'Morton\'s of Chicago in Hong Kong is located in vibrant Kowloon famous for its shopping, harbor side location and world class hotels. With iconic harbour views from every table, the restaurant offers fine quality dining, seamless service and elegant surroundings including a private dining room for 12 and a bar serving Morton\'s famous Bar Bites menu alongside an award winning wine menu. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2659, 'en_US', 'Tosca\n - The Ritz-Carlton Hong Kong', 'The innovative Italian menu features improved interpretations of the region’s notable cuisine.', 'Spaghetti alla chitarra with baby squid and swordfish, Sea Tiramisu, Baked Lobster', '', 'Relive the passion and enchantment of one the world’s most beloved operas through the inspired cuisine of Tosca. The innovative Italian menu features improved favorites and thrilling interpretations of the region’s notable cuisine, and an open kitchen allows guests an even more theatrical dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit C1, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2660, 'en_US', 'Cafe 103 - The Ritz-Carlton Hong Kong', 'Cafe 103 have elegant and comfortable environment, make your life perfect.', 'Milk Chocolate Caramel Tart, French Puffs, Tuffle Egg Mayonaise Brown Bread         Sandwich', '', 'Cafe 103 has elegant and comfortable environment, located at 103 F, International Commerce Centre in Hong Kong, is the Hong Kong highest cafe, through the window you can see the coastline in Tsim Sha Tsui. Offer famous chocolate afternoon tea and buffet lunch and dinner. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit C1, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2661, 'en_US', 'Tin Lung Heen - The Ritz-Carlton Hong Kong', 'Hong Kong’s traditional Dim Sum, Tin Lung Heen also features an elegant setting and awesome view from the 102nd floor.', 'Spanish barbecued black pork, Eel ball combined with osmanthus, honey andpepper, Rice wine crab claws with steamed egg', '', 'A popular venue for Hong Kong’s traditional Dim Sum, Tin Lung Heen also features an elegant setting, impeccable service and a spectacular view from the 102nd floor. Experience our six-course degustation menu, showcasing the brilliant presentation and overall culinary excellence that have earned Tin Lung Heen the distinction of two Michelin stars. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit C1, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2662, 'en_US', 'The Lounge & Bar - The Ritz-Carlton Hong Kong', 'The Lounge & Bar offers a wide tea and coffee selection, including its signature afternoon tea accompanied by live band performance.', 'Top Oysters, Boston Lobster, Italian Organic Pumpkin Risotto', '', 'The Lounge & Bar Located at ICC in Hong Kong. An ideal all-day dining venue from breakfast onwards, The Lounge & Bar offers a wide tea and coffee selection, including its signature afternoon tea accompanied by live band performance. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit C1, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2663, 'en_US', 'Amber - The Landmark Mandarin Oriental', 'Exquisite fine dining with a stunning design and delicious cuisine by Culinary Director Richard Ekkebus.', 'Hokkaido Sea Urchin, Foie Gras Lollipop, Tasmanian Salmon', '', 'Exquisite Fine dining with a stunning design and delicious cuisine by Culinary Director Richard Ekkebus. Amber has earned its two Michelin Star for 6 years running. It also claims its 4th spot on the S.Pellegrino Asia\'s 50 Best restaurants. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2664, 'en_US', 'Hugo\'s - Hyatt Regency Hong Kong, Tsim Sha Tsui', 'Hugo’s revives the craft of table-side preparation for dishes.', 'Lobster bisque, Steak au Poivre, Mango Foster', '', 'Hugo’s is a fine dining restaurant offering classic European cuisine. Hugo’s revives the craft of table-side preparation for dishes such as caesar salad, lobster bisque, steak tartare, cherries jubilee and Café Diablo. Roasted US rib of beef, served from the silver carving wagon, is also the signature dish of Hugo’s. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit N2, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2665, 'en_US', 'Cafe - Hyatt Regency Hong Kong, Tsim Sha Tsui', 'Diners are able to watch their food being freshly prepared and eat straight out of the pan, off the grill or from the wok.', 'Desserts, Ice, cream, Lobster', '', 'The all-day restaurant Cafe offers breakfast, lunch, dinner and afternoon tea buffet as well as a la carte delicacies, serving international fare by various show kitchens specialising in dishes such as sushi and sashimi, teppanyaki, tempura etc. . Diners are able to watch their food being freshly prepared and eat straight out of the pan, off the grill or from the wok. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit N2, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2666, 'en_US', 'The Chinese Restaurant - Hyatt Regency Hong Kong, Tsim Sha Tsui', 'The Chinese Restaurant combines a modern art deco design masterfully blended with the essence of a traditional 1920s tea house, a warming dining time for you.', 'Double, boiled fish maw soup, sea cucumber, young papaya, Wok, baked lobster, superior broth, Grilled Half Lobster Tail', '', 'The Chinese Restaurant combines a modern art deco design masterfully blended with the essence of a traditional 1920s tea house, creating a warm and unique dining experience for authentic Chinese cuisine such as dim sum, double-boiled crab meat soup in young papaya, barbecued pork, smoked chicken with jasmine flavour and steamed garoupa fillet with home-made pickled chilli. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit N2, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2667, 'en_US', 'Le 188° Restaurant & Lounge - Harbour Grand Hong Kong', 'Relax at any corner of the restaurant and enjoy high tea accompanied by the setting sun behind the Hong Kong skyline.', 'Foie gras, Lobster salad, Italian Oxtail Wonton', '', 'Surrounded by floor-to-ceiling windows on 3 sides, Le 188° Restaurant & Lounge offers a 188-degree harbour view from the very top of Harbour Grand Hong Kong. Savour modern European cuisine and seafood delights from our Oyster Bar in a romantic, intimate environment. Relax at any corner of the restaurant and enjoy high tea accompanied by the setting sun behind the Hong Kong skyline. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2668, 'en_US', 'Kwan Cheuk Heen - Harbour Grand Hong Kong', 'Each one is all outstanding delicious, to the utmost accept the world Cantonese food essence.', 'Kwan Cheuk abalone cakes, Truffles, Pears with season crab', '', 'Experience the delights of fine Cantonese cuisine against the backdrop of Hong Kong\'s signature harbour view at Kwan Cheuk Heen. Dine in an exquisite restaurant setting that tastefully combines modern and traditional Chinese design, either in the main dining hall or the private dining room of Kwan Cheuk Heen. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2669, 'en_US', 'Nagomi - Harbour Grand Hong Kong', 'Nagomi tantalizes your taste buds with expertly prepared Japanese cuisine, featuring mouth-watering sushi, sashimi and tempura.', 'Sushi, Sashimi, Tempura', '', 'Nagomi tantalizes your taste buds with expertly prepared Japanese cuisine, featuring mouth-watering sushi, sashimi and tempura. This exclusive Japanese cuisine dining experience provides a feast for the eyes as well as the palate with its unique Zen garden setting. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2670, 'en_US', 'Brasserie on the Eighth - Conrad Hong Kong', 'Our vibrant atmosphere and warm service is inspired by a dynamic open kitchen serving a seamless blend of past and present in French-continental cuisine.', 'Oven, Roasted Stuffed “Pauillac” Lamb Saddle, Foie gras, Line, Caught French Seabass', '', 'Our vibrant atmosphere and warm service is inspired by a dynamic open kitchen serving a seamless blend of past and present in French-continental cuisine, and featuring traditional French provincial specialties, Brasserie on the Eighth is also a very popular venue for Sunday brunch. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2671, 'en_US', 'Nicholini\'s - Conrad Hong Kong', 'Nicholini\'s serves Northern Italian cuisine with homemade pastas, fresh produce and the region\'s finest culinary traditions at heart.', 'Angel hair pasta with lobster, tomato and basil, Grilled langoustine, Beef carpaccio', '', 'Nicholini\'s serves Northern Italian cuisine with homemade pastas, fresh produce and the region\'s finest culinary traditions at heart. Experience a feast for the senses with towering views of Hong Kong as your personal backdrop. With an extensive wine cellar and wide selection of home-made pasta, the award-winning Nicholini\'s features authentic Italian cuisine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2672, 'en_US', 'Golden Leaf - Conrad Hong Kong', 'A beloved name in Chinese dining, the one Michelin-Starred Golden Leaf is a must-visit destination for fans of Cantonese cuisine with a passion for detail at its very core.', 'Sautéed diced beef with spicy salt, Deep, fried prawn balls, Pan, fried mixed vegetables rolled in dried bean curd skin', '', 'A beloved name in Chinese dining, the One Michelin-Starred Golden Leaf is a must-visit destination for fans of Cantonese cuisine with a passion for detail at its very core. It provides a special Cantonese dining experience. A wide range of traditional Cantonese dishes is available, plus innovative creations from the chef. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2673, 'en_US', 'Garden Cafe - Conrad Hong Kong', 'Serving a sumptuous international buffet featuring fresh seafood and a variety of Western and Asian favourites.', 'Linguine “Cabonara” style, Chinese wonton noodle soup, Hainanese Chicken Rice', '', 'Serving a sumptuous international buffet featuring fresh seafood and a variety of Western and Asian favourites, Garden Café is an engaging dining experience fit for any occasion. Select from full breakfast, tempting lunch, or extensive a la carte menus. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2674, 'en_US', 'Café Malacca - Hotel Jen', 'Hong Kong the one and only Singapore and Malaysia Cuisine,can\'t wait for it.', 'Penang Asam Laksa, Char kway teow, Hainanese Chicken Rice', '', 'Café Malacca has been named a Bib Gourmand restaurant in the MICHELIN Guide 2014 & 2015, and my dining team has crafted the perfect culinary experience. Transport yourself to the hawker stalls of Malaysia and Singapore for street-style food, all freshly prepared with aromatic spices, herbs and ingredients. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit B2, University station MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2675, 'en_US', 'Café Post - Hotel Indigo Hong Kong Island', 'From Western and Chinese go to a popular food of Asian taste.', 'Roasted pork chop with potato ball, Mini Wagyu burger with french fries, British Afternoon Tea', '', 'Our very own Café Post on the 2nd floor offers an all day cafe menu combining a continental taste with a touch of local flavour. Cosy and comfortable, the intimate space smacks of diverse Wan Chai neighbourhood. Its alfresco lounge area is directly opposite to the Old Wan Chai Post Office that captures the contagious spirit of local history. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit A3, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2676, 'en_US', 'Cuisine Cuisine - The Mira Hong Kong', 'A upscale, modern Chinese eatery offering the finest Cantonese and Chinese delicacies, with a unique contemporary twist.', 'Poached spotted garoupa with taro, celery and mushrooms, Steamed crab claw with black truffles on winter melon, Steamed lobster with egg white, sea urchin and fish roe', '', 'Set against sleek modern interiors designed by Charles Allem, on the 3rd floor of The Mira Hong Kong, Michelin recommended Cuisine Cuisine at The Mira showcases a dining experience that’s steeped in some of the most exacting Cantonese culinary traditions, serving top quality, authentic fare crafted by master chefs. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2677, 'en_US', 'Whisk - The Mira Hong Kong', 'Finest Contemporary European gastronomy in a relaxed, ambient environment.', 'Tagliolini with Bretagne lobster, Large king prawns with pan, fried crispy polenta and gazpacho, Crispy suckling pig with braised baby lettuce', '', 'While contemporary European classics demonstrate culinary craftsmanship with the finest meats and seafood enhanced by fresh and seasonal ingredients, the wine pricing allows patrons to enjoy the world’s most exquisite vintages for less than what they are available for in any other five star hotel gourmet restaurant in Hong Kong and across the region. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2678, 'en_US', 'Yamm - The Mira Hong Kong', 'We all like to be masters of our own meals. After all, why restrict yourself to choosing just one dish, when you could enjoy an explosion of flavours?', 'Yamm classic cheese burger Yamm, Lobster and scallop risotto, Grilled lamb chop', '', 'We all like to be masters of our own meals. After all, why restrict yourself to choosing just one dish, when you could enjoy an explosion of flavours? At Yamm, our award-winning buffets are testament to quality and fresh Boston Lobster deserves much of that glory. Whether it’s Tasmanian oysters, botan ebi shrimp or Iberico ham, it’s your right to choose. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2679, 'en_US', 'Celebrity Cuisine - Lan Kwai Fong Hotel', 'This luxurious dining in Hong Kong is a unique gastronomic experience that Lan Kwai Fong Hotel is delighted to offer.', 'Bird’s nest in chicken wing, Braised abalone with goose web in oyster sauce, Steam crab claw stuffed with minced shrimp', '', 'Awarded as Two Stars Michelin Restaurant in Hong Kong, Celebrity Cuisine is a cosy restaurant with 40 seats. Celebrity Cuisine offers luxury Cantonese dining on Hong Kong Island with the freshest A-list ingredients, handpicked by our Chief Chef - Chef Cheng – daily. His dishes are prepared with nostalgic gourmet cuisine and health in mind. This luxury dining in Hong Kong is a unique gastronomic experience that Lan Kwai Fong Hotel is delighted to offer. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit E1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2680, 'en_US', 'The Market - Hotel Icon', 'The Market\'s open kitchens serves international delights from antipasti to laksas to grilled beef.', 'Laksa, Hainanese Chicken Rice, Seafood Yakitori', '', 'Inspired by the iconic food markets of Asia and Europe, with their vibrant atmosphere and abundant fresh produce, Hotel ICON presents a restaurant unlike any other. The Market\'s open kitchens serve international delights from antipasti to laksas to grilled beef. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2681, 'en_US', 'Above & Beyond - Hotel Icon', 'Enjoy exquisitely prepared dim-sum and seasonal Cantonese cuisine together with vintage wines from our private collection.', 'Steamed coral crab with glutinous rice, Sweet, and, sour Iberian pork with red wine vinegar, Steamed lobster with egg white and black truffles', '', 'Welcome to Above & Beyond, a lounge for guests staying in either Club Rooms or Suites at our hotel in Tsim Sha Tsui. Located on our top floor with a Private Bar and amazing panoramic views of Hong Kong, Above & Beyond is indeed a place apart. Join us for an unforgettable cocktail at dusk and watch as the dazzling night world lights up before you.To start your day in style, enjoy the magnificent full, American breakfast on us - with everything from Asian specialities to international favourites - every morning. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2682, 'en_US', 'Ming Court - Langham Place Hotel Hong Kong', 'Michelin star Ming Court unlocks 21st century Cantonese culinary mastery, at its finest.', 'Pan, fried chicken skin with minced chicken and black truffle, Stir, fried shrimps with egg white, Stir, fried sliced giant garoupa stuffed with shrimp paste', '', 'Michelin star Ming Court unlocks 21st century Cantonese culinary mastery, at its finest. Profiling sophisticated contemporary cuisine crafted by Ming Court’s culinary talents, Ming Court’s innovative, authentic flavours offer an elevated dining experience. Located on level 6, Ming Court’s two distinctive dining areas, Ming Sun and Ming Moon, are perfected by modern décor profiling a fascinating collection of replica Ming Dynasty pottery as well as ink landscape paintings by leading contemporary Chinese artists. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E1, Mong Kok MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2683, 'en_US', 'THE PLACE - Langham Place Hotel Hong Kong', 'Their medium is the finest, freshest ingredients jetted in daily from around the world.', 'Ice, cream, Oyster, Pancake', '', 'Boasting a 7-metre-high ceiling and splendid garden area complete with waterfalls and tropical plants, The Place offers scrumptious international specialties such as Paella, Tandoori and Hainannese Chicken Rice are prepared at the various open-kitchen cooking stations. Each of our chefs is a master artist, adept in culinary creativity. Their medium is the finest, freshest ingredients jetted in daily from around the world. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E1, Mong Kok MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2684, 'en_US', 'Tokoro Robatayaki and Sushi Bar - Langham Place Hotel Hong Kong', 'The charismatic chefs star in this robatayaki-style theatre restaurant on level 3, creating Japanese food with flair in an energetic atmosphere.', 'Homemade minced chicken, US rib, eye steak, Deluxe Sushi', '', 'The charismatic chefs star in this robatayaki-style theatre restaurant on level 3, creating Japanese food with flair in an energetic atmosphere. Revel in the spirit of Roppongi for an entertaining lunch or dinner.Enjoy an intimate meal at our robatayaki bar or sushi bar. Join a larger group in our intriguing designer pods, or reserve one of three private rooms for your special occasion. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E1, Mong Kok MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2685, 'en_US', 'AVA Restaurant Slash Bar - Hotel Panorama by Rhombus', 'Enjoy panoramic harbour views, cocktails and lounge beats in a contemporary setting.', 'Boston Lobster, Fried Scallop, Tender Beef Shoulder', '', 'AVA Restaurant Slash Bar, located on the 38th floor of Hotel Panorama by Rhombus, serves modern international cuisine with the finest seasonal ingredients, and an extensive list of international wines, champagnes, and creative cocktails. With stunning 270° Victoria Harbour views, the award-winning AVA Restaurant Slash Bar is the ultimate venue to unwind over Happy Hour and enjoy exciting new flavours, stylish private events, socialising, and networking. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit N1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2686, 'en_US', 'Cafe Express - Hotel Panorama by Rhombus', 'Whether you are in a rush or would like to leisurely enjoy a relaxing meal, Café Express will have something for you.', 'Alaskan crab legs, Grilled Swiss cheese －Swallows\' nest with Egg white', '', 'Café Express located on the lobby level, is our informal all-day restaurant providing you with buffet breakfast, lunch, dinner or à la carte menu. Whether you are in a rush or would like to leisurely enjoy a relaxing meal, Café Express will have something for you. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit N1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2687, 'en_US', 'FINDS Restaurant & Bar - The Luxe Manor', 'Our stylish interiors offer a variety of social environments that suit every mood, all day, every day.', 'House, smoked salmon fillet, Nordic seafood platter, Salmon in six ways', '', 'FINDS, Hong Kong’s first and only Nordic seafood restaurant and bar with award winning cuisine by Finland celebrity chef Jaakko Sorsa and exciting molecular mixology cocktails. Nordic cuisine is western food, prepared with ingredients of Nordic countries and typical European techniques including smoking, curing and pickling. Seafood is an important part of the cuisine as the people are surrounded by sea and lakes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2688, 'en_US', 'CUCINA - Marco Polo HongKong Hotel', 'The interactive dining, bar and cocktail areas and the outdoor seating provide you different options for private parties and special occasions.', 'Fassona beef tartare, Umbria black truffle, Modena 25 years old balsamic vinegar, Home, made truffle fettuccine, Wagyu beef ragout, shaved black truffle, Oven cooked cod fillet, citronella, lemon cress, creamy coconut sauce', '', 'Showcasing truly authentic Italian cuisine, Cucina offers a contemporary lifestyle venue for an exquisite culinary experience against a backdrop of the spectacular Victoria Harbour. The interactive dining, bar and cocktail areas and the outdoor seating provide you different options for private parties and special occasions. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit L6, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2689, 'en_US', 'Shang Palace - Kowloon Shangri-La Hotel', 'The delicious food, ornate décor and friendly staff make dining here a truly wonderful and memorable experience.', 'Braised Bird’s Nest with Pumpkin Cream, Japanese, style, Crispy Lobster with Oatmeal, Oven Baked Cod Fillet with Egg White and Conpoy', '', 'The Michelin two-star Shang Palace has opened after an extensive but thoughtful renovation. The \"new\" restaurant now proudly presents an elevated level of wining and dining with a host of brand new and upgraded facilities. Shang Palace serves Cantonese specialities that evoke the grandeur of traditional China. The delicious food, ornate décor and friendly staff make dining here a truly wonderful and memorable experience.', '2-min walk from Exit P1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2690, 'en_US', 'Nadaman Japanese Restaurant - Kowloon Shangri-La Hotel', 'The master chefs at Nadaman serve up fresh and innovative Japanese dishes.', 'Omakase kaiseki, Simmered fresh Kinki fish from Hokkaido, Deluxe Selection of Sashimi', '', 'The master chefs at Nadaman serve up fresh and innovative Japanese dishes. Guests can choose to dine in the elegant main room or get close to the chefs at the teppanyaki grill and sushi bar.For discreet business meals or family gatherings, the restaurant offers comfortable private rooms, including a private teppanyaki room and a tatami room.', '2-min walk from Exit P1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2691, 'en_US', 'Angelini - Kowloon Shangri-La Hotel', 'Angelini delivers stylish Italian cuisine in a down-to-earth and informal atmosphere.', 'Home, made candy pasta with mascarpone, 24, month aged Parmigiano Reggiano cream and confit tomato, Hokkaido scallops on taleggio cream and truffle pearl, Lobster with marinated tomatoes, red onions and basil with Dijon mustard essence', '', 'Angelini delivers stylish Italian cuisine in a down-to-earth and informal atmosphere. Set against the breathtaking backdrop of Victoria Harbour and Hong Kong\'s skyline, the restaurant serves a wide range of dishes using only the best quality ingredients. The lunch menu provide 20 appetizer and there are eight of the main course selection.', '2-min walk from Exit P1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2692, 'en_US', 'Café Kool - Kowloon Shangri-La Hotel', '“Heavenly international breakfast spread”－Café Kool serves a diverse international buffet with an array of Asian, Western and Indian cuisines.', 'Prime rib eye steak with grilled tomato, sautéed onions, grilled portobello mushroom, béarnaise sauce, Hainanese chicken with fragrant rice and broth, Apple walnut strudel with vanilla ice, cream', '', 'Café Kool serves a diverse international buffet with an array of Asian, Western and Indian cuisines, including salads, pastas, desserts and fruit. The dynamic open-kitchen divides into six stations, each showcasing the quality of ingredients that go into every dish. An all-day à la carte menu is also available.', '2-min walk from Exit P1, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2693, 'en_US', 'Three on Canton - Gateway Hotel', 'Three on Canton is the ultimate gourmet destination where your lifestyle is celebrated with a trilogy.', 'Fondant au chocolat, Hainanese Chicken Rice, Lobster Mango Salad', '', 'Three on Canton is the ultimate gourmet destination where your lifestyle is celebrated with a trilogy. Dine, wine and be all you can be at Three on Canton.Experience the tempting selections of the world’s most popular cuisines, charge up a hip night at the lounge and bar, unwind at the most vibrant al fresco dining space, or bring your private parties to the wine room and four exclusive function rooms. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2694, 'en_US', 'Feast (Food by EAST) - EAST Hotel, Hong Kong', 'Serving cuisine with the freshest ingredients, you can expect to enjoy tasty breakfast, lunch, afternoon tea and dinner from Feast.', 'Alaskan King Crab, Lobster Bisque Risotto, Chargrilled Dry, aged Steaks 280g ribeye', '', 'Feast(Food by EAST) is our big, bustling café on the first floor. Brimming with authentic Asian specialties and international favourites, our philosophy is \'simple things, done well\'. Guests can expect to enjoy tasty breakfast, lunch, afternoon tea and dinner from Feast. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit D1, Tai Koo MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2695, 'en_US', 'Café on M - InterContinental Grand Stanford Hong Kong', 'Chefs of Café on M bring out authentic tastes that will please the palate.', 'Japanese Robatayaki and tempura, Fresh oysters, Seafood Bar', '', 'Café on M takes all-day dining to an engaging level giving guests a whole new experience. Food is prepared in cooking theatres where guests can see the chefs take centre stage and cook with flair and fervour. One can hear the sizzle as you delight in a tapestry of colours and enjoy the aroma as food is served fresh to your table. Our chefs will prepare culinary delights and mouth-watering desserts right in front of you, offering you an experience that will satisfy all your five senses. With influences found throughout the world, our chefs bring out authentic tastes that will please the palate. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit D1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2696, 'en_US', 'Hoi King Heen - InterContinental Grand Stanford Hong Kong', 'Hoi King Heen is recognised as one of Hong Kong’s finest Chinese restaurants specialising in Cantonese cuisine.', 'Steamed garoupa rolls with Yunnan ham, Braised beef brisket stuffed in pear, Three tastes tofu in fortune bag', '', 'Hoi King Heen is recognised as one of Hong Kong’s finest Chinese restaurants specialising in Cantonese cuisine. Celebrity Master Chef Leung Fai Hung uses refined Chinese cooking methods combined with the best ingredients and top quality seasonal products.With the warm earth tones and tastefully done islands of red and gold, the restaurant is designed to redefine the essence of traditional Cantonese fine-dining, Each of the five private rooms has been tastefully decorated to offer the most quintessential of VIP Chinese dining experiences. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit D1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2697, 'en_US', 'Mistral - InterContinental Grand Stanford Hong Kong', 'Mistral preparing innovative dishes using only the freshest ingredients flown in from Italy.', 'Tagliatelle with antichokes and Sicilian red prawn, Sautéed baby squid with marinated zucchini and tomatoes, Handmade ravioli with buffalo mozzarella and smoked tomatoes', '', 'Rediscover the truly distinctive Italian Cuisine at Mistral and embark on a new culinary adventure with our Italian Chef, Samuele Baudoino, preparing innovative dishes using only the freshest ingredients flown in from Italy. The friendly, attentive and professional service team can offer advice and recommendations on wine selection from our award winning wine list, recognised by Wine Spectator. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit D1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2698, 'en_US', 'City Art Restaurant - Royal Park Hotel', 'Let the stylishly contemporary design of the restaurant with a touch of elegance and coziness be a prelude to an unforgettable experience.', 'Lobster bisque, Oyster', '', 'Located on the 2nd floor, strikingly stunning is our oasis of European culinary delights - City Art Restaurant. Let the stylishly contemporary design of the restaurant with a touch of elegance and coziness be a prelude to an unforgettable experience as you meander down the dazzling aisle of crystal chandeliers. An innovative yet engaging dining experience awaits… (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A3 , Sha Tin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2699, 'en_US', '2+2 café - Royal Park Hotel', 'An elegant and spacious café with a modern and stylish decor, 2+2 café offers outstanding international buffet with cuisine from the East and the West.', 'Tom yum goong, Chocolate fountain', '', 'An elegant and spacious café with a modern and stylish decor, 2+2 café offers outstanding international buffet with cuisine from the East and the West for breakfast, lunch and dinner. For more personalized service, an a la carte menu is also available from morning till late. The adjoining Coffee Corner offers gourmet snacks and coffee in a more relaxed setting. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A3 , Sha Tin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2700, 'en_US', 'Sakurada Japanese Restaurant - Royal Park Hotel', 'Renowned for its authentic Japanese cuisine, Sakurada offers a wide selection of sushi and washoku specialties.', 'Assorted Selection of Sashimi, Teppanyaki lamb chop with mixed vegetables', '', 'Renowned for its authentic Japanese cuisine, Sakurada offers a wide selection of sushi and washoku specialties in addition to live teppanyaki demonstration performed by our talented Japanese chefs. Enjoy the traditional Japanese ambiance, comfortable seating and first-class service. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A3 , Sha Tin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2701, 'en_US', 'Royal Park Chinese Restaurant - Royal Park Hotel', 'Royal Park Chinese Restaurant court to quality Cantonese and seafood dishes famous in Sha Tin.', 'Peppers with fresh abalone, Black pepper, mustard and curry goose, Foie gras with goose meat roll', '', 'Royal Park Chinese Restaurant court to quality Cantonese and seafood dishes famous in Sha Tin, is the ideal choice for a dinner or party. More offers fine dim sum and all kinds of business packages at lunch time. Also has a few VIP rooms, suitable for small business meetings or a Chinese banquet. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A3 , Sha Tin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2702, 'en_US', 'Man Ho Chinese Restaurant - JW Marriott Hotel', 'Featuring a contemporary table setting and decor for the finest authentic Cantonese cuisine.', 'Deep, fried crab claw with shrimp mousse, Roast chicken with fermented bean curd sause, Double, boiled fish maw soup with sea whelk and chicken', '', 'Man Ho Chinese Restaurant located on the 3rd floor of the Marriott Hotel, which is award-winning restaurant, features a contemporary table setting and decor for the finest authentic Cantonese cuisine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2703, 'en_US', 'Flint Grill & Bar - JW Marriott Hotel', 'Experience exceptional dining in a cutting-edge industrial, chic setting at Flint Grill & Bar.', 'Six Point Berkshire Black Pork Chop, Nebraska 63, day dry, aged on the bone (rib, eye 20, ounce), Seafood Skewer', '', 'Experience exceptional dining in a cutting-edge industrial, chic setting at Flint Grill & Bar. Enjoy pre-dinner drinks at the stunning arrival bar and lounge, featuring an array of iconic cocktails and specialty drinks to start off the evening or complement your meal with a choice of exquisite wines from the bespoke sommelier\'s table. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2704, 'en_US', 'Fish Bar and Grill  - JW Marriott Hotel', 'Fish Bar offers fresh fish recipes to bring you an extraordinary experience.', 'Seafood Tower, Crumb, fried calamari with marinara dip, Nicoise salad with blackened yellow fin tuna', '', 'A hidden oasis, Fish Bar on the 7th floor, offers fresh fish recipes. Serving daily fresh catch and seafood selections in a stylish alfresco–setting. Enjoy signature cocktails at the trendy Pool Lounge.  \"daily specials\" and refreshing drinks are a must carte dishes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2705, 'en_US', 'Le Chef - Metropark Hotel Wan Chai', 'Chef team\'s creativity and Le Chef’s ‘East meets West’ approach to fine dining.', 'Galician Rubia Gallega beef txuleton, Chargrilled snow crab leg, BBQ octopus with paprika and Spanish organic potato purée', '', 'Being located on the mezzanine floor, our signature fusion award-winning restaurant, Le Chef, features a menu crafted to showcase some of the best ingredients sourced from around the world, as well as Chef team\'s creativity and Le Chef’s ‘East meets West’ approach to fine dining. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2706, 'en_US', 'Dynasty Restaurant - Renaissance Harbour View Hotel', 'Dynasty restaurant creates delightful lifestyle destination for unique dining experience set against the backdrop of Victoria Harbour.', 'Barbecued pork, Fresh crab claw steamed with parsley and preserved egg or deep, fried in spicy salt, Braised whole abalone in oyster sauce', '', 'Showcasing authentic Cantonese cuisine, Dynasty, the award-wining Chinese restaurant in Wan Chai, creates delightful lifestyle destination for unique dining experience set against the backdrop of Victoria Harbour. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit A5, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2707, 'en_US', 'Cafe Renaissance - Renaissance Harbour View Hotel', 'Café Renaissance is the perfect place for all-day dining with a wide range of international food selections.', 'Lobster & asparagus in champagne sauce with Linguini, Fresh oysters, Grilled Australian lamb cutlets', '', 'Café Renaissance is the perfect place for all-day dining with a wide range of international food selections. Located on the Mezzanine floor, the 210-seat café serves breakfast, lunch and dinner buffets plus à la carte menu daily and brunch on weekends. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit A5, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2708, 'en_US', 'ToTT\'s and Roof Terrace - The Excelsior Hong Kong', 'Alfresco dining with exhilarating views of Victoria Harbour and the stunning Hong Kong skyline.', 'Japanese, style yellowfin tuna salad, mirin dressing, shaved fennel, Roasted Organic Duck Breast, Pan Fried Foie Gras, Autumn Vegetables, Red Wine Sauce, Corn Fed Chicken Autumn Casserole, Roasted Vegetables, Mushrooms and Sausage, Mashed Potato', '', 'Alfresco dining with exhilarating views of Victoria Harbour and the stunning Hong Kong skyline Enjoying a stunning location on our 34th floor, TOTT’s and Roof Terrace offers a unique combination of indoor and outdoor modern European dining. With ingredients sourced from around the world, our talented culinary team brings you a menu brimming with contemporary flair and international flavours. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2709, 'en_US', 'Yee Tung Heen   - The Excelsior Hong Kong', 'Bringing the finest authentic Cantonese cuisine to Hong Kong, Yee Tung Heen sets new standards for Chinese cooking.', 'Braised Beef Ribs in Chef\'s Special sauce, Braised Rice with Crab Meat and Spring Onion, Sweet and Sour Shredded Eel and Bamboo Piths stuffed with Fish Maw and Jin Hua Ham in Pumpkin Sauce', '', 'Bringing the finest authentic Cantonese cuisine to Hong Kong, Yee Tung Heen sets new standards for Chinese cooking Using only the most refined Chinese cooking methods combined with the best ingredients, Yee Tung Heen has created a wonderful menu of seasonal Cantonese specialties and much-loved favourites. Having won numerous praise and awards, the restaurant’s enticing menu perfectly illustrates the culinary team’s sophisticated techniques in crafting authentic Cantonese cuisine with modern flair. In particular, the lunchtime dim sum offerings are famous throughout Hong Kong and not to be missed. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2710, 'en_US', 'Cammino - The Excelsior Hong Kong', 'Authentically delicious Italian cuisine in a stunning contemporary setting.', 'Sardine Toast, Baked Seabass in ‘Cartoccio’, Grilled veal shank with saffron risotto and tomato, gremolata', '', 'Authentically delicious Italian cuisine in a stunning contemporary setting. Our light and healthy a la carte menu features many traditional favourites including antipasto, fresh pasta and risotto. In addition, we offer a range of mouth-watering signature dishes from different regions of Italy including linguine with scampi, crayfish and green asparagus in white wine sauce, and grilled veal cutlet with rosemary. On weekdays, we serve a popular semi-buffet lunch with an appetizer buffet. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2711, 'en_US', 'Azure Restaurant Slash Bar - Hotel LKF by Rhombus', 'Azure’s unique ambience is further enhanced by our international chefs, who proudly feature their ever changing modern cuisine.', 'Azure Caesar salad, Iberico pork rack, Fresh lemon linguini', '', 'The famed Azure Restaurant Slash Bar, located on 29th and 30th floors of the hotel, has been bestowed numerous honours. Guests can step out onto our patio to experience the open fresh air and amazing views of Central while enjoying a glass of wine or a cocktail. Azure’s unique ambience is further enhanced by our international chefs, who proudly feature their ever changing modern cuisine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D1, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2712, 'en_US', 'Promenade Restaurant   - Harbour Plaza Metropolis', 'Promenade Restaurant offers spectacular harbour views with the sumptuous international a la carte dishes.', 'King Crab, Scallops and assorted octopus vegetables salad', '', 'Indulge in a divine array of Asian and Western cuisines, feast on a magnificent range of buffets or afternoon tea on weekends, Promenade Restaurant offers spectacular harbour views with the sumptuous international a la carte dishes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit D2, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2713, 'en_US', 'Senzuru Japanese Restaurant   - Harbour Plaza Metropolis', 'Senzuru Japanese Restaurant, where you can savour all your favourite Japanese dishes and try a daily selection of seasonal items from Japan.', 'Teppanyaki Shrimp with Crab York Cream Sauce, Mini Diced Sashimi Rice Bowl Set', '', 'Senzuru Japanese Restaurant, where you can savour all your favourite Japanese dishes and try a daily selection of seasonal items from Japan. To suit your every need, Senzuru features a sushi & sashimi counter, teppanyaki tables and also two private rooms with karaoke to celebrate your special occasions. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit D2, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2714, 'en_US', 'Di King Heen - Royal Plaza Hotel', 'Di King Heen, brings you a moveable feast from pure Cantonese cuisine to tasty delicious Dim Sum.', 'Perch with pine nuts and daisy, Distilled matsutake giant grouper soup, Candied with barbecued black pork', '', 'When it comes to contemporary Chinese cuisine, the newly renovated Chinese restaurant, Di King Heen, brings you a moveable feast from pure Cantonese cuisine to tasty delicious Dim Sum. The freshest, most succulent ingredients are selected to cater to both casual dining and banquets. Three well appointed VIP rooms are available for small gatherings. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B2, Prince Edward MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3272, 'en_US', 'La Scala  - Royal Plaza Hotel', 'Known throughout Hong Kong as having one of the finest hotel buffets, La Scala features a wide range of international cuisines.', 'Iced Boston Lobster, Braised Oxtail in Red Wine, Stewed Lamb Shank in Italian style', '', 'Known throughout Hong Kong as having one of the finest hotel buffets, La Scala features a wide range of international cuisines. The spacious restaurant offers both a comfortable uncluttered dining area as well as an open kitchen. Conveniently located in Mongkok, whether a family gathering or an intimate dinner, La Scala will satisfy any appetite. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B2, Prince Edward MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3273, 'en_US', 'Stables Grill - Hullett House', 'Stables Grill is the perfect place to soak up the ambience of old Hong Kong and enjoy casual dining .', 'Grilled USDA prime sirloin, Margherita, Lobster linguini', '', 'Nestled inside the old horse stables of Hullett House with views over the House’s white-stucco colonnades dating from 1881 and its sweeping lawns, Stables Grill is the perfect place to soak up the ambience of old Hong Kong and enjoy casual dining expertly presented by the culinary team. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit L5, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3274, 'en_US', 'St. George - Hullett House', 'St. George is Hullett House’s signature fine dining restaurant, serving contemporary French cuisine within the historical former Marine Police Headquarters.', 'Blue lobster, Chocolate, banana, chocolate sponge', '', 'St. George is Hullett House’s signature fine dining restaurant, serving contemporary French cuisine within the historical former Marine Police Headquarters. Its refined setting brings contains reflections of Hong Kong’s British influences. The cuisine at St. George entices diners with the best of modern French flavours in an intimate setting made expressly for long, relaxed dinners and lunches. Guests have the option to indulge in five- or eight-course tasting menus, or order a selection from the St. George à la carte menu. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit L5, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3275, 'en_US', 'Loong Toh Yuen  - Hullett House', 'Loong Toh Yuen revives long-lost Hong Kong dishes and offers a comprehensive selection of classic dim sum and Chinese tea.', 'Stir, fried shrimps with oatmeal, Barbecued pork with honey, Deep, fried shrimp rolls stuffed with thousand, year egg', '', 'Loong Toh Yuen is Hullett House’s signature Chinese dining restaurant. Embodying elements of old Hong Kong teahouse culture and King George IV chinoiserie in its inspired décor, Loong Toh Yuen revives long-lost Hong Kong dishes and offers a comprehensive selection of classic dim sum and Chinese tea. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit L5, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3276, 'en_US', 'The Parlour   - Hullett House', 'The Parlour is a glamorous and grand chinoiserie lounge that is the perfect place to entertain visitors or simply to indulge oneself.', 'Surf and Turf, Seared whole Boston lobster', '', 'The Parlour is a glamorous and grand chinoiserie lounge that is the perfect place to entertain visitors or simply to indulge oneself. The day starts with English breakfast, followed by luncheon and afternoon tea. In the evenings, romantic dinner and exotic cocktails are the order of the day. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit L5, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3277, 'en_US', 'Sha Tin 18 - Hyatt Regency, Sha Tin', 'The best Chinese restaurant serving authentic Dongguan and northern Chinese cuisine in a lively show kitchen environment.', 'Traditional Peking duck, Houjie pan, fried fish cake with Chinese dried sausage, Tossed mustard greens with beancurd sheet and shallots', '', 'Named after the hotel\'s street address number \"18\" which also means good fortune in terms of Feng Shui, Sha Tin 18 is a new concept for Hong Kong, and perhaps the best Chinese restaurant serving authentic Dongguan and northern Chinese cuisine in a lively show kitchen environment. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B, University MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3278, 'en_US', 'Cafe - Hyatt Regency, Sha Tin', 'Cafe at Hyatt Regency Hong Kong, Sha Tin hotel consists of a lounge, main dining area, a private dining room, and a spacious outdoor terrace for alfresco dining.', 'Grilled Lamb Rack, Grilled Beef', '', 'Cafe at Hyatt Regency Hong Kong, Sha Tin hotel consists of a lounge, main dining area, a private dining room, and a spacious outdoor terrace for alfresco dining. The show kitchens present exciting buffets featuring Hong Kong’s favourite steamed and wok-fried dishes; seasonal salads and refreshing seafood on ice; freshly baked pizza and pastas; as well as prime meat grilled a-la-minute. No meal is complete at this Shatin restaurant without trying the freshly made desserts and baked pastries, with seasonal fruits and ice creams from the dessert kitchen. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B, University MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3279, 'en_US', 'Harbour Grill - Harbour Grand Kowloon', 'Sweeping views combine with fine dining in a relaxed, harbour view setting where premium quality beef features on an ever-evolving menu of seasonal dishes and foie gras.', 'French Seafood Soup, Goose Liver with Fennel and Caramel Black Pepper Sauce, Lobster and Beef Set', '', 'Sweeping views combine with fine dining in a relaxed, harbour view setting where premium quality beef features on an ever-evolving menu of seasonal dishes and foie gras. Our extensive wine list is as impressive as the lights on Victoria Harbour. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '15-min walk from Exit B1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3280, 'en_US', 'Hoi Yat Heen - Harbour Grand Kowloon', 'The tastes of Canton and the views of modern Hong Kong & Victoria Harbour unite to create a memorable Chinese dining experience.', 'Crispy boneless chicken wing stuffed with shark\'s fin, Saut\'eed sliced pork with pear and black vinegar, Roasted pork belly', '', 'The tastes of Canton Province and the views of modern day Hong Kong and Victoria Harbour unite to create a memorable Chinese dining experience. A highlight of your afternoon will be our succulent dim-sum specialties. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '15-min walk from Exit B1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3281, 'en_US', 'Robatayaki Japanese Restaurant   - Harbour Grand Kowloon', 'Experience rustic décor, traditional charm and freshly grilled produce at Robatayaki.', 'Hokkaido taraba crab, Cod fish, Matsuzaka sirloin steak (250g)', '', 'Experience rustic décor, traditional charm and freshly grilled produce at Robatayaki. Robatayaki features rooms lined with old-world oak. Traditional Japanese barbecue is skillfully prepared by master chefs on open grills. Sushi, sashimi and a selection of fine sake round off every meal. A private VIP room seats 20 and is perfect for private gatherings. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '15-min walk from Exit B1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3282, 'en_US', 'Waterfront Bar & Terrace - Harbour Grand Kowloon', 'Waterfront Bar & Terrace is the perfect place to unwind with friends and family for lunch, dinner or drinks.', 'Sea scallops, shrimp, squid, mussels tomato and lobster sauce, Pizza Diavola, Pizza prosciutto di Parma', '', 'Offering a cosy and relaxed setting with gourmet delights, Waterfront Bar & Terrace is the perfect place to unwind with friends and family for lunch, dinner or drinks. Live broadcast of English Premier League is available with happy hour offers, every Saturday and Sunday according to the broadcasting schedule. Patrons can also enjoy free Wi-Fi upon consumption. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '15-min walk from Exit B1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3283, 'en_US', 'The Promenade - Harbour Grand Kowloon', 'It also boasts additional live-cooking stations and a quality selection of seafood.', 'Mango Napoleon, Braised Abalone with Oyster Sauce, Roast Prime Rib of Canadian Beef', '', 'The Promenade offers fabulous views over Victoria Harbour. Lined with floor to ceiling harbour view windows, marble flooring and plush seating creating an opulent venue. It also boasts additional live-cooking stations and a quality selection of seafood. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '15-min walk from Exit B1, Hung Hom MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3284, 'en_US', 'ALTO 88 - Regal Hongkong Hotel', 'The restaurant serves contemporary Italian favourites and a host of innovative dishes which are masterly made by our Italian Chef.', 'Pan, seared scallop, burrata cheese and dehydrated Parma ham, Red tuna and green apple tartare served with yogurt sauce, Pan, seared black cod, liquorice and sweet garlic sauce', '', 'Alto 88, formerly known as the Italian restaurant Zeffirino, the restaurant serves contemporary Italian favourites and a host of innovative dishes which are masterly made by our Italian Chef. Come and enjoy an awe-inspiring experience and stunning views of Victoria Harbour and the park beyond. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
