(3292, 'en_US', 'Regal Terrace - Regal Riverside Hotel', 'Come and savour Guangdong or Canton at Regal Terrace.', 'Baked king scallop with herbs and butter, Streamed fresh abalone with dried mandarin peel and cordyeeps flower, Baked green mud crab with vermicelli in casserole', '', 'Culture is defined by people\'s beliefs, language, music, art, history. A closer look at what they eat and drink, tells you even more. Regal Terrace provide Guangdong authentic traditional dishes, Select for top and fresh ingredients, perfect for guests to bring a new sense of taste and visual enjoyment. Come and savour Guangdong or Canton at Regal Terrace. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '11-min walk from Exit C, Sha Tin Wai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
