(3296, 'en_US', 'Avanti Pizzeria   - Regal Riverside Hotel', 'Avanti Pizzeria is serving authentic Italian culinary delight.', 'Pan, fried pancetta and chicken rolls, Lipari fried seafood served in basket, Linguine with king prawns in garlic and chili', '', 'Avanti Pizzeria is serving authentic Italian culinary delight. Lavishing Cheese, Juicy Tomatoes, Fresh Basils, Crunchy Thin Dough... altogether releases true Italiano pizzas from our Italian pizza oven. Hot and Crispy! And more than 7 choices of Spaghetti and over 30 Italian Starters, Salads, Hot Soups, Grilled & Roasted and Desserts! (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '11-min walk from Exit C, Sha Tin Wai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3297, 'en_US', 'Riva and the deck - The Park Lane Hotel', 'The à-la-carte menu from our Executive Chef is a memorable culinary experience.', 'Low, temperature, roasted Lamb Rack, Steamed Chilean sea bass', '', 'Contemporary dining restaurant with an outdoor deck perched on the 27th floor, offers sumptuous contemporary cuisine matched with an equally impressive cellar of new and old world wines and rare vintages. The à-la-carte menu from our Executive Chef is a memorable culinary experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3298, 'en_US', 'Cafe One - The Park Lane Hotel', 'From the Buffet Breakfast through the Lunch Buffet to the Late Night Buffet, there is a menu and a range of choices.', 'Salmon Salad, Fondant au chocolat, Lobster', '', 'Cafe One offers buffet and a la carte service daily. From the Buffet Breakfast through the Lunch Buffet to the Late Night Buffet, there is a menu and a range of choices. Cafe One offers a Lunch and dinner Buffet with a choice of seven exciting options - a Salad Bar, Seafood Bar, Indian Selections, Western Flavours, Chinese Flavours, Sweet Ones, or Congee & Noodle. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3299, 'en_US', 'Café Neo - Regal Oriental Hotel', 'Café Neo offers both Asian and Western fare featuring Kowloon City’s legendary Hong Kong favorites.', 'Char, grilled rib, eye steak, Hainese Chicken Rice', '', 'Café Neo offers both Asian and Western fare featuring Kowloon City’s legendary Hong Kong favorites. The café is a perfect venue for family dining or friend’s social gatherings, providing diners with delightful surprises including games and special celebrations every evening. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', 'Take bus 46, 49, 69, 69A, 105 and 105S to Regal Oriental Hotel bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3300, 'en_US', 'Regal Terrace - Regal Oriental Hotel', 'The Chinese restaurant is renowned for its masterful art in Cantonese Culinary.', 'Lobster in two flavors: sauteed lobster meat with egg white and crab roe & rice in lobster soup, Sautéed Scallops with Fresh Yam and Vegetables, Deep, fried Crispy Beef Brisket', '', 'Regal Terrace located in Regal Oriental Hotel, Kowloon City, mainly provides Cantonese cuisine. The Chinese restaurant is renowned for its masterful art in Cantonese Culinary. Experience the delights from the choice of classic dim sums to Chinese delicacies. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', 'Take bus 46, 49, 69, 69A, 105 and 105S to Regal Oriental Hotel bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3301, 'en_US', 'The China Coast Pub + Restaurant - Regal Oriental Hotel', 'The China Coast Pub + Restaurant is the only American pub and restaurant in Kowloon East.', 'The prime signature Angus, Signature Angus and Goose liver burger, Penne with Porcini mushroom and Pomodoro sauce', '', 'The China Coast Pub + Restaurant is the only American pub and restaurant in Kowloon East specializes on a wide selection of burgers complimented by classic American sized dishes featuring signature milkshakes and a global selection of beers. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', 'Take bus 46, 49, 69, 69A, 105 and 105S to Regal Oriental Hotel bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3302, 'en_US', 'Kitchen - W Hotel', 'From the gorgeous views, to the culinary masterpieces, this is how we define our KITCHEN.', 'Prime canadian beef, Bali yellowfin tuna', '', 'Indulge your taste buds with our wow-worthy buffets and their revolving array of culinary creations accented with local and exotic global flavours. Don\'t miss our \"Legendary Sunday Brunch\" buffet with cocktail and live stations, while epicurean classics and famed favourites grace an à la carte menu that will surprise and satisfy even the most seasoned gourmand.This modish bistro boasts a brilliant buffet as well as international and pan-Asian à la carte fare. With a live view of our amazing chefs on one side, and a stunning panorama of West Kowloon Harbour on the other, KITCHEN is also a feast for the eyes. From the gorgeous views, to the culinary masterpieces, this is how we define our KITCHEN. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3303, 'en_US', 'Sing Yin  - W Hotel', 'Sing Yin offers authentic Cantonese cuisine highlighted by flawless dim sum, traditional delicacies and an unmatched selection of the freshest seafood plates.', 'Steamed crab claw with ginger wine, Wood, fired crispy chicken, “Budda jump over the wall” pot', '', 'Situated on W Hong Kong\'s first floor, Sing Yin offers up authentic Cantonese cuisine highlighted by flawless dim sum, traditional delicacies and an unmatched selection of the freshest seafood plates. The brainchild of world-renowned architect and interior designer Steve Leung, this 120-seat restaurant embodies the classic features of Hong Kong electrified streets. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3304, 'en_US', 'Hoi Yat Heen Chinese Restaurant - Harbour Plaza North Point', 'Expect to sample delights from Canton, Sichuan, Shanghai and Yunnan province.', 'Fried King Prawns with Chinese Shao Xing Wine, Sauteed Diced Beef, Mango and Asparagus, Braised Whole Abalone in Oyster Sauce', '', 'The elegant Hoi Yat Heen Chinese Restaurant had been honoured Silver Award in the Dim Sum Category in “Best of the Best Culinary Awards” by the Hong Kong Tourism Board. Our chefs bring their own artistry to bear in both traditional and modern creations. Expect to sample delights from Canton, Sichuan, Shanghai and Yunnan province. Remember to book in advance for special occasions. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit C, Quarry Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3305, 'en_US', 'Greens Cafe - Harbour Plaza North Point', 'Greens Café offers an extensive all day international menu and serves the most generous food in town.', 'Grilled US Angus Beef Fillet, Wild Mushroom Risotto, Tomato and Mozzarella Cheese Salad with Pesto Sauce', '', 'Greens Café offers an extensive all day international menu and serves some of the most generous breakfast, lunch and dinner buffets in town. The comfortable contemporary décor makes this restaurant a popular choice for families and groups. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit C, Quarry Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3306, 'en_US', 'Le Cafe - Novotel Century Hong Kong,', 'The open kitchens of Le Café revolutionizing the culinary experience, and creating a truly interactive restaurant.', 'Fresh oysters, Chocolate Fountain, Seafood Teppanyaki', '', 'The open kitchens of Le Café set this international buffet restaurant a level above the rest, revolutionizing the culinary experience, and creating a truly interactive restaurant. The linear, modern furniture harks back to the quiet stillness of a bamboo forest, and is accented beautifully by the innovative kitchen and accessories. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3307, 'en_US', 'Pepino Italian Restaurant - Novotel Century Hong Kong,', 'Come to Romantic Pepino restaurant to enjoy customized modern Italian cuisine.', 'Strip Loin Steak, Risotto', '', 'Come to Romantic Pepino restaurant to enjoy customized modern Italian cuisine, just like going to a restaurant to have a tea-time, all dishes can be order to create your own package, everything depands on you! The entire package can match with your own random order fully meet your unique taste! (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3308, 'en_US', 'Osteria Ristorante Italiano   - Holiday Inn Golden Mile Hong Kong', 'The dishes are  full of flavour and promise to transport your palate to the various regions of Italy for a truly traditional culinary experience.', 'Liguria, style octopus salad, green beans, potatoes, basil pesto, Mum’s lasagna bolognese with old fashion beef ragout in chunks, Venetian tiramisu made with Lavazza espresso', '', 'Timeless Italian specialties are what Osteria is all about. The dishes are authentically crafted, inviting, full of flavour and promise to transport your palate to the various regions of Italy for a truly traditional culinary experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit H, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3309, 'en_US', 'Casa Pennington - Hotel pennington by rhombus', 'Casa Pennington is the ideal place for food connoisseurs, and for friends and family to share an enjoyable time.', 'Pear Tarte Tatin, Sea Urchin Liniguini', '', 'Its innovative cuisine is fresh and rich in taste, ranging from seasonal oysters and seafood, exclusive fine wines, and desserts from around the world. Known for outstanding customer service, Casa Pennington ensures you will have a memorable fine dining experience.Casa Pennington is the ideal place for food connoisseurs, and for friends and family to share an enjoyable time. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3310, 'en_US', 'W\'s Entrecôte  - Express by Holiday Inn Causeway Bay', 'Charbroiled ribeye steak, with W\'s unique herbal butter sauce is perfect match.', 'Grilled Beef Rib Eye Steak, Grilled Lamb Steak', '', 'Simply the Best ! As those who know this homely restaurant are fond of saying, you can order anything you like, as long as it is steak. And it is true.... almost. Open the main menu and all you will find is charbroiled ribeye steak, which the French call Entrecôte, with W\'s unique herbal butter sauce. The steak is served in a choice of three sizes, with French green salad topped with W\'s vinaigrette and walnut, and as many fries as you can eat. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3311, 'en_US', 'Xin Dau Ji (Causeway Bay Branch) - Express by Holiday Inn Causeway Bay', 'Xin Dau Ji strives to serve authentic, traditional Cantonese cuisine, and prides itself for its sincere, responsive and friendly service.', 'House Special Roasted Suckling Pig, House special soya pigeon, Chiu chow style, Tiger prawns in soya sauce', '', 'Xin Dau Ji strives to serve authentic, traditional Cantonese cuisine, and prides itself for its sincere, responsive and friendly service, outstanding dishes and exquisite dim sum. Our first shop in Jordan was awarded a Michelin star in 2012-2013 for its outstanding food and service. The restaurant is famous for its signature roasted suckling pig, of which delicately sliced meat comes with a reasonable amount of fat, flavourful taste and crispy skin. The crispy and juicy deep fried fish fillet in sweet cream of corn dressing is also an unregrettable choice. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3312, 'en_US', 'Xin Dau Ji (North Point Branch) - The South China Hotel', 'Xin Dau Ji strives to serve authentic, traditional Cantonese cuisine, and prides itself for its sincere, responsive and friendly service, outstanding dishes and exquisite dim sum.', 'House Special Roasted Suckling Pig, House special soya pigeon, Chiu chow style, Tiger prawns in soya sauce', '', 'Xin Dau Ji strives to serve authentic, traditional Cantonese cuisine, and prides itself for its sincere, responsive and friendly service, outstanding dishes and exquisite dim sum. Our first shop in Jordan was awarded a Michelin star in 2012-2013 for its outstanding food and service. The restaurant is famous for its signature roasted suckling pig, of which delicately sliced meat comes with a reasonable amount of fat, flavourful taste and crispy skin. The crispy and juicy deep fried fish fillet in sweet cream of corn dressing is also an unregrettable choice. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit A1, North Point MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4316, 'en_US', 'Wada Japanese Restaurant (North Point Branch) - The South China Hotel', 'Wada is the paradise for sashimi and the Japanese beer lovers, you must try peony shrimp sashimi.', 'King shrimp sashimi, Japanese tempura, Peony shrimp sashimi', '', 'Wada Japanese Restaurant located on the 2nd floor of Java Road, North Point, South China Hotel, served Japanese-style buffet, featuring provide tiger shrimp sashimi, this sort of sashimi which is rare in Hong Kong, but also the Japanese beer unlimited supply. If you are sashimi and the Japanese beer lovers, there will be your paradise. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit A1, North Point MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4317, 'en_US', 'Nishimura Restaurant - Marco Polo HongKong Hotel', 'With freshest Japanese food ingredient and the traditional Japanese cooking style, Nishimura restaurant caters the finest Japanese cuisine.', 'Sole Fish Edge Sushi, Deluxe Nishimura sushi set meal', '', 'Established by Mr. Hiromi Nishimura (西村弘美先生) in 1985, Nishimura Restaurant has been renowned for the best sushi and sashimi in town. He uses every freshest Japanese food ingredient which copes with his super traditional Japanese cooking style, caters the finest Japanese cuisine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit L6, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4318, 'en_US', 'Yat Tung Heen (Kowloon Branch) - Eaton Hong Kong', 'Yat Tung Heen our Brigade of highly skilled Chefs using only the best ingredients, ultimately in creating a taste to savour.', 'Honey, glazed barbecued pork, Simmered prawns with vermicelli in clay pot, Braised pork apareribs in brown sauce', '', 'Named as one of the Eight Great Culinary Traditions of China, Cantonese cuisine is renowned for its superior quality. And at Yat Tung Heen our Brigade of highly skilled Chefs work day and night to exemplify that quality by insisting on using only the best ingredients, ensuring the dishes are beautifully and elegantly presented, ultimately in creating a taste to savour. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B1, Jordan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4319, 'en_US', 'Metro Buffet & Grill - Eaton Hong Kong', 'Having an exciting buffet dining experience in Metro Buffet & Grill where our chefs display their cooking talents in a lively open kitchen.', 'Satay sauce grilled whole squid, Fried curry crab, Assorted Satay string', '', 'The 80 seat Metro Buffet & Grill offers you smart, modern design featuring stainless steel and marble buffet and grill counters and an exciting buffet dining experience where our Brigade of Chefs display their cooking talents in a lively, interactive show kitchen. It will keep you coming back with its wide selection of local and international buffet favourites served for breakfast, lunch and dinner along with an extensive a la carte menu and wine list. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B1, Jordan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4320, 'en_US', 'Yagura Japanese Restaurant  - Eaton Hong Kong', 'As one of Kowloon\'s most renowned hotspots for relaxed Japanese dining, Yagura serves a high quality creative menu of sushi, tempura and izakaya style dishes.', 'Deluxe selection of sashimi, Australian M5 Wagyu, Wagyu foie gras maki rolls', '', 'Literally translated from old Japanese Yagura means \"tower\" or \"turret\" which embodies the design of this stylish Japanese hotspot. Izakaya restaurants became popular in Japan among businessmen looking to relax over good food and drinks. They are now one of the country\'s most popular type of casual eatery. As one of Kowloon\'s most renowned hotspots for relaxed Japanese dining, Yagura serves a high quality creative menu of sushi, tempura and izakaya style dishes, all designed to be shared. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B1, Jordan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4321, 'en_US', 'The Window Cafe - The Kowloon hotel', 'It offers an expansive international and a la carte menu as well as breakfast, lunch, afternoon tea, dinner and even a supper buffet.', 'Fettuccine with Mushroom and Truffle Sauce, Mesclun Salad with Mango and Crab Leg Meat in Thousand Island Dressing, Braised Veal Osso Bucco with Vegetable in Red Wine Sauce Served with Saffron Risotto', '', 'The Window Café overlooks the famous \"Golden Mile\" of shops along Nathan Road with dramatic floor-to-ceiling glass walls. It offers an expansive international and ala carte menu as well as breakfast, lunch, afternoon tea, dinner and even a supper buffet. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L4, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4322, 'en_US', 'Loong Yat Heen - The Kowloon hotel', 'You can enjoy Dim Sum and classic Chinese delicacies including abalone, shark\'s fin as well as fresh seafood in Loong Yat Heen.', 'Sautéed Crystal Prawn, Steamed Fresh Crab Claw with Winter Melon, Braised Goose Web with Pomelo Peel', '', 'Welcome to Loong Yat Heen, where you can enjoy Dim Sum and classic Chinese delicacies including abalone, shark\'s fin as well as fresh seafood. Ready to serve business lunches, banquets and all meals with style from our experienced chefs. The restaurant also features two private rooms to cater for intimate lunch or dinner gatherings. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit L4, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4323, 'en_US', 'Crystal Lotus  - Hong Kong Disneyland Hotel', 'Try the seasonal chef’s recommendations for the freshest and most arresting flavors.Disney Dim Sum only available at Crystal Lotus.', 'Peking Duck, Baked crab with pumpkin, Red bean with osmanthus flowers cake', '', 'Tour the 4 major culinary regions of China—Sichuan, Beijing, Shanghai and Guangdong—at this award-winning restaurant. This rich legacy of epicurean excellence blossoms into unforgettable premium dishes like top-quality seafood, poultry and barbecued specialties. Try the seasonal chef’s recommendations for the freshest and most arresting flavors. Our master dim sum chefs have dreamed up a whimsical assortment of Disney Dim Sum that are only available at Crystal Lotus. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', 'Disneyland Resort MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4324, 'en_US', 'Enchanted Garden Restaurant - Hong Kong Disneyland Hotel', 'Indulging in a sumptuous buffet overgrown with Victorian elegance and meet some of your favorite Disney Characters!', 'Sashimi, Sushi', '', 'Indulge in a sumptuous buffet overgrown with Victorian elegance and meet some of your favorite Disney Characters! The delectable dinner buffet also offers fresh seafood dishes, like our succulent crab legs. For dessert, Enchanted Garden Restaurant blooms with a sweet harvest of cakes, cookies, pudding and fresh fruit dipped in our twin chocolate fountains—one with milk chocolate and one with white chocolate. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', 'Disneyland Resort MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4325, 'en_US', 'Walt\'s Cafe - Hong Kong Disneyland Hotel', 'Feel the romance of the bygone Victorian era, as you savor delicious dishes that pay tribute to Walt Disney.', 'Egg linguine with slow, cooked veal fillet, Tempting Bombay butter chicken, Baked Boston lobster thermidor', '', 'Feel the romance of the bygone Victorian era, as you savor delicious dishes that pay tribute to Walt Disney. Invite your family and friends to relax with appetizing food, outstanding service and genteel Victorian décor—including soothing cream-colored walls, dark wood molding, gleaming brass highlights and ornate antique chandeliers. Gaze out the window and take in the sweeping view of the Hong Kong Disneyland Hotel gardens and the South China Sea. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', 'Disneyland Resort MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4326, 'en_US', 'Cafe on the 1st - The Excelsior Hong Kong', 'All-day dining to take your breath away. Café on the 1st offers creative cuisine and spectacular harbour views.', 'Deep, fried Chicken Pieces with Chili and Salt, Hainan Chicken Rice, Raspberry Chocolate Truffle', '', 'All-day dining to take your breath away. Café on the 1st offers creative cuisine and spectacular harbour views. Enjoying breathtaking views of Hong Kong’s famous Victoria Harbour, our relaxed all-day dining restaurant is one of the hotel’s most popular venues. Offering guests a choice of creative à la carte menus, a buffet and delicious desserts in a friendly atmosphere, there really is something for everyone. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit E, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4327, 'en_US', 'Café East\n - New World Millennium Hong Kong Hotel', 'Café East combines the best Western and Asian dishes for a comprehensive à la carte menu.', 'fondant au chocolat', '', 'Located on the first floor, Café East combines the best Western and Asian dishes for a comprehensive à la carte menu. Delivering a refreshing ambience with views of the world-famous Victoria Harbour on one side, this casual-eatery/café serves a lavish buffet breakfast and a delightful lunch and dinner. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4328, 'en_US', 'Tao Li - New World Millennium Hong Kong Hotel', 'Presenting authentic Cantonese cuisine, Tao Li is the perfect choice for a true taste of Hong Kong.', 'Osmanthus honey with barbecued black pork, Braised Tsui Yuk Melon Stuffed with Minced Shrimp, Whole Abalone and Bird’s Nest Topped with Pumpkin Sauce', '', 'Winning the “Best of the Best Culinary Award”  given by the Hong Kong Tourism Board, Tao Li is a celebrated restaurant offering an elegant selection of Cantonese fare and dim sum that combines traditional flavours with originality. Located on the second floor with 180 seats and five private rooms, the restaurant can be converted to a large function room for private and corporate gatherings. Presenting authentic Cantonese cuisine, Tao Li is the perfect choice for a true taste of Hong Kong (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4329, 'en_US', 'Sagano   - New World Millennium Hong Kong Hotel', 'Inspired by a famous suburb of Kyoto, Sagano offers an authentic Japanese dining journey.', 'Kaiseki Ryori', '', 'Inspired by a famous suburb of Kyoto, Sagano offers an authentic Japanese dining journey. Using bamboo and wood as core design elements, the restaurant presents a modern interpretation of traditional Kyoto style, both simple and elegant. Worthy of particular mention are the six VIP rooms, one of which is a tatami room with traditional bamboo flooring. Here, dining is no longer just about food, but a complete cultural experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4330, 'en_US', 'La Table - New World Millennium Hong Kong Hotel', 'La Table offers an exquisite à la carte menu with an extensive selection of gastronomic pleasures.', 'Chocolate tart', '', 'La Table offers an exquisite à la carte menu with an extensive selection of gastronomic pleasures. Featuring a VIP room, the French eatery provides an ideal venue for private parties of up to 10 persons. A wide selection of fine wines can be found in the impressive glass-encased wine cellar, where discerning diners can pair food with the most compatible vintages. A show-cooking area with a full-length glass wall makes for a charming dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit P2, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4331, 'en_US', 'Harbour Grand Café\n - Harbour Grand Hong Kong', 'Harbour Grand Café offers casual all-day a la carte dining and a lavish buffet selection, serving the best of international cuisine.', 'Pan fried goose liver, Boston Lobster, Fresh Oyster', '', 'Harbour Grand Café offers casual all-day a la carte dining and a lavish buffet selection, serving the best of international cuisine. Enjoy breakfast, lunch or dinner in a relaxing and refreshing environment by the poolside overlooking the Victoria Harbour.Offering you a wide range of options, our dinner buffet provides you with surprises from pan fried goose liver to crab legs, oysters and lobsters. We are also proud to present you a wide selection from Chinese, Western, Indian and Thai. Round up your meal with an array of heavenly sweets and12 types of Mövenpick ice cream. Harbour Grand Café is your choice for fresh exquisite food that tantalise your taste buds. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
