(4333, 'en_US', 'Lychee Garden Chinese Restaurant\n - Metropark Hotel Mongkok', 'Lychee Garden Chinese Restaurant famous to blend the local cuisine including fresh seafood and dim sum and other prime Guangdong dishes.', 'Gold medals roasted chicken, Shrimp ball with cashew sause, Honey flavor rib', '', 'Lychee Garden Chinese Restaurant famous to blend the local cuisine including fresh seafood and dim sum and other prime Guangdong dishes, located on the first floor of Metropark Hotel Mongkok , offers 8 banquet rooms, to meet the needs of the business and private parties. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B2, Prince Edward MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4334, 'en_US', 'Cafe du Parc - Metropark Hotel Causeway Bay', 'The combination of stylish decor with impeccable hotel service provides the perfect place to meet and dine at any time of the day.', 'Canadian crab legs, Grilled seafood, Fresh shrimps', '', 'Designed open, interactive kitchen which helps bring an innovative and dynamic concept to your dining experience. Our menu features fusion food along with international favourites. The combination of stylish decor with impeccable hotel service provides the perfect place to meet and dine at any time of the day. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B, Tin Hau MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4335, 'en_US', 'YUE -  City Garden Hotel', 'Intimate and inspiring, the Michelin-starred YUE serves authentic Cantonese dishes, Hong Kong delicacies and traditional dim sum.', 'Wok, fried Wagyu beef cubes with garlic chips, Barbecued eel with honey, glazed, Sauteed scallops with asparagus and wild mushrooms in X.O. sauce', '', 'Intimate and inspiring, the Michelin-starred YUE serves authentic Cantonese dishes, Hong Kong delicacies and traditional dim sum. While the private rooms are ideal for business talks, you can celebrate a special occasion or impress a date at the award-winning restaurant, which can welcome over 220 guests. Choose from a tempting list of the chef’s recommended dishes, including Seared Star Garoupa Fillet with Fish Maw on Egg White with Truffle Sauce. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4336, 'en_US', 'Garden Cafe -  City Garden Hotel', 'Garden Café offering a sumptuous buffet selection of pan-Asian and Western dishes which are exclusively available.', 'Japanese Salmon and tuna tartar, Lobster bisque with crab meat, Barbecued pork spare ribs with crispy fries', '', 'Garden Café guests can look forward to a relaxed setting and creative cuisine at this all-day dining venue. Offering a sumptuous buffet selection of pan-Asian and Western dishes, Garden Café also delights diners with an eclectic selection of over 50 types of bottled craft beers and snacks which are exclusively available. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4337, 'en_US', '沙嗲軒   \n -  City Garden Hotel', 'Guests don’t have to travel to Singapore or Malaysia to sample their unique cuisines.', 'Chilli crab, Signature Hainanese chicken rice, Chicken, beef or pork satay', '', 'Guests don’t have to travel to Singapore or Malaysia to sample their unique cuisines. Satay Inn is the go-to venue in Hong Kong for authentic Singaporean and Malaysian dishes. The selection includes a range of much-loved classics, from Hainanese chicken rice and bak kut teh to satays and laksa. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4338, 'en_US', '沙嗲軒   \n - Hong Kong Gold Coast Hotel', 'Enjoy authentic Singaporean and Malaysian cuisine at Satay Inn.', 'Chilli crab, Signature Hainanese chicken rice, Chicken, beef or pork satay', '', 'Enjoy authentic Singaporean and Malaysian cuisine at this popular local restaurant. Offering alfresco dining, guests can surround themselves with lush greenery, experience the invigorating sea breeze and choose from a menu of all-time favourites, including Hainanese Chicken Rice, Hokkien Prawn Mee and Fried Carrot Cake. Satay Inn is also at our sister properties, The Royal Pacific Hotel & Towers and City Garden Hotel. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Golden Beach Bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4339, 'en_US', 'YUE - Hong Kong Gold Coast Hotel', 'YUE presents traditional Cantonese delicacies with a modern twist.', 'Wok, fried Wagyu beef cubes with garlic chips, Barbecued eel with honey, glazed, Sauteed scallops with asparagus and wild mushrooms in X.O. sauce', '', 'Selected in the MICHELIN guide Hong Kong Macau 2014 and 2015, YUE presents traditional Cantonese delicacies with a modern twist. While guests are welcome to dine outdoors to enjoy the surrounding greenery, casual mood and sea views, our private booths provide an intimate setting for romantic dinners, small gatherings or family get-togethers. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Golden Beach Bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4340, 'en_US', 'Cafe Lagoon - Hong Kong Gold Coast Hotel', 'Cafe Lagoon entices with a tranquil setting, alfresco dining and a tantalising buffet selection of pan-Asian favourites, signature Hong Kong dishes and Western cuisines.', 'Charcoal roasted duck, Frozen seafood dish, Thai, style chicken wings.', '', 'Cafe Lagoon entices with a tranquil setting, alfresco dining and a tantalising buffet selection of pan-Asian favourites, signature Hong Kong dishes and Western cuisines. While the floor-to-ceiling windows invite natural light in, Cafe Lagoon’s seating extends outdoors to surround the pool. Offering all-day buffets, an a la carte menu and freshly barbecued dishes, Cafe Lagoon is a feast for the senses. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Golden Beach Bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
