(4342, 'en_US', 'Pierside Bar & Restaurant - The Royal Pacific Hotel & Towers', 'Waterfront view of the Hong Kong skyline make Pierside Bar the venue of choice for a pre-dinner drink, after-hour cocktail or a memorable dinner with friends.', 'Roasted Australian king size tomahwak steak (40 oz.) with seasonal vegetable & beef jus, Pierside seafood platter', '', 'Sleek and chic interiors, coupled with waterfront view of the Hong Kong skyline, make Pierside Bar the venue of choice for a pre-dinner drink, after-hour cocktail or a memorable dinner with friends. Known for its market-fresh seafood, the menu celebrates the simplicity of genuine flavours and traditional cooking styles. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit F, Austin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4343, 'en_US', 'Café on the PARK  - The Royal Pacific Hotel & Towers', 'Enjoy a sumptuous buffet selection and views overlooking buzzing Tsim Sha Tsui at this trusted Hong Kong restaurant.', 'Seafood Robatayaki in Japanese Style, Canadian Blue Mussels, Alaskan Snow Crab Claw', '', 'Enjoy a sumptuous buffet selection and views overlooking buzzing Tsim Sha Tsui at this trusted Hong Kong restaurant. With its interactive cooking stations, selection of pan-Asian and Western cuisines and full-length windows welcoming natural light, Café on the PARK boasts rich flavours and a welcoming setting.Open daily for breakfast, lunch and dinner, guests can indulge in the bountiful buffet or choose from the a la carte menu. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit F, Austin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
