(4346, 'en_US', 'Sonata Western Restaurant - Rosedale Hotel Kowloon', 'Sonata Western Restaurant offers a lively atmosphere and inviting menu of creative dishes.', 'Seafood buffet', '', 'Sonata Western Restaurant offers a lively atmosphere and inviting menu of creative dishes throughout breakfast, lunch and dinner as well as room service menus. Imaginative and tantalizing Western and Asian cuisines as well as other special international themes are served in both a la carte menus and buffet styles. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit C5, Olympic MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2715, 'en_US', 'L\'Atelier de Joel Robuchon', 'L\'ATELIER de Joel Robuchon offers a variety of French classic dishes.', 'Thick Sliced Wagyu Beef Sirloin, Free, range quail with foie gras, served with mashed potato, Caramel Custard', '', 'Awarded three Michelin stars for 3 consecutive years, L\'ATELIER de Joel Robuchon offers a variety of French classic dishes. The restaurant is designed with a circular bar enveloping an open kitchen, allowing customers to witness how chef turns fresh ingredient into fabulous dishes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2716, 'en_US', 'Ambrosia Oyster Bar & Grill', 'Featuring an extensive variety of freshly imported oysters from all over the world including France, Australia, USA and Japan', 'Oyster, Charcoal Grilled 12oz US Charcoal Grilled 12oz US Sirloin, Linguine Boston Lobster with Cherry Tomatoes & Basil Infuse', '', 'Featuring an extensive variety of freshly imported oysters from all over the world including France, Australia, USA and Japan, Ambrosia Oyster Bar & Grill also highlights authentic continental cuisines and charcoal grilled steaks from USA, Australia and Japan. The exclusive 270° panoramic harbour views also give a romantic touch to the night scenery. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit H, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2717, 'en_US', 'Teppanyaki Kaika', 'Kaika Teppanyaki always take diners in wonder with teppanyaki dishes with meticulously curated.', 'Grilled Kinki Fish with Herb Olive Sauce, Baked Top Shell with Butter Herb Sauce, Teppan Miyzaki Gyu(beef)', '', 'Having been recommended in the Macau and Hong Kong Michelin Guide 2014, Kaika Teppanyaki always take diners in wonder with teppanyaki dishes, premium Japanese beef, sushi along with meticulously curated collection of sake. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2718, 'en_US', 'Kanizen', 'Epitomises the Japanese aesthetic of crab cuisine in a cozy and intimate ambiance.', 'Taraba crab leg tempura, Matsuba crab sashimi, Japan Hokkaido Hairy Crab', '', 'Kanizen epitomises the Japanese aesthetic of crab cuisine in a cozy and intimate ambience. With the choice of sushibar-style, couch table as well as private dining rooms, indulge in the most exclusive Japanese crab cuisine in Hong Kong.At Kanizen, you can order Red King Crab, Queen crab and hairy crab at all seasons. Our restaurant also have a 2*4M crab aquarium, conserve fresh crab. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2719, 'en_US', 'Liberty Private Works', 'The unique 26 seat layout that surrounds the French open kitchen provides an unpretentious and cozy dining experience.', 'Tuna Sea Urchin Espelette Rice, Egg truffle Parmesan caviar, Mochi with Condensed Milk', '', 'The unique 26 seat layout that surrounds the French open kitchen provides an unpretentious and cozy dining experience. Both the Tasting Menu and Wine Pairing is ever-changing based on the Chefs inspirations and his interpretations of seasonal ingredients.LPW makes accommodations for food allergies and dietary restrictions with prior notice.Award winning chef Vicky Cheng leads a team of dedicated professionals, to ensure each and every one of our 26 guests enjoy a unique and personal experience at the “Chef’s Table”. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2720, 'en_US', 'Wa San Mai', 'Design concept of Japanese concise fashion, divided to Teppanyaki, Japanese-style hot pot, Sushi Bar and Leisure area.', 'Saga Beef Wagyu, Hot, plate Abalone, Foie Gras', '', 'Design concept of Japanese concise fashion, Wa San Mai divided in four part, Teppanyaki, Japanese-style hot pot, Sushi Bar and Leisure area. Chef\'s consummate skill let diners feel deeply enjoy about the dish. You can enjoy the intoxicating views of Victoria Harbour when you dine in our restaurant. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit D2, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2721, 'en_US', 'Sevva', 'SEVVA deliver a unique and quintessentially Hong Kong dining experience inspired by ‘the DNA’ of Hong Kong– traditional regional Asian cuisines intermixed with Western fine dining.', 'Crunch Cake, High Tea, Lemon Meringue', '', 'Pronounced ‘Savour’, meaning to experience a taste, SEVVA will deliver a unique and quintessentially Hong Kong dining experience inspired by what Gokson describes as ‘the DNA’ of Hong Kong– traditional regional Asian cuisines intermixed with Western fine dining, coupled with her own travels and experiences. SEVVA will be located at the top of Central’s designer shopping mall, Prince’s Building - suitably positioned to enjoy stunning 360 degree views over Hong Kong’s breath-taking skyline and the prime heart of the city. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit K, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2722, 'en_US', 'Inakaya', 'Inakaya, as the traditional ‘Robata-yaki’ restaurant, has been loved by substantial numbers of distinguished personalities.', 'Teppanyaki Goose Liver, Teppanyaki Wagyu Beef Roll, Sea Urchin Sushi', '', 'Our original restaurant in Japan was established and opened its first door in the heart of Roppongi, Tokyo in 1970, as the traditional ‘Robata-yaki’ restaurant. Since then, Inakaya has been loved by substantial numbers of distinguished personalities, comprising of former President of the United States, renowned politicians, Hollywood star, and other celebrities and the epicureans from around the world for more than 40 years. ‘Robata’ is the Japanese term that stands for ‘around a sunken hearth’ and ‘yaki’ means ‘grilling’. Families used to gather around the hearth for dinner, which evolved into ‘Robata-yaki’ style. It is known as a type of traditional cuisine, which features fresh ingredients grilled in proximity of guests’ own eyes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2723, 'en_US', 'Amigo', 'Classic continental décor styles Hong Kong\'s noble France restaurants', 'Napoleon, Fish chowder, Foie gras', '', 'Hong Kong\'s noble France restaurants, its classic continental décor styles, with lot of display around the world, including paintings and antique furnishings, you can feel the exotic, like exposure to the sixties and seventies, romantic atmosphere. Restaurants pay attention to the guest’s privacy, also attracted many celebritie to visit. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Wong Nai Chung Road trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2724, 'en_US', '8½ Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA', '8 ½ Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA taken care of every detail from kitchen to interior design to ambience and menus.', 'Homemade Tagliolini (butter and parmesan, \"melanosporum\" black truffle), Seasonal Green Vegetables, Braised Beef Tongue, Manjari Chocolate Mousse', '', '“The King of White Truffles”, Executive chef Umberto Bombana, returned to the limelight with a new heartfelt, personal ristorante 8 ½ Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA in Central’s Landmark Alexandra. Bombana delight the gourmet palate with his unique, sophisticated yet and contemporary culinary creations. Located in the second floor of Landmark Alexandra, the restaurant occupies a total of 4,700 square feet space. Overlooking the famous bustling street view of Chater Road, the spacious main dining room can accommodate up to 55 pax, while the two delightfully-decorated private dining rooms can sit 12 guests each. The great chef ’s commitment to delight his guests delivering only the best Italian cuisine using the freshest ingredients is even more enhanced at 8 ½ Otto e Mezzo BOMBANA, for which he has taken care of every detail from kitchen to interior design to ambience and menus. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit H, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2725, 'en_US', 'Sushi Fuku-Suke', 'Sushi Fuku-Suke provides the highest quality sashimi and sashimi with using the best possible ingredients.', 'Japanese Beef Sashimi, Premium Assorted Sashimi, Omakase', '', 'Sushi Fuku-Suke on behalf of blessing from sushi. The store provides the highest quality sashimi and sashimi with using the best possible ingredients. Design concept of Japanese style and the cypress wood sushi station, bring you the exclusive Japanese restaurant style, just like dining in japan. Sushi Fuku-Suke ship fresh seafood to Hong Kong every day, make you can eat the freshest seasonal sashimi and sushi. Let customer can enjoy the dinner. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit D2, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2726, 'en_US', 'The Principal', 'The Principal\'s, provide the finest dishes with both traditional and innovative .', '63º Egg, Chocolate Mousse, Suckling Pig', '', 'Fine dining often conjure images of austere surroundings, immaculate table settings, and luxurious but minuscule portions. The experience can be gratifying for your palette, but may not be where you want to just sit back and relax.Walk through the understated entrance of The Principal (the esteemed Press Room Group\'s only fine dining concept) and you may just be pleasantly surprised to find an elegant, yet relaxed ambience with a mix of rustic, warm wood tones and modern, contemporary design. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2727, 'en_US', 'Tate Dining Room & Bar', 'Tate, provide a truly inspired dining experience by french & japanese dishes.', 'Kagoshima Beef Tenderloin, Sakura Ebi Tagliolini, Honey, Milk & Chamomile', '', 'Tate, French & Japanese Restaurant.A truly inspired dining experience requires every facet of the service to be delivered to perfection. Sourcing only the best possible ingredients, infusing our quirky take on culinary expressionism to stimulate the sense of smell, taste, touch and sight. Make each customers visit a memorable encounter.At Tate we want our customer to enjoy more than just food that we provide, we want it to be an experience to remember whilst dining with us, we believe every dish should tell a story of its nature and concept, pulling all the senses together with culinary technics and conceptual plating.Tate\'s dining room offers an intimate and warm environment with cozy nooks that can be exclusively yours. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2728, 'en_US', 'BO Innovation', 'Bo London introduces Alvin’s signature cooking style, “X-treme Chinese” to the city, playing with ingredients and techniques with immeasurable precision.', 'MOLECULAR, Saga, Gyu Beef, har gau”black truffle', '', 'Bo London introduces Alvin’s signature cooking style, “X-treme Chinese” to the city, playing with ingredients and techniques with immeasurable precision and combining centuries old recipes with modern cooking methods. The self taught chef breaks down perceptions of traditional and regional Chinese food, taking his guests to the “X-treme” and hopes to revolutionise Chinese gastronomy, creating an entirely new dimension for his diners to explore.The menu at Bo London exemplifies Alvin’s ability to surprise. It will highlight not only favourite dishes from Bo Innovation in Hong Kong, but will also debut new culinary creations inspired. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit B2, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2729, 'en_US', 'Dragon Seal Restaurant & Bar', 'Dragon Seal belief is strives for we have tremendous passion & dedication in culinary arts.', 'Shark\'s Fin Mixed with Steamed Egg White, Poached Rice with Prawn Meat, Roasted Crispy Pork Cubes', '', 'Cooking is like living - always be considerate towards others \'needs \"Cooking requires from mind and heart\" said by Mr. Wong Wing Chee. Chee is adventurous and creative in blending new and rare ingredients in his cooking. Dragon Seal belief is strives for we have tremendous passion & dedication in culinary arts. \"Sourcing fresh ingredient from its origin\" – by eliminating the use of anti-decay agent and preventing contamination during food production and transportation. Attracted by the building\'s grand location and design, Dragon Seal boasts perfect positioning to its patrons to enjoy the spectacular views of Victoria Harbor and the magnificent fireworks displays, that are truly part of Hong Kong\'s must-see, for locals and tourists. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2730, 'en_US', 'Gin Sai Japanese Restaurant', 'The restaurant engage Japanese chefs with the Kyoto style mix with the modern style.', 'Assorted Tempura Platter, Scallop with Sea Urchin, Steamed Japanese Wagyu and Kurobuta Pork with Seasonal Vegetables', '', 'The restaurant engage Japanese chefs with the Kyoto style mix with the modern style. The environment designed as noble style with natural dark tone. The chef Ogawa prepare high quality Japanese food such as Seiromushi, which is very rare in Hong Kong. Guests sitting on the countertop can watch the chiefs prepare the Tempura and the Kantoni. Also, Yakitori are cooked with the Bincho charcoal behind the glass screen, such opened environment can let the guests observe the preparation of the food clearly. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A3, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
