(2736, 'en_US', 'Akita Crab Shabu Shabu Specialist', 'Akita Crab Shabu Shabu Specialist, the main product of Akita is king crab and snow crab', 'Queen crab Sashimi with rice, Kagoshima Berkshire, Hokkaido crab feast, Sapporo Teriyaki Queen crab with king crab', '', 'Schools of daily jet-flown live Hokkaido jumbo Taraba, Snow and Meat Crabs side by side with Alaskan King all displayed in specially designed chill pools and tanks for customers to choose while our chefs busy slicing top grade marble Kobe and Angus beef; hand-picking Chiba organic warm house vegetable artfully assigned on platters; traditional and imaginative boiling Shabu Shabu broths and sauces (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B2, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2737, 'en_US', 'ÉPURE', 'Revel in the joy of our French colonial atmosphere and exclusive dining experience.', 'Oyster, French tender chicken, A5 Wagyu Beef', '', 'You can sense the intimate aura of romance as you enter ÉPURE’s exquisitely painted surroundings complemented by our custom-made furniture.As you dine, revel in the joy of our French colonial atmosphere. Admire the large regency style mirrors laminated with gold metal mesh and vintage decorative wall sconces which add a final touch of glamour to your dining experience.The minute you sit down, you are transported to a forgotten time of French aristocracy. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit L5, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2738, 'en_US', 'SUSHI SASE', 'Sushi Sase, guarantees exceptionally attentive service.', 'Maguro Tataki with rice, Broiled toro, Red Miso Soup', '', 'Located on the junction of Hollywood Road and Graham Street in Central. Sushi Sase takes up the entire corner with its subtle light brown wooden exterior, causing most passerbys to take a second look. Once you enter through the automatic sliding door, the tranquil atmosphere continues. A large sushi bar, seating about 18 diners, takes up centre stage in the main dining room. The room itself is sparse when compared to other Japanese restaurants, with only two or three small tables occupying the rest of the spacious room.\nThe staff speaks in lowered tones and are knowledgeable, helpful and efficient. The best experience is to be had at the sushi counter where four sushi chefs cater to 18 diners, guaranteeing exceptionally attentive service. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit E2, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2739, 'en_US', 'Bibo', 'Bibo offers French “gastronomie gourmande”, where everything is home-made, from the bread to the ice cream.', 'Australian Wagyu beef bavette with cauliflower, almond pesto and beef jus, Roasted Guinea fowl breast, crushed ratte potatoes, garlic and parsley puree, Dover Sole', '', 'Enter into a world full of passion, energy and happiness, a place that brings the best of two worlds together: art and food. Discover the world of Bibo. This place got to be known as Bibo, a place where contemporary and street art converge from all corners of the world and where freedom of the senses is encouraged. It is a place that redefines understated luxury and gives a nod to bohemian lifestyle. A place with no restrictions, where people can be themselves and enjoy the simple pleasures of life with their friends, sharing good times, good food, good drinks, and art. Heading the culinary team is Executive Chef Mutaro Balde with Chef de Cuisine Conor Beach. Their menu at Bibo offers French “gastronomie gourmande”, where everything is home-made, from the bread to the ice cream. Behind the bar, mixologist Alexandre Chatté creates a menu of handcrafted cocktails from the forgotten classics of the 1930s. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '9-min walk from Exit E2, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
