(2743, 'en_US', 'Ryu Gin', 'Situated 101 floors of the ICC, first overseas branch of Ryu Gin', 'Charcoal, grilled kinki broth, Sashimi assorted cold dishes, RyuGin Specialty, 196 ℃ Candy Peach and +99 ℃ Peach Jam', '', 'As the first overseas restaurant of RyuGin Japan, Tenku RyuGin strives to recreate the Tokyo dining experience here in Hong Kong. Seasonal menus overseen by the founder chef Seiji Yamamoto are prepared under supervision of chef de cuisine Hideaki Sato. With high quality ingredients daily flown from Japan to Hong Kong, Tenku Ryugin strives to offer a traditional and unique Kaiseki cuisine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
