(2750, 'en_US', 'Hana Sakazuki Japanese Restaurant', 'Our mission is to serve our customers with the best and the most extensive collections of traditional Japanese cuisines.', 'Sashimi, Sushi, Teppanyaki', '', 'Our mission is to serve our customers with the best and the most extensive collections of traditional Japanese cuisines. Some of the seafood is exclusive to our restaurant and we can assure you that you will always want to come back to enjoy our unforgettable dishes. As one of the most reputable Japanese restaurants in Hong Kong, we have been featured on a number of television programms, such as TVB\'s \"Dining with the Stars. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
