(2753, 'en_US', 'One Thirty-One', 'Our restaurant is located in a 3 storey Mediterranean style house situated in one of the most beautiful parts of Sai Kung, our restaurant’s atmosphere is elegant and relaxed.', 'Obsiblue prawn, Petit fours, Salmon Appetizer', '', 'One-thirtyone will take your breath away. Our restaurant is located in a 3 storey Mediterranean style house situated in one of the most beautiful parts of Sai Kung. Reminiscent of a luxury European country retreat, our restaurant’s atmosphere is elegant and relaxed. Delectable contemporary European cusine is served in our honey toned dining room looking out onto the bay. one-thirtyone is the perfect place to relax and escape the hustle and bustle of the city, be it a leisurely lunch sipping champagne or taking in the sunset with a glass of wine before dinner. For those who want to make a grand entrance, the front lawn can accommodate small helicopter landings or there is a private dock for mooring your yacht. Fabulous setting, wonderful food and attentive service make our restaurant unique, our guests return again and again for romantic dinners, business entertainment, or simple get togethers with friends. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-10 min taxi from University station MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2754, 'en_US', 'Matsubishi Japanese Restaurant', 'Matsubishi dream is to bring the ultimate dining experience to our patrons, and this is achieved with our continued excellence in maintaining our authentic tastes and premium quality.', 'Japanese Set Meal“Pine”, Kabayaki, Grilled silver cod fillets with miso', '', 'Matsubishi dream is to bring the ultimate dining experience to our patrons, and this is achieved with our continued excellence in maintaining our authentic tastes and premium quality. Noh is a classical Japanese performance form which combines elements of drama, music and poetry into one highly aesthetic stage art and is unique in it\'s slow, spartan grace and it\'s use of distinctive masks. Glamorous expressed Noh\'s response and motion in the area regarding the Teppanyaki area as a Noh Stage and chefs as Noh actors.  So here is a new stage in the restaurant, guests will surely enjoy the performance. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2755, 'en_US', 'NUR Restaurant', 'Caring importance of variety and the details that affect the quality of produce.', 'Taiyouran egg with shitake mushroom bread, Home baked mushroom butter bread, Oyster', '', 'NUR Restaurant all began when Raymond Blanc walked through the door of the kitchen of London’s Claridge’s hotel, where I was working. He prepared a tomato dish which I tasted, nothing I ever tried managed to pack so much flavour, but was yet so light and balanced. Raymond taught me about the importance of variety and the details that affect the quality of produce. I came to deeply respect the food chain, and taught my guests all about nutrition and how to source food in a responsible fashion. The Inspiration was where I met Hong Kong born chef Richie Lin, who told me upon my return to London that a friend of his was looking to open an interesting restaurant in Hong Kong. That restaurant became NUR. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2756, 'en_US', 'Zurriola', 'ZURRIOLA offeres contemporary spanish dishes with rustic flair and sophisticated flavours.', 'one minute low, temperature cook Japan\'s mackerel, Seared Japanese branquillo, 36 hours slow cooked Lamb Loin', '', 'ZURRIOLA offeres contemporary spanish dishes with rustic flair and sophisticated flavours. The concept is inspired by ZURRIOLA Tokyo, 1 Michelin-starred restaurant with Japanese Chef Seiichi Honda contemporary menu of Spain cuisine. Hong Kong Shop is the first outlet overseas with a close emotional bond to the Tokyo. Our intention is coherence, to promote fine and avant-garde Spanish gastronomy, but with a unique ambiance and different design on menu. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2757, 'en_US', 'Amuse Bouche', 'Amuse Bouche is served as an excitement for the taste buds and a glimpse of the chef\'s cooking approach.', 'Baked Alaska crab leg, Pan fried Norwegian scallops, Home made duck pie', '', 'In traditional French cuisine, Amuse Bouche is served as an excitement for the taste buds and a glimpse of the chef\'s cooking approach. This complimentary canapé is not on the menu and served usually right after the order is taken. By choosing Amuse Bouche as the name of the restaurant, we would like to present our guests with a happy and amusing prelude to the perfect dining experience ahead. Accompanying the simple and comfortable interior decoration is the spectacular 270-degree view of the city. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit A3, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2758, 'en_US', 'Sushi Shin Japanese Restaurant', 'Omakase is the best. Fresh seafood with chef’s skill, is a work of art.', 'Tempura soba, Grill Anago sushi, Toro', '', 'Sushi Shin Japanese Restaurant is located in Tung Lo Wan Road, Tai Hang, The majority of diners choose sashimi and sushi platter. Sushi chef looks great with experience and skill. It is no wonder that a Japanese restaurant is hard to find a seat. One of the recommendations by the chef is their omakase, because only the chef knows what is the best. Fresh seafood with chef’s skill, is a work of art. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B, Tin Hau MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2759, 'en_US', 'Sushi Ginza Onodera', 'We pride ourselves in serving every guests with \"authentic taste\" and \"warm-hearted sushi\".', 'Toro, Foie Gras, Hokkaido hairy crab', '', 'We pride ourselves in serving every guests with \"authentic taste\" and \"warm-hearted sushi\". Our skilled sushi chef freshly crafts every piece of sushi in front of guests. Our sushi chefs hand pick the freshest seafood and ingredients daily, from the Tsukiji market and all over the world to provide our guests with the finest quality sushi. We strive to deliver the greatest experience for our guests with courteous service and seasonal dishes in relaxed environment with a Japanese cypress sushi bar and sophisticated furnishing. Our mission is to introduce the wonderful Japanese culture all over the world by presenting our traditional cuisine, sushi, in the most original style in major cities like Honolulu, Paris and Hong Kong. We hope to share our culture with you. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit C, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2760, 'en_US', 'Sushi Asahi', 'At Sushi Asahi, we devote in maintaining the traditional Japanese sushi dining experience.', 'Stone grilled wagyu beef, Fried cod fillet, grilled Kinki with salt', '', 'Sushi Asahi is an authentic sushi joint in the popular district of Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong. We believe that remarkable food starts with the best quality and therefore, we select the freshest seafood and ingredients from Japan. At Sushi Asahi, we devote in maintaining the traditional Japanese sushi dining experience. Reservations can be made for indoor dining, sushi bar dining, or outdoor patio lounging. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit D, Jordan Station\nMTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2761, 'en_US', 'Japanese Restaurant Shun Sai Tomi', 'Japanese Restaurant Shun Sai Tomi focuses on Japanese kaiseki.', 'Grilled silver cod fillets, Kaiseki Bento, Shrimp Cake', '', 'Japanese Restaurant Shun Sai Tomi focuses on Japanese kaiseki. The main emphasis are seasonal dishes, tableware, food placement and matching, utensils temperature, time, and serving food order. Owner Tomio Sato requires very regularly to make changes for meals, consistent in adding more elements. The restaurant’s goal is to make seasonal ingredients to create a material advantage of taste. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit N3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
