(2866, 'en_US', 'The Chop House', 'The star attraction of The Chop House, allowing you to freely pour your own beer while enjoying a delicious meal.', 'Chicken quesadillas, Soft shell crab club sandwiches, Beef shank', '', 'The Chop House focuses on serving the freshest ingredients around the world in an approachable way to target audience who craves for a casual yet unique dining experience. With floor-to-ceiling windows, an indoor dining area for tuck-away comfort, a semi-outdoor bar, and a spacious al-fresco area for a laid-back atmosphere, The Chop House portrays the best picture of a casual dining concept where guests can enjoy a good meal in a stress-free environment. Situated at the same location as Wooloomooloo Prime in Causeway Bay, The Chop House brings together simplicity and tantalizing cuisine, inviting guests to a relaxing destination that serves unpretentious flavors in high quality dishes. Hearty items on the menu are accompanied by an extensive selection of wines, crafted cocktails and artisan beers. The star attraction of The Chop House, the self-serve beer system, is available in both indoor and outdoor area – allowing you to freely pour your own beer while enjoying a delicious meal. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit B, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2867, 'en_US', 'Serenade Chinese Restaurant', 'Serenade Chinese Restaurant popularizes a “yam cha” culture with unique Cantonese Dim Sum and deli.', 'Baked Sea Whelk stuffed with Portugese Dressing, Flaming Prawns in Chinese Liquor, Pepper Bun', '', 'The Hong Kong Cultural Centre is one of Hong Kong’s premier points of interest, attracting both locals and tourists who admire its Victoria Harbour backdrop. Serenade is the only Cantonese restaurant at the Cultural Centre, offering visitors delicious Cantonese dishes. One of the trademarks here is the figurine dim sum, such as Goldfish Dumplings and Squid-shape Red Bean Bun, which are eye-catching and loved by many diners. Moreover, there are a number of irresistible awarded dishes like Deep-fried Bean Curd stuffed with Ham and Mushrooms, Baked Sea Whelk stuffed with Portugese Dressing and Flaming Prawns in Chinese Liquor. Visitors can enjoy a gastronomic experience, served with the metropolitan charm of Hong Kong. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit L6, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2868, 'en_US', 'Rice Paper', 'Rice Paper invites food lovers to taste the Vietnam and Thailand of today.', 'Soft shell Crab Rice Paper Rolls, Viet Raw Beef Noodle in Soup, French Kiss', '', 'Rice Paper invites guests to taste the Vietnam and Thailand of today. From authentic local dishes to those infused with hints of French and Western culinary. The abundant use of fresh herbs and vegetables for brilliant flavors, textures and colors; the fondness in char-grilling and wok-frying seafood and meat all accentuate the very essence of the two Southeast Asian regions. Rice paper believes a perfect dining experience comprises of great food, pleasant ambience and attentive service; and they are indeed the fundamental of every m.a.x. concepts restaurant. The restaurants deliver distinctive cuisines with innovative ideas. It has also brought internationally renowned restaurant chain Lawry’s the Prime Rib to Hong Kong. The interior design complements the menu with a French colonial atmosphere - relaxing, yet romantically elegant. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon Tong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2869, 'en_US', 'Thai Basil', 'Thai Basil is inclined to Northern Thailand where food is spicy and peppered with Thai herbs.', 'Wok Fried Thai Spicy Crab, Char, grilled King Tiger Prawn Curry, Sticky banana pudding', '', 'Experience the flavors of Northern Thailand where food is spicy and peppered with Thai herbs. Thai Basil restrains use of coconut milk accentuates the authentic sour and spicy taste to stimulate the palate. Cocktails are made with refreshing Thai herbs to compliment the food. Thai Basil is a restaurant line of Maxim’s Group, m.a.x. concepts has been diversifying its portfolio of characteristic restaurants since 1998. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2870, 'en_US', 'Pirata', '『Restaurant of true Italian taste』', 'Agnolitti”GrandmaPaolina” with beef ragu Pasta, Speckpiadina traditional “Emilia, Romagna” breads, Steaktartare', '', 'TheItalian restaurant “Pirata”, Servedby chef Stefano Rossi,Their dishes are true Italian taste, and the “uncompromising” quality and value.Coupled with friendly and personalized service style, and their passion for food, the guests have left a very deep impression. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A4, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2871, 'en_US', 'Cafe Deco', 'Offers a vast range of delicious Asian and Western dishes with most amazing views of Hong Kong.', 'Foie gras hand roll, Tandoori specialties, Grill & rotisserie', '', 'The menu of Cafe Deco offers a vast range of delicious Asian and Western dishes including tandoori specialties, pizzas, barbecue and roasted dishes, fresh pasta and jet-fresh Pacific and West-Coast oysters as well as Sushi. The restaurant with the most amazing views in the whole of Hong Kong has reopened its doors with a fresh and exciting new look. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '- The Peak Tram on Garden Road, Central\n- No 1 green mini bus from IFC minibus depot \n- No 15 The Peak bus from Exchange Square', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2872, 'en_US', 'Grappa\'s Ristorante', '“Grappa\'s Ristorante” take pride in our home-style Italian recipes', 'Fresh homemade squid ink pasta with fresh prawns, Roast lamb chops with fennelparmesan gratin and rosemary port sauce, Seabass, potato purée, corn edamame salsa, and miso lobster butter', '', '“Grappa\'s Ristorante” take pride in our home-style Italian recipes and the fact that all sauces, pasta, sausages and desserts are produced exclusively in Grappa’s kitchen. They use only natural ingredients,also bake fresh bread daily in they own kitchen. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2873, 'en_US', 'Duddell\'s', 'It is a place where people come together to meet, eat, drink, entertain and relax in an environment that connects art and people in a fresh.', 'Fried beef cubes with wasabi and soy sauce, Crispy salted chicken, Fried fresh lobster, scallion and shallots', '', 'Duddell’s is a cultural and social destination for people who have an active appreciation for the arts. It is a place where people come together to meet, eat, drink, entertain and relax in an environment that connects art and people in a fresh, new way - allowing art masters and novices alike to embrace and develop the new cultural context adopted by the city. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2874, 'en_US', 'Café Landmark', 'it manages to evoke an illusion of the restaurant floating like a colorful jewel of a garden within the embrace of LANDMARK ATRIUM.', 'Lobster linguine, Fresh crabmeat Au Gratin, Kobe beef tenderloin salad', '', 'CAFÉ LANDMARKis recognised for its excellent international cuisine with an Asia-inspired refinement; the exclusive cake selection is a work of art and a feast for the eyes as well as for the taste buds. It is artisanal patisserie at its best.As the sun baths the building with its light through the high glass ceiling during the day, it manages to evoke an illusion of the restaurant floating like a colorful jewel of a garden within the embrace of LANDMARK ATRIUM. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2875, 'en_US', 'The Chairman', 'The ingredients are fresh, the sauces are outstanding, simple cooking will rule. This is what Cantonese cuisine is all about', 'The Chairman\'s Soy Sauce Chicken, Steamed Fresh Flowery Crab with Aged ShaoXing Wine, Spicy Peppercorn Flowery Crabs', '', 'Cantonese cuisine is light and delicate, and strives to bring out the original flavours of food. The foremost element of good food is the use of the finest\nand freshest ingredients. They also have a small farm of our own in Sheung Shui which is used as the venue for curing preserved meat and making different kinds of pickles. Recently we have started growing organic vegetables. They believe that as long as the ingredients are fresh, the sauces are outstanding, simple cooking will rule. This is what Cantonese cuisine is all about. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A2, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2876, 'en_US', 'La Saison by Jacques Barnachon', 'Offering elegant and opulent décor and Michelin-starred culinary skills', 'Miyazaki A4 beef tenderlion in mushroom sauce, morels and mashed potatoes served on the side, Gambas Obsiblue with pumpkin, blood orange confit and agrum foam, Pan fried duck foie gras with red apple confit & gingerbread', '', 'La Saison means “season” in France, highlighting the fact that the restaurant respects the rhythm of the seasons and serve only when the product is at its best, without any superfluous ingredient.The menu is designed by Jacques Barnarchon, executive chef of the renowned L’Etang du Moulin in France. La Saison is one of the few French fine dining restaurants in Tsim Sha Tsui, offering elegant and opulent décor and Michelin-starred culinary skills which guarantee unforgettable French meal. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B2, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(2877, 'en_US', 'La Parole', 'intended to delight every diner with authentic French flavors and artistic presentation in every dish.', 'Pan Fried Foie Gras \"Pot Au Feu\" with Grapes and Mashed Pear, Beef Tartar with Knives, Purple Chips and Choron Sauce, Poached White Cod, Pan Fried Quail Eggs with Chestnut and Vineger Sauce', '', 'La Parole is dedicated to traditional French cuisine, intended to delight every diner with authentic French flavors and artistic presentation in every dish. They insist in using only fresh and finest ingredients, matched with selection of the finest wines and offering the best service, striving to amuse our diner with a luxury culinary journey.La Parole is composed of two differently designed areas, one with a modern and vitality interior design, while the other is more elegant and romantic. In which makes La Parole the perfect place for any occasions and taste. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit A1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
