(3361, 'en_US', 'Jasmine', 'Jasmine offers a new Chinese dining experience by serving smaller portion Chinese dishes', 'Crispy barbecued suckling piglet, Shark\'s fin soup with crabmeat and crab coral', '', 'Enjoy authentic Chinese in a different way. The aroma of jasmine filled in the air. Jasmine offers a new Chinese dining experience by serving smaller portion Chinese dishes, healthy greens and tofu, a large selection of tea and home-made desserts, with MSC free and healthy cooking method. To experience Chinese food in a different way, one should start from Jasmine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon Tong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3362, 'en_US', 'Nepal - Nepalese Cuisine', 'Nepal offers you this aromatic Royal Nepalese cuisine after two hundred and fifty years of refinement.', 'Eggplants fried in herbs and spices, Barbequed chicken marinated in a cashew nut paste, saffron and spices, Stewed lamb in almond gravy', '', 'Nepalese cuisine is diverse and flavourful, reflecting many different Royal cuisines. Two hundred and fifty two ago there were many small states from the peak of Mount Everest to the southern Tarai border with India. The Royal cuisine was known as the deluxe bhojan offered to Royal guests in the different states according to their own tradition. Over the years, it has evolved into a variety of tastes, which can be classified as mild, medium hot, and very hot. Nepal offers you this aromatic Royal Nepalese cuisine after two hundred and fifty years of refinement. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit C, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3363, 'en_US', '121BC', 'The dynamite team is guided by ex Vini head chef Daniel Johnston and the food made in the same spirit of Vini and 121BC Sydney – Italian family style, substantial share plates, caring cooking, and hand-made pastas and ricotta.', 'Homemade ricotta, aubergine caponata, Caramelised lamb ribs, orange, caraway, Grilled octopus, chickpeas, olives, tomato', '', 'The dynamite team is guided by ex Vini head chef Daniel Johnston and the food made in the same spirit of Vini and 121BC Sydney – Italian family style, substantial share plates, caring cooking, and hand-made pastas and ricotta. Sommelier Giorgio De Maria travels to vineyards across Italy where he meets with producers and sources artisan, minimal interventionist wines for both Hong Kong and Sydney. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit E1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3364, 'en_US', 'Al Molo Ristorante Italiano', 'launches the exquisite skills of New York celebrity chef, Michael White to Hong Kong diners', 'Braciola, Zuppetta di pesce, Astice e burrata', '', 'AL MOLO - Al Molo Ristorante Italiano with its stunning New York design overlooking the spectacular Victoria Harbour and city environs, launches the exquisite skills of New York celebrity chef, Michael White to Hong Kong diners. Presenting an eclectic array of fine Italian cusine, AL MOLO presents a unique dining experience, New York style. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit L5, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3365, 'en_US', 'BellBrook Bistro oz by Laris', 'a unique Australian dining experience – flavorsome', 'Black pork Scotch egg, Kinkowooka mussels with tanami fire frites, Barramundi cooked in Aboriginal paperbark', '', 'AUSTRALIAN Chef, David Laris, introduces the BellBrook - a unique Australian dining experience – flavorsome, no fuss food with indigenous specialties, daily blackboard specials created to tantalize and surprise the palate, flared together by multi-cultural influences stemming from David Laris’ Australian origins and the village of BellBrook, the restaurant is filled with a relaxed vibe and a contagious energy for foodies and friends looking for a new no fuss dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit C, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
