(3379, 'en_US', 'Harlan\'s', 'Harlan’s has long been a preferred haven for lovers of fine Western and continental cuisine', 'Spaghetti, Boston lobster, chilli and shellfish sauce, Grilled home smoked beef tenderloin, foie gras, grapefruit, Japanese snow crab cake, fennel salad, mango lime dressing', '', 'Having welcomed its first discerning diner in 2004, Harlan’s has long been a preferred haven for lovers of fine Western and continental cuisine. With roomy, floor-to-ceiling windows providing spectacular harbour views and black and white photos showcasing Harlan’s illustrious history, lunch and dinner simply doesn’t get any grander than this. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3380, 'en_US', 'Toro Steakhouse & Gastro Bar', 'Celebrity Chef Richard Sandoval brings to Hong Kong his eclectic Pan Latin cuisine to Toro Steak House.', 'Yellowfin tuna nikkei ceviche, Canadian bone, in rib, eye, Achiote–barbecued salmon with chayote slaw', '', 'TORO Steak House & Gastro Bar – Celebrity Chef Richard Sandoval brings to Hong Kong his eclectic Pan Latin cuisine to Toro Steak House. An array of the finest cuts of steaks together with pork, veal, lamb and chicken sizzle from the grill while for non meat eaters, a great selection of ocean fresh seafood and vegetable dishes are featured on the menu. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3381, 'en_US', 'The Pawn', 'an excellent cooking skill for Modern British dishes', 'Charcuterie board, Razor clam, mitsuba, black garlic, pickled white radish, Violet and chocolate éclair', '', 'The Pawn is located 62 Johnston Road, in a four-storey building. Chef Aikens very famous in the UK, debut soon became the youngest British chef to win by two Michelin star honors with his an excellent cooking skill for Modern British dishes. Chef Aikens partnership with The Press Room Group, is responsible for the menu of  The Pawn dishes design. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit B2, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3382, 'en_US', 'Mesa 15', 'Mesa 15 continues to serve top quality Spanish cuisine to Hong Kong diners with top ingredients from both East and West', 'Signature octopus black rice, Duck rice', '', 'Moved from Hollywood Road to Lan Kwai Fong in June 2013. Mesa 15 continues to serve top quality Spanish cuisine to Hong Kong diners with top ingredients from both East and West. One of the first Spanish restaurant recommended by Michelin star guide HK & Macau edition (2012, 2013) (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3383, 'en_US', 'Sumac', 'Fine Lebanese cuisine prepared according to traditional family recipes by our Head Chef and Founder, Nadim Hamze.', 'Halloumi cheese salad, Sumac king prawns, Mixed grilled platter for two', '', 'Sumac, a dark red spice widely used throughout the Arabic world and along the Mediterranean coast, releases a subtle citrus infusion over the food it touches. Our restaurant takes its inspiration from the homeland of this unique spice - Lebanese at heart, Mediterranean in style. Come and savour our fine Lebanese cuisine prepared according to traditional family recipes by our Head Chef and Founder, Nadim Hamze. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3384, 'en_US', 'Soho Spice', 'One of the most popular restaurants in the Soho dining precinct specializing in authentic Thai and Vietnamese cuisine, presented in a contemporary style', 'Crispy Thai tiger prawn with spiced tamarind and coriander, Deep, fried Thai prawn cake with plum dipping sauce, Seafood laksa, prawns, clams, squid in thick rice noodles', '', 'SOHO SPICE Vietnamese & Thai - has become one of the most popular restaurants in the Soho dining precinct specializing in authentic Thai and Vietnamese cuisine, presented in a contemporary style. With tasty, tempting dishes, Soho Spice continues to delight diners seeking the best in Asian cuisine. Sensational desserts are a feature. The exceptional décor features exotic design in a sophisticated setting (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3385, 'en_US', 'Yung Kee', 'Yung Kee acquires fame for its gourmet specialty-Roast Goose. It becomes well known among people in Guangdong, Hong Kong and Macau, and it also attracts many tourists from foreign countries.', 'Roasted goose, Barbecued pork with roasted assorted goose giblets, Steamed crab with rice in a bamboo steam pot', '', 'Yung Kee acquires fame for its gourmet specialty-Roast Goose. It becomes well known among people in Guangdong, Hong Kong and Macau, and it also attracts many tourists from foreign countries. After tasting the Roast Goose, they buy and carry it home with them by air to share among relatives and friends. For that, Yung Kee\'s Roast Goose is nicknamed \"Flying Roast Goose\". Yung Kee\'s founder, Mr. Kam Shui Fai, is also called \"Roast Goose Fai\". (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3386, 'en_US', 'Saint Germain', 'Happy Valley, is a provider of high-level French restaurant, but in the evening there will become a bar', 'Roasted Sea Bass w/ Rosemary & Lemon Sauce, Half Lobster Linguini, Thai Asparagus & Lobster Bisque', '', 'Saint Germain is located in Wong Nai Chung Road, Happy Valley, is a provider of high-level French restaurant, but in the evening there will become a bar. And because the restaurant in the vicinity of Happy Valley Racecourse, just to provide another option for some people after the event finished. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Happy Valley Terminus trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3387, 'en_US', 'Carpaccio Pasta Pizza Vino', 'Carpaccio takes the diner to Italy where one can enjoy the finest Italian fares made of the freshest seasonal ingredients.', 'Home, made cured swordfish loin carpaccio with Sicilian citrus, served with avocado and lime salsa, Pappardelle tossed with a rich seafood sauce, Parma ham pizza', '', 'Carpaccio offers Hong Kongers the opportunity to explore the daily trattoria experience, from the fast, dynamic dining in the morning, and lunch in afternoon to a casual yet elegant dining at night. Carpaccio takes the diner to Italy where one can enjoy the finest Italian fares made of the freshest seasonal ingredients. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit H, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3388, 'en_US', 'Loyal Dining', 'For an authentic Hong Kong classic dining experience infused with the unique history and traditions of Hong Kong', 'Loyal Pigeon Simmered in Homemade Sweet Soya Sauce, Baked Kurobuta Pork Chop with Fried Riece & Sunny Sidr Egg, Loyal Souffle', '', 'The name “Loyal Dining” is drawn from a play on words “Loi Lo”, a Cantonese saying refers to the exquisite imported goods from the West that became popular during colonial Hong Kong in the 60s and 70s. The concept of Loyal Dining is derived from the idea of revisiting this colonial era, when East meets West. For an authentic Hong Kong classic dining experience infused with the unique history and traditions of Hong Kong, look no further than Loyal Dining! (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3389, 'en_US', 'Mostaccioli Brothers', 'Mostaccioli Brothers brings you some of the best dishes to come out of the Italian immigrant tradition in America during the 50s and 60s.', 'Boston lobster with fettuccine in a spicy tomato sauce, 1/2 Roasted Italian Herb Chicken, Veal Parmesan', '', 'Mostaccioli Brothers brings you some of the best dishes to come out of the Italian immigrant tradition in America during the 50s and 60s. Specialties such as its namesake pasta dish, mostaccioli, are made from simple recipes and boast a humble wholesomeness evocative of early immigrant family kitchens, while dishes such as the veal scaloppini marsala add a balancing touch of modern flavor. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit E1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3390, 'en_US', 'La Pampa Argentinian Steak House', '\"Best Argentinian Steak House in Town\"', 'Grilled Lomo, Empanada, Grilled Provolone', '', 'The name La Pampa derived from Pampas (in Spanish) are the vast lowland plains of Argentina where since the middle of 19th century the breeding of high-grade sheep and cattle started. If you are a serious steaks lover, head into this homely restaurant for the \"Best Argentinian Steak House in Town\". (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3391, 'en_US', 'Swiss Chalet', 'As most traditional authentic Swiss cuisine, preferred fondue, you can choose one of cheese here: Gruyee, Emmetaler, Lamdenberger and Vacherin', 'Fried Veal in Swiss Style, Cheese fondue, Toblerone chocolate fondue', '', 'The Swiss Chalet championed the typical Swiss food culture, from Decoration to dishes are full of Swiss style. The restaurant offers both French and Italian specialties dishes, also allows guests to have different options. As most traditional authentic Swiss cuisine, preferred fondue, you can choose one of cheese here: Gruyee, Emmetaler, Lamdenberger and Vacherin. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit P3, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3392, 'en_US', 'Tapeo (Central Branch)', 'Tapeo has a highly social atmosphere, reminiscent of an authentic traditional tapas bar in Spain.', 'Seared scallops and candied pork, Mussels and chorizo, Gambas pil pil', '', 'Tapeo, Spanish tapas bar and restaurant, is located right in the heart of bustling Central. With food and wine sourced from a variety of different regions around Spain, the restaurant offers genuine Spanish fare cooked in an open kitchen, allowing diners to interact with the chefs as it is prepared. Tapeo has a highly social atmosphere, reminiscent of an authentic traditional tapas bar in Spain. Tapeo’s open kitchen setting always provides a fun and exciting venue for all kinds of small-scale functions. Enjoy some authentic Spanish tapas and wine whilst watching our experienced chefs cook for you and your friends. Staff at Tapeo pride themselves on having had excellent training, to ensure that service is of the highest quality. At Tapeo, every detail is carefully considered, making sure that every function is a success. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit C, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3393, 'en_US', 'Tapeo (Sai Wan Ho Branch)', 'Tapeo has a highly social atmosphere, reminiscent of an authentic traditional tapas bar in Spain.', 'Seared scallops and candied pork, Mussels and chorizo, Gambas pil pil', '', 'Tapeo, Spanish tapas bar and restaurant, is located right in the heart of bustling Central. With food and wine sourced from a variety of different regions around Spain, the restaurant offers genuine Spanish fare cooked in an open kitchen, allowing diners to interact with the chefs as it is prepared. Tapeo has a highly social atmosphere, reminiscent of an authentic traditional tapas bar in Spain. Tapeo’s open kitchen setting always provides a fun and exciting venue for all kinds of small-scale functions. Enjoy some authentic Spanish tapas and wine whilst watching our experienced chefs cook for you and your friends. Staff at Tapeo pride themselves on having had excellent training, to ensure that service is of the highest quality. At Tapeo, every detail is carefully considered, making sure that every function is a success. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B, Sai Wan Ho MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3394, 'en_US', 'Il Milione', 'IL Milione Bar & Ristorante Italiano brings the best of Italy cuisine to the heart of Hong Kong.', 'Pan, fried pigeon breast, Passatelli pasta with with lobster tail, lobster broth and samphire, Crispy lentil cannolo with pistachio mousse and blackberry sorbet', '', 'IL Milione Bar & Ristorante Italiano brings the best of Italy cuisine to the heart of Hong Kong. Named after the fabled book of travels by Marco Polo, IL Milione aims to create an exchange of culinary experiences not unlike the pioneering trade that took place in the 13th century. The star restaurant offers a variety of authentic Italian dishes, many of which are inspired by Umbrian cuisine – a style originating from the landlocked region flanked by Tuscany and Marche, best known for its black truffle, cured meats, and olive oil. IL Milione’s cocktail bar is not to be missed. \nIL Milione is proud to bring the best flavours of Italy with sophistication to the heart of the city, in Hutchison House, Central. With gold and black undertones, complemented with soft yellow lighting, IL Milione sets the scene for the ultimate elegant, warm and welcoming dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B, Admiralty MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3395, 'en_US', 'Teppanyaki Ginza Sumikawa', 'Sumikawa give customers an authentic Japanese dining experience, where the attention to detail, meticulous care and preparation of the food is reflected in the flavour.', 'Supreme Kobe beef sirloin, French foie gras in “dengaku” style, Fresh abalone teppanyaki', '', 'Teppanyaki Ginza Sumikawa, located in Sheung Wan, top level teppanyaki restaurant. Everything from the tableware and furniture, to the produce and mostly importantly, the beef, are all flown in from Japan. Sumikawa give customers an authentic Japanese dining experience, where the attention to detail, meticulous care and preparation of the food is reflected in the flavour. The essence of teppanyaki stays true to the quality and natural flavours of ingredients, so little is done with seasoning besides salt and pepper. The restaurant is structured into four private, minimalistic-styled rooms, so diners can have an intimate experience while they socialise, with the expert chef cooking the food in front of them. The main focus here is the food after all, and the restaurant takes great care in getting rid of frivolous distractions. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit C, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3396, 'en_US', 'Le Dôme de Cristal', 'The restaurant’s exquisite French dishes and superior selection of fine wines promise an unparalleled dining experience with a symphony of flavours that pay homage to the luxury, exclusivity, history and prestige of Cristal.', 'Aubrac Beef RibEye, Cancale Oyster No.4˙Cauliflower˙Caviar, Pigeon˙in two ways˙Beetroots˙Raspberry˙Mashed Potatoes˙Acidic Jus', '', 'Le Dôme de Cristal , occupies almost 10,000 square feet and is a true celebration of the luxury, exclusivity, history, and prestige of Cristal. \nThe restaurant’s exquisite French dishes and superior selection of fine wines promise an unparalleled dining experience with a symphony of flavours that pay homage to the luxury, exclusivity, history and prestige of Cristal.\nThe dome-shaped restaurant maintains an elite status without compromising its relaxed vibe, the dining area features dark parquet oak wood flooring with rotational seating, while the large windows bring elegant panoramic views of the Hong Kong city landscape. \nWith strong passion in food, curiosity in cultures and a wealth of impeccable experience gained from working in Michelin starred restaurants, Chef Charles-Benoit Lacour, the culinary director, is always in pursuit of perfection in culinary arts which blends the joy of homely cooking with the elegancy of French fine dining. He cooks with all his heart, uses the freshest and delicate produce to create modern French cuisine with sublime combinations of Asian flavours. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit K, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3397, 'en_US', 'Trattoria Caffe Monteverdi', 'MONTEVERDI brings you a taste of ancient folk and country cooking paired with wines.', 'Sicilian Red Prawns and Crab Risotto, Veal  Cutlet Umbria Style, Layered Oven baked Pasta', '', 'TRATTORIA CAFFE- MONTEVERDI purpose is to make the Inn relive in Hong Kong. MONTEVERDI trying to bring to you is a taste of ancient folk and country cooking paired with wines. In a relaxed atmosphere that is a mix of classic and modern Monteverdi hope to give you a taste of what you could find travelling through Italy. Monteverdi strive to give you a culinary tour of Italy. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Eastern Street trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3398, 'en_US', 'Santorini Greek Restaurant', 'Santorini\'s traditional look, inspired by Greek island architecture and modern decorations will surely grab your attention at first glance!', 'Potato salad with calamari, Vinsanto Chicken', '', 'Located in the bustling Soho area in central, Santorini\'s traditional look, inspired by Greek island architecture and modern decorations will surely grab your attention at first glance!\nSantorini\'s authentic Greek dishes and warm Hellenic hospitality will take your senses on a refreshing journey to the Aegean Sea. Chef Andrea’s philosophy in cooking is based on simplicity, which brings out the most of the flavors of each unique ingredient he uses.\nAuthenticity is the foundation for all of his unique mouthwatering creations.\nThe majority of Santorini\'s wine collection at Santorini Restaurant, is not only produced in Greece but also made of ancient Greek varieties which are very unique in aromas and textures. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3399, 'en_US', 'Tango Argentinian Steakhouse', 'TANGO Argentinian Steak House - Mingle with the flavours and culture of Argentina.', 'Argentinean rib, eye, Traditional hand, cut beef sirloin empañadas, Leche flan', '', 'TANGO Argentinian Steak House - Mingle with the flavours and culture of Argentina. Tango is a steak house in the Argentinian tradition, seductive, rustic, elegant. Tango is the place to enjoy prime cuts of prime Argentine beef lovingly prepared by our South American chef over the open fired Parilla. Sizzling seafood, pasta and indulgent desserts are complimented with an impressive array of Argentinian, Spanish and South American wines and classic cocktails, Buenos Aires style. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3400, 'en_US', 'ZUMA', 'ZUMA brings a sophisticated twist on the traditional japanese izakaya style of informal eating and drinking.', 'Haccho miso marinated lamb chops, pickled onions and myoga, Miso marinated black cod wrapped in hoba leaf, Sashimi selection', '', 'ZUMA is located at hong kong\'s most prestigious address, the landmark, in the heart of central. It brings a sophisticated twist on the traditional japanese izakaya style of informal eating and drinking. complemented by a terrace in a surrounding garden on level 5, a dramatic spiral staircase joins the two levels, which brings customers to level 6, the lounge & bar. the lounge and bar offers the same menu as the restaurant during lunch and dinner hours within a more relaxed and informal environment. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3401, 'en_US', 'Manzo Italian Steak House', 'Manzo offers a fresh approach to  steak house dining with the introduction of exclusively grown red and black angus beef.', '35oz USDA fiorentina, Grilled lamb chops with honey and rosemary marinade, Spaghetti with sautéed shrimps, green peas and lemon butter', '', 'MANZO Italian Steak House – located at Hong Kong’s most dynamic shopping and dining destination, Times Square in Causeway Bay, Manzo offers a fresh approach to  steak house dining with the introduction of exclusively grown red and black angus beef. In addition, a selection of USDA prime and Australian wagyu is featured. Superb antipasto presentation, homemade pasta and a special ‘butcher’s selection’ also feature on the menu with delectable Italian desserts and a comprehensive collection of Italy’s finest wines. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit A, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3402, 'en_US', 'Cecconi\'s Italian', 'Blending traditional Italian favourites with modern and delightfully innovative dishes, the menu selection is both comprehensive and enchanting.', 'Roast figs with goat’s cheese and flat pancetta, Roasted pork loin, Sand crab with avocado, iceberg lettuce and tomato gazpacho', '', 'Cecconi\'s Italian – introduces a place where food, wine, service and atmosphere come beautifully together. Blending traditional Italian favourites with modern and delightfully innovative dishes, the menu selection is both comprehensive and enchanting. Our aim is to express the true spirit of good Italian cooking and create a dining experience to savor. An institution for Italian flavours in the heart of Soho. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '9-min walk from Exit E1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3403, 'en_US', 'Craftsteak', 'CRAFTSTEAK, Open Fire Cooking, created for comfort, provides a memorable fine dining experience.', 'Korean Beef Shortrib with Sesame & Green Apple Gremolata, Seasonal Oysters, Atlantic Salmon Fillet', '', 'CRAFTSTEAK, Open Fire Cooking ,created for comfort, Craftsteak provides a memorable fine dining experience. The open fire cooking on the custom made charcoal fired grill creates wonderful hints of smoke flavor to the sizzling grills. Classic starters, the freshest cuts of steaks from Australia, USA and Canada as well as poultry, seafood and vegetables, all presented with a selection of individual sauces, are there to enjoy in an atmosphere created for comfort. Famous for its great selection of world wines, many available by the glass. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit E1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3404, 'en_US', 'Nahm', 'Exotic tastes featuring Asia\'s most popular food styles, Nahm delights guests with fine dining in a contemporary setting.', 'Deep fried soft shell crabs roll with mange, avocado, spinach with orange caramel dipping sauce, Braised lamb shank with tamarind curry, Baked king prawns with fragrant chili in spicy pomolo, peanut sauce', '', 'Nahm, Vietnamese & Thai – Exotic tastes featuring Asia\'s most popular food styles, Nahm delights guests with fine dining in a contemporary setting. Truly in a league of its own, Nahm doesn\'t only serve the best Vietnamese and Thai cuisine, but is unquestionably among the best restaurants of its type in Hong Kong. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3405, 'en_US', 'Mama San Restaurant & Bar', 'Mama San is for anyone who appreciates to lounge in style and eat quality food without it being too expensive.', 'Oyster nahm jihm with coriander and crispy shallots, Chilli harbour prawns with deep, fried garlic iceberg lettuce, Salt, crusted barramundi', '', 'Mama San is for anyone who appreciates to lounge in style and eat quality food without it being too expensive. Step into colonial Britain in Shanghai during the 1920s, with marble top mah-jong tables and oversized tan leather chesterﬁelds, in a purpose designed industrial high ceiling warehouse. Gaze up to Mama San in all her glory staring down at patrons while dining and ponder over a travelogue of old style photographs. Colorful displays of retro inspired ﬂowers tower up to vintage clocks and aChinese patterned mirror. A feature of the ground ﬂoor interior are two staircases either side of a service bar that climb a brick wall to the upper level.\nThe Mama San ground ﬂoor dining room is fully air-conditioned, seats up to 70 at any one time and is open for lunch at 11am -2pm and for dinner from 6pm – 11pm. Reservations are recommended for lunch and essential for the dinner service. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3406, 'en_US', 'Ole Spanish Restaurant', 'Ole was created from this crave for authenticity, recreate a unique and cozy atmosphere.', 'Spanish red prawns and clams juicy rice casserole, Spanish Iberico ham \"Joselito Gran Reserva\", Spanish churros with hot chocolate', '', 'Ole was created from this crave for authenticity! Just Experience the genuine touch of Spain the moment you step inside the restaurant: The lemon yellow plastered walls and glazed terracotta tiles of the Mediterranean, the lighting Fixture and the decorative potteries directly flown from Spain. All  these elements combined to recreate a unique and cozy atmosphere that goes hand in hand for the enjoyment one of the world\'s finest cuisines. The extensive variety of delicacies, perfect with the Spanish wines, sangria or chilled beers. Live guitar music throughout the evening gracefully exhilarates a relaxing and enjoyable mood. An attentive and energetic team is at your service to provide each and every customer a satisfactory dining experience. Ask for our experienced &competent supervisors to assist or plan for events of any kinds. They are always delighted to bring alive the occasion for you. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3407, 'en_US', 'The Stonegrill (Tsim Sha Tsui Branch)', 'The Stonegrill, quickly established itself as a firm favorite amongst Hong Kong\'s fickle food culture, and is constantly rated as one of the city\'s best restaurants.', 'Super Prime Canadian Angus Tenderloin, Pacific Lobster Tail, Rack Of Lamb', '', 'The Stonegrill, quickly established itself as a firm favorite amongst Hong Kong\'s fickle food culture, and is constantly rated as one of the city\'s best restaurants. Now you can enjoy the unique and delicious Stonegrill flavours in THE HART 1/F. Our innovative and healthy dining alternative method of cooking your own meal table-side on a natural Australian volcanic stone designed to retain heat, is a concept unlike anywhere else in the area. The Stonegrill offers lunch and dinner, menu cooked in house, as well as our infamous Sunday Brunch. We strive to use locally grown produce from our own Stonegrill Gardens, as well as local meat whenever possible. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit P3, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3408, 'en_US', 'The Stonegrill (Central Branch)', 'The Stonegrill, quickly established itself as a firm favorite amongst Hong Kong\'s fickle food culture, and is constantly rated as one of the city\'s best restaurants.', 'Super Prime Canadian Angus Tenderloin, Pacific Lobster Tail, Rack Of Lamb', '', 'The Stonegrill, quickly established itself as a firm favorite amongst Hong Kong\'s fickle food culture, and is constantly rated as one of the city\'s best restaurants. Now you can enjoy the unique and delicious Stonegrill flavours in 51 Peel Street at Central. Our innovative and healthy dining alternative method of cooking your own meal table-side on a natural Australian volcanic stone designed to retain heat, is a concept unlike anywhere else in the area. The Stonegrill offers lunch and dinner, menu cooked in house, as well as our infamous Sunday Brunch. We strive to use locally grown produce from our own Stonegrill Gardens, as well as local meat whenever possible. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit E1, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3409, 'en_US', 'Shiro (Hysan Place Branch)', 'Shiro reflects elegant Zen simplicity – the essence of Japanese dining.', 'Seared scallop with cod roe, Taraba king crab tempura, Spinach with sesame sauce', '', 'Shiro reflects elegant Zen simplicity – the essence of Japanese dining. Six styles of contemporary Japanese cuisine. Shiro is a sleek yet casual dining room featuring two kaiten sushi belts to provide guests with fresh sushi and sashimi. The glamorous space is fitted out with angled mirrors and sexy lighting to create a slick and contemporary space where patrons can enjoy a modern take on the traditional Japanese dining experience.  House-mixed sake cocktails and iced teas are the perfect accompaniment to signature dishes such as the A4 Premium cut Wagyu beef and the tempura Taraba crab with miso sauce and cucumber.  A take-away \"prêt-a-porter\" service also available made fresh to order. Shiro offers different and unique private event spaces for all sizes and types of events both corporate and private parties. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
