(3412, 'en_US', 'Stockton Bar and Restaurant', 'Stockton is a restaurant and bar tucked away right in the heart of Central.', 'The Stockton ultimate whole lobster salad, Scotch egg, Beetroot gravlax', '', 'Stockton is a restaurant and bar tucked away right in the heart of Central. At Stockton, we have recreated the halcyon days of the 1890s London, when life moved at a slower pace and the fortunate lived life to a remarkably high standard of living. Stockton is wood paneled and full of classic furniture, art, antiques and historical artifacts sourced from markets in Paris. Stockton is an escape from the humdrum of Lan Kwai Fong and Central. Conversation is highly valued and privacy guaranteed. Stockton is open to all and everyone and is not a private members venue. Stockton accepts reservations for both dinner and libations. The bar team is made up by the creators and talented mixologists at Maximal Concepts that won the Tatler’s Best Cocktail award in Hong Kong, 2013 at Blue Butcher. To make your experience more unique, we barrel age and leather age our own spirits at Stockton. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3413, 'en_US', 'Carbone', 'Carbone, exceptionally well-prepared food was served in settings that were simultaneously elegant, comfortable and unpretentious.', 'Baked clams, Mario\'s meatballs, Spicy rigatoni vodka', '', 'Carbone Hong Kong is a New York-Italian restaurant that pays homage to the essence of the great Italian restaurants of mid-20th century in New York, where delicious, exceptionally well-prepared food was served in settings that were simultaneously elegant, comfortable and unpretentious. The food nods to that same history, but takes culinary cues from the great talents and techniques of the present and future, featuring familiar dishes like Seafood Salad, Linguini Vongole, Lobster Fra Diavola, Chicken Scarpariello and Veal Parmesan elevated to a new level. Carbone Hong Kong was created by Mario Carbone, Rich Torrisi and Jeff Zalaznick of New York-based Major Food Group in collaboration with Syed Asim Hussain and Christopher Mark of Black Sheep Restaurants. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3414, 'en_US', 'Francesco By Franck Muller', 'FRANCESCO by FRANCK MULLER delights the senses by marrying Italian and Japanese cuisine to create a new dining perspective in the heart of Causeway Bay.', 'Sashimi octopus salad, Roasted Okinawa miso pork, Baked French chicken casserole', '', 'FRANCESCO by FRANCK MULLER delights the senses by marrying Italian and Japanese cuisine to create a new dining perspective in the heart of Causeway Bay. Inspired by the essence of the two, FRANCESCO presents to its diners a casually sophisticated yet comforting menu, intended to bring up memories of home. The playful atmosphere boasts contemporary furnishings inspired by our very own Franck Muller Color Dreams Collection as well as reoccurring Japanese and Italian decorative influences. As an extension of the Franck Muller brand, the FRANCESCO dining room and bar offers a relaxed destination where guests can enjoy creative cocktails, à la carte dining and indulge themselves in sumptuous Italian desserts. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3415, 'en_US', 'Youka', 'Youuka, a Japanese Washoku Restaurant is as much about the unique experience as it is about delectable cuisine.', 'Assorted tempura, Deluxe assorted sushi platter, Grilled Japanese chicken served with Japanese ponzu sauce', '', 'A new Japanese premium dining experience. Youuka, a Japanese Washoku Restaurant is as much about the unique experience as it is about delectable cuisine. Whether you\'re looking for a satisfying and delicious lunch, or a premium sashimi, sushi or yakitori dinner paired with sake and Japanese beer – Youka\'s quality food, its warm and hospitable service as well as its contemporary interior design culminates in an impeccable dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B2, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3416, 'en_US', 'Frites Belgium on Tap (Quarry Bay Branch)', 'Frites Belgian beer houses offer a delicious selection of traditional Belgian cuisine, along with Hong Kong’s largest selection of Belgian beer, available by draught or by the bottle.', 'Whole herb roasted sea bream, Laksa mussel pot, Steak tartare', '', 'Frites Belgian beer houses offer a delicious selection of traditional Belgian cuisine, along with Hong Kong’s largest selection of Belgian beer, available by draught or by the bottle. The setting of each Frites venue reminds one of a European-style bistro or beer hall, instantly creating a comfortable, casual and welcoming environment for its loyal guests. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B, Quarry Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3417, 'en_US', 'Frites Belgium on Tap (Wan Chai Branch)', 'Frites Belgian beer houses offer a delicious selection of traditional Belgian cuisine, along with Hong Kong’s largest selection of Belgian beer, available by draught or by the bottle.', 'Whole herb roasted sea bream, Laksa mussel pot, Steak tartare', '', 'Frites Belgian beer houses offer a delicious selection of traditional Belgian cuisine, along with Hong Kong’s largest selection of Belgian beer, available by draught or by the bottle. The setting of each Frites venue reminds one of a European-style bistro or beer hall, instantly creating a comfortable, casual and welcoming environment for its loyal guests. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3419, 'en_US', 'Mango Tree (Kowloon Branch)', 'Mango Tree using only the best and freshest ingredients, organic herbs and spices, our chefs bring the essence of Thai cuisine – Sweet, Sour, Spicy – to delicious extreme.', 'Chicken in pandan leaves, Crispy catfish salad, Fresh river prawn in clay pot', '', 'Upholding Mango Tree’s tradition and prestige, Mango Tree Hong Kong is dedicated to maintaining authenticity and sophistication in its cuisine, environment and services. By using only the best and freshest ingredients, organic herbs and spices, our chefs bring the essence of Thai cuisine – Sweet, Sour, Spicy – to delicious extreme. Managed by 1957 & Co., Mango Tree Hong Kong follows the “4D Dining” concept: Apart from offering “Delicious” cuisine, it combines artistic “Design”, attention to “Details” and masterful “Dedication”. Ensuring every of our guests has a dining experience that is both memorable and enjoyable, as well as bringing Mango Tree’s contemporary interiors and presentation skills to a global audience, whilst staying true to its authentic Thai roots. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
