(3421, 'en_US', 'Xia Fei Society', 'Xia Fei Society congregates tasteful people who love enjoying authentic Shanghainese cuisine in an elegant and comfortable environment.', 'Sautéed shredded freshwater fish, Deep, fried minced shrimp ball with chicken broth in centre, Fried glutinous rice with fresh crab', '', 'Upholding Mango Tree’s tradition and prestige, Mango Tree Hong Kong is dedicated to maintaining authenticity and sophistication in its cuisine, environment and services. By using only the best and freshest ingredients, organic herbs and spices, our chefs bring the essence of Thai cuisine – Sweet, Sour, Spicy – to delicious extreme. Managed by 1957 & Co., Mango Tree Hong Kong follows the “4D Dining” concept: Apart from offering “Delicious” cuisine, it combines artistic “Design”, attention to “Details” and masterful “Dedication”. Ensuring every of our guests has a dining experience that is both memorable and enjoyable, as well as bringing Mango Tree’s contemporary interiors and presentation skills to a global audience, whilst staying true to its authentic Thai roots. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3422, 'en_US', 'Souvla', 'Souvla’s food and beverage offerings following the age-old tradition of simplicity, quality and freshness in everything served.', 'Glacier 51 toothfish, Cypriot salata, Octopus sti skara', '', 'Souvla is a contemporary Greek restaurant in the heart of Lan Kwai Fong. Named after the popular Greek dish of open-spit grilled meat, Souvla’s unique design adopts essences of old Greece with a modern, yet subtle, twist. Greek honey is considered to be some of the finest in the world, due to unlimited summer sun; at Souvla, this idea is presented not only in its food, but also throughout the entire restaurant via a honeycomb feature and the use of golden honey timber.The bar and tabletops are made from honed white granite, taking on the appearance of 800,000 year-old marble. This, together with Robert Gordon’s beautifully handcrafted pieces of ceramic crockery, creates an atmosphere reminiscent of Ancient Greece, with a modern feel. Much the same can be said about Souvla’s food and beverage offerings, – following the age-old tradition of simplicity, quality and freshness in everything served. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3423, 'en_US', 'Alfie\'s', 'Traditional British pub fare with an understated contemporary spin is on offer here, with a thoughtful and concise menu paving the way for swift decision-making.', 'Fish and Chips, Cottage pie, Old English bangers and mash', '', 'Alfie’s is located in the heart of Central, tucked away above the Alfred Dunhill store in the Landmark Prince’s building. The dark, masculine personality behind this established brand is certainly carried through to the restaurant, with its black leather seating, marble floors and metallic details. A hefty bar area consumes the middle of the restaurant and on a Thursday evening, the ‘70s disco tunes were pumping and post-work drinks were certainly flowing. Traditional British pub fare with an understated contemporary spin is on offer here, with a thoughtful and concise menu paving the way for swift decision-making. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit K, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3424, 'en_US', 'Fofo by El Willy', 'With its uniquely creative interior design, its seductive mountain view and tranquil surroundings, Fofo provides its customers with a most relaxing and pleasant gastronomical experience that can rarely be found in Hong Kong.', 'Crispy suckling pig, Traditional Spanish Boston lobster and seafood paella, Scallop ceviche, avocado and crispy shallots', '', 'As a contemporary Spanish restaurant, Fofo offers both traditional and contemporary Spanish taps and rice. It also proposes the world\'s favorite lberian ham, as well as other new and innovative dishes such as the \'scallop ceviche\' and \'beef cheek with banana & passion fruit crispy roll\'. The menu features more than 60 dishes, offering a variety of starters, tapas , soups, salads, omelets, paellas & juicy rice, as well as desserts that aim to satisfy even the pickiest of customers.\nWith its uniquely creative interior design, its seductive mountain view and tranquil surroundings, Fofo provides its customers with a most relaxing and pleasant gastronomical experience that can rarely be found in Hong Kong. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3425, 'en_US', 'The Socialhouse', 'The Socialhouse embodies a philosophy of using only fresh ingredients, with an inspirational approach to create innovative dishes, which are grounded in proper French technique.', 'Spain porchetta, Duck Confit', '', 'The Socialhouse is a gem hidden from the crowd. It is located in Tai Hang, all the way into the heart of the neighbourhood, surrounded by layers of petite blocks and houses.\nIt is a restaurant that embodies a philosophy of using only fresh ingredients, with an inspirational approach to create innovative dishes, which are grounded in proper French technique. It embraces flavours of traditional European cuisine with a contemporary twist, dispelling the notion of its heaviness and pretentiousness. The name of the restaurant explains itself, by providing a warm and inviting atmosphere, guests are able to fully enjoy an exceptional dining experience with a wide and brilliant selection of wines and beverages.\nChef and owner Ray, who was trained in France had bought his knowledge back home to Canada and finally to Hong Kong. With years of experience, Ray expresses his talent passionately in creating a concept of casual fine dining - from menu design to appreciation of wine, from exceptional service to heart-warming ambience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit B, Tin Hau MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
