(3437, 'en_US', 'Joy and Joy', 'Joy & Joy is a unique boutique restaurant with Chinese elements along with a western style.', 'Honey glazed roast pork, Double, boiled fish maw, pig’s lung and almond soup', '', 'Joy & Joy is a unique boutique restaurant. Chinese elements along with a western style bar blend east and west with a modern and nostalgic flair. Private booths and VIP rooms collude to produce an elegant setting making Joy & Joy the ideal choice for exclusive banqueting. The restaurant features exquisite dim sum and modern asian dishes guaranteed to delight both Western and Chinese epicureans alike. Joy & Joy has been designed to suit the sophisticated, with details that exude elegance equally by elements of tradition Chinese along with western modern style. Together with the VIP rooms, it makes Joy & Joy the ideal venue for dining or banqueting. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit C, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3438, 'en_US', 'House of Jasmine', 'House of Jasmine is a restaurant which gives you comfortable and tranquil environment.', 'Crispy barbecued suckling piglet, Fresh fruit mapoleon, Steamed prawn on egg white in \"Tai Diao\" rice liquor', '', 'House of Jasmine in Harbour City, Tsim Sha Tsui, is a restaurant which gives you comfortable and tranquil environment. It has tables in open air area which is unique in town and offers a splendid harbour view for customers hosting fine dinners. Apart from the comfortable and elegant environment, the dishes are the same brilliant in House of Jasmine. All the dishes are MSG free and using healthy cooking method, which fully presenting the original style and taste of Chinese cuisine. House of Jasmine adopts the best food produce and always innovate new dishes. The dish cooking also demand chefs’ art of cooking and experience. They specially make different kinds of sauce of unique flavours for every dish in each food produce. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit L5, East Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3439, 'en_US', 'Charisme Pavillon', 'Charisme Pavillon is an authentic Shunde private kitchens.', 'Supreme Soy Sauce Chicken Wings, Pot Burn Pork Rib, Fried Chicken Wing Balls with Lotus', '', 'Charisme Pavillon is an authentic Shunde private kitchens. In 2003, founded by Mr. Hu Deming, the restaurant’s above floor private kitchens and high-quality skilled pattern dishes, attracting attention of the guests to come. In addition to the main dishes of abalone and shark fins, as well as the home of Shunde dishes. There are more than quality guarantee, the price is also very reasonable. Not plainly the pursuit of luxurious ingredient, but pay attention to taste homemade, like the use of local materials, with the most unusual materials, the most simple seasoning, to highlight the original flavor of the ingredients. Not eat expensive, but to eat fine. It is fine to do so-called coarse material, the use of time effort, can make a delicious humble. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit A3, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3440, 'en_US', 'Le Blanc', 'Filled with passion in southern of France, Le Blanc is a private kitchen in Hong Kong.', 'Roast tartlet of tomatoes with goat cheese, Braised pork knuckle with lentils and truffle vinaigrette, Dark cherry clafoutis', '', 'Le Blanc, as a French restaurant and private kitchen, makes you feel like being at home filled with passion in southern of France. All of favorite things here: great food, fine wine, quaint design, welcoming people, to our courteous & attentive service. These allows you to soak up the relaxed atmosphere as well as European customs. While you are dining in your private home (private area), the meal is created and presented with care. Meals here (also in France) are drawn out for the purpose of enjoyment - civilized loitering. There is much to observe over the course of a meal, about the people around you, about the origins of the customs, and about the food itself. So please sit back, relax and enjoy tonight. Bon Appétit. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit A3, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3441, 'en_US', 'Pak Loh Chiu Chow Restaurant (Causeway Bay Branch)', 'Pak Loh Chiu Chow Restaurant provides genuine Chiu Chow cuisine and excellent service to win customer loyalty.', 'Shark’s Fin (Chiu Chow Special), Freshly Steamed Crab served in Cold, Steamed Fresh Water Goby Fish', '', 'Pak Loh Chiu Chow Restaurant was founded by Mr. S. H. Pui in 1967. During the past four decades, Pak Loh Group has expanded with branches in high-prestige locations all over Hong Kong, providing genuine Chiu Chow cuisine and excellent service to win customer loyalty. To cater to the newest generations of Hong Kong diners, Pak Loh Chiu Chow brings new elements to conventional popular dishes. Our creative chef teams combine Chiu Chow ingredients and seasonings with stylish, innovative methods and techniques, to produce new and delightful additions to Chiu Chow traditional cuisine. Each Pak Loh restaurant has its own kitchen management system, and a dedicated team of outstanding chefs that consistently produces unique tastes that satisfy customers’ expectations in each of our various locations. We provide a variety of dim sum, marinated foods, and premium dishes that enable our diners to fully savor and enjoy Chiu Chow tastes in a relaxed, friendly dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
