(3488, 'en_US', 'Pearl Delights', 'Pearl Delights is a dedicating attempt to bring to life the classic Hong Kong flavors.', 'Double boiled shark fin soup with seafood and cabbage, Barbecued pork with honey sauce, Hand shredded chicken with Yuzu and fish sauce', '', 'Pearl Delights, JC Group’s first Cantonese dining restaurant located in New Town Plaza in Shatin, is a dedicating attempt to bring to life the classic Hong Kong flavors with a dazzling array of Cantonese dishes which include the world’s favorite dim sum and roasted dishes.Dim Sum, a dining culture in Hong Kong that showcases Hong Kong’s culinary craftsmanship, will be exquisitely presented in Pearl Delights. The not-to-be-missed items include Steamed Scallop & Shrimp Dumplings, Pork Meat Dumplings with Crab & Fish Roe, and Deep Fried Crispy Egg Custard Buns. The char siu prepared by Pearl Delights is 1 inch thick that helps to reserve the juiciness of the meat. It is exceptionally tender and succulent under chef’s precise timing on roasting. The pork is bathed in a generous serving of honey sauce which gives the pork a glittering appearance when served. A true melt-in-the-tongue indulgence. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit A3 , Sha Tin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3489, 'en_US', 'Shanghai Lu Yang Cun Restaurant', 'Shanghai Lu Yang Cun Restaurant is very popular for Shanghai style cuisine in Hong Kong.', 'Slow, Braised Pork Belly in Don, PoStyle, Jade Qin Steamed Dumpling, Dry braised prawn with Sichuan sauce', '', 'Shanghai Lu Yang Cun Restaurant is located on the Causeway Bay’s World Trade Shopping Centre, up on the 11th floor, is a famous spot for tourists from different parts of the world. The restaurant has taken on a modern look and is very popular for Shanghai style cuisine in Hong Kong. The menu is designed concisely into sections with pictures of some of the quite popular dishes for the layman. You can tell a Shanghai restaurant is good or not by its Xiao Long Bao. This place is a definitely a must go for Shanghainese food, as the dishes are authentic and tastes so good. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D4, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3490, 'en_US', 'SUSHI SEI', 'Selected materials, \nfresh and high quality ingredients, SUSHI SEI provide customers with delicious sushi and sashimi.', 'Sashimi, Sushi', '', 'SUSHI SEI Japanese restaurant, located in Central international financial center. Selected materials, fresh and high quality ingredients, SUSHI SEI provide customers with delicious sushi and sashimi. The restaurant is decorated in simplified, especially significant Japanese style atmosphere. Japanese food lovers can enjoy the dining experience just like in japan. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A2, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3491, 'en_US', 'Naha', 'NAHA is an authentic Okinawan restaurant located in Taikoo Shing.', 'Sauteed Okinawan Bitter Gourd with Pork, Homemade Peanut Flavored Bean Curd', '', 'NAHA is an authentic Okinawan restaurant located in Taikoo Shing. Serving healthy, vibrant island cuisine - the décor, to the recipes, to the Executive chef - all can trace their roots back to Okinawa. Genuine Okinawan gourmet food presented in a homey and warm atmosphere allows diners to experience the essence of this unique cuisine.Epicurean is constantly exploring and reviewing the addition through acquisition and/or development of several new concepts, as well as potential opportunities in other key Asian cities as well. NAHA sparkles in its own way to attract its band of loyal customers. Apart from the well-trained and experienced personnel, we use the freshest ingredients and maintain the highest standards of hygiene in cooking. To entertain our customers with innovative menus and special promotions is one of the approaches we adopted to exceed their expectations. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit D1, Tai Koo MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3492, 'en_US', 'Greyhound Cafe (Mong Kok Branch)', 'Greyhound Café is the fashion café offering the food concept with a twist in a casual dining experience.', 'Greyhound’s Famous Fried Chicken Wings, Salmon Carpaccio in Spicy Hot Sauce, Spaghetti with Thai Anchovy', '', 'Greyhound Café is the first fashion café in Bangkok offering the food concept with a twist in a casual dining experience. As the first store outside Bangkok, Greyhound Café is brought to Hong Kong by Gaia Group. By offering trendy and creative mix of menus, service and ambience at the competitive price in the same segment, Hong Kong’s Greyhound Café will not forget its roots and diners can expect a vast menu of simple food with a twist with Greyhound Cafe’s personal touch of service and atmosphere. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit C, Mong Kok East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
