(3523, 'en_US', 'Limehouse', 'Limehouse gives customers a homey touch in true British style.', 'Fish and Chips, Apple crumble', '', 'Limehouse, a petite shophouse tucked away in one of the more tranquil parts of Wan Chai. You’ll be able to find all the British menu standards here, like fish and chips as well as bangers and mash. A few items on the menu are especially addictive, like the apple crumble and shepherd’s pie. With its relaxing ambience, Limehouse gives customers a homey touch in true British style. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B2, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3524, 'en_US', 'Jashan Indian Cuisine', 'Jashan\'s highlight is  fusing India\'s finest traditional tastes into a contemporary celebration.', 'Grilled Lime Coconut Chicken, Goan fish curry', '', 'Jashan\'s highlight is fusing India\'s finest traditional tastes into a contemporary celebration.\nThe signature dishes include the Bombay Tawa Chicken, a mouthwatering, Mumbai style roasted chicken, marinated with sweet paprika, tumeric and sea salt served with chilled cucumber in yoghurt dip. Chef Asif ensures us that the authentic recipe is there. A fresh cream is added to give that richness, velvety texture of the dish. Other innovations include the Patte Ki Pomfret, the Mirchi Kebab, Aloo Tikki Chana Chat, to name a few. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit C, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3525, 'en_US', 'Locofama', 'Locofama, is out to prove that healthy meals don\'t have to be bland or boring – or strictly vegetarian for that matter.', 'Seared Octopus & Baby Spinach Salad, Cauliflower Risotto, Scottish Organic Miso Salmon', '', 'Locofama’s unpretentious menu of fresh pressed juices, delicious bites, hearty salads, and comfort food roll-ups, designed by Asian American chef and nutritionist Justin Chan, is out to prove that healthy meals don\'t have to be bland or boring – or strictly vegetarian for that matter.\nVisitors can also enjoy Locofama Grocery Store, where one finds a selection of organic everyday necessities, including extra virgin olive oil, baby products, and healthy snacks. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit B1, HKU MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3526, 'en_US', 'agnès b. LE PAIN GRILLÉ (Festival Walk Branch)', 'Idea of operating LE PAIN GRILLÉ is to enable everyone to share Agnès’ taste of French food.', 'All day breakfast, Mussels simmered with white wine, shallot & cream, Scallop Seafood pasta', '', 'Agnès b considers dining culture as an important part of one’s lifestyle. Idea of operating LE PAIN GRILLÉ is to enable everyone to share Agnès’ taste of French food. Our cozy deli leads you to a voyage discovering the authenticity of French all day dining cuisine. You can enjoy French food and drinks amidst French ambience and atmosphere without the need of taking a plane abroad!! By introducing this “very French” eating style, Agnès wants to relax Hong Kong people’s hectic life and enrich their lifestyles. \nMeaning “toasted bread” in French, the name “LE PAIN GRILLÉ” is named by the designer Agnès herself. “Toasted bread” is an essential in French daily diet, so to Agnès, “LE PAIN GRILLÉ” not only means a piece of bread but also French eatery. Integrating the concepts of French café, bistro and cake shop, LE PAIN GRILLÉ serves the most signature French gourmet in just a single stop (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon Tong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
