(3529, 'en_US', 'Gold By Harlan Goldstein', 'Harlan Goldstein’s approach of respecting the ingredients ensures natural flavours are enhanced through his favorite cooking techniques such as slow cooking and smoking.', '12 OZ prime beef rib eye, Lobster spaghetti, Hokkaido sea scallop carpaccio', '', 'Located in Hong Kong’s most dynamic entertainment and dining area, Gold by Harlan Goldstein is Harlan G’s first “Harlan Goldstein” branded restaurant. Opened in November 2010, Gold has become a “must-go” dining experience for its sophisticated décor and diverse contemporary European menu with a few touches of Harlan’s Lower East Side New York roots. \nHarlan Goldstein’s approach of respecting the ingredients ensures natural flavours are enhanced through his favorite cooking techniques such as slow cooking and smoking. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3530, 'en_US', 'Penthouse by Harlan Goldstein', 'Penthouse showcases an exciting selection of new dishes and techniques, including centuries old slow-cooking and fresh handcrafted pastas.', 'Spanish farm, raised bluefin tuna tartare, Spanish Duroc Pork Ribs Bomba Rice, Hokkaido King Crab Ravioli, Tomato Basil Sugo 368', '', 'Michelin-star chef, Harlan Goldstein has opened his eagerly awaited fourth restaurant - Penthouse, located at Soundwill Plaza II Midtown in Causeway Bay. Penthouse showcases an exciting selection of new dishes and techniques, including centuries old slow-cooking and fresh handcrafted pastas. Penthouse boasts spectacular views and a relaxed ambience inspired by a chic and rustic New York style penthouse, showcasing a great mix of my favourite and new recipes and techniques, such as slow-cooking and handcrafted pastas. It will be a place where you will want to come back again and again. From the stylish urban-rustic interior design to its jaw-dropping panoramic harbour views. From its extensive menu of contemporary Western cuisine to its solid wine and cocktail menu - it is all impressive. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit B, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3531, 'en_US', 'Steak Frites by The Butchers Club', 'The Black Angus brings you the best dining experience', '40 day dry, aged rib eye & duck fat fries', '', 'The concept came through The Butchers Club’s desire to practise nose-to-tail butchery. After the primary cuts of beef have been used for the restaurant’s signature dry-aged steaks, gorgeous secondary cuts of rump, chuck and brisket are first dry-aged and then marinated in The Butchers Club’s secret seasoning mix before being ground in a huge old-fashioned grinder right in front of the customer.\nThe Black Angus cattle are fed on a diet of organic hormone-free and antibiotic-free pasture, which is supplemented by organic grain, creating a flavour that is totally unique! (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '9-min walk from Exit A2, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3532, 'en_US', 'The Butchers Club Deli', 'The Butchers Club Deli, specialising in handcrafted charcuterie, using only natural and organic ingredients.', 'Dry Aged Australia Stockyard Rib, eye Steak, Butchers Club Dry Aged Beef Burger, Butcher Platter', '', 'The Butchers Club Deli offers the same Butchers Club dining experience it has become famous for, plus more. By day, it’s a New York-style deli, specialising in handcrafted charcuterie, made using only natural and organic ingredients. By night, the space becomes an extension of the butchery and private dining room of The Butchers Club in Tin Wan. The space can also cater to a wide range of events at any time of the day.\nThe Butchers Club Deli is part of a unique concept in the heart of Aberdeen called ED1TUS. This exciting new concept is Asia’s only men’s fashion and lifestyle showroom, which showcases the best modern luxury brands from Europe and the US in a stunning multi-brand showroom.\nThe space can be tailored to suit all kinds of events, from small 14 person private dinners, to seated dinners for 120 people or standing cocktail events for up to 300 people, whether for breakfast, lunch or dinner. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Victory Factory Building bus stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3533, 'en_US', 'Lam\'s Imperial Cuisine', 'Lam\'s cooking style aims at exposing and enhancing the natural beauty of fresh ingredients with minimal oil and spices.', 'Traditional char, grilled fresh conch a la Chiu Chow, Lam\'s very own abalone/lobster terrine, Crispy tofu a la Chiu Chow', '', 'Lam\'s Imperial Cuisine, chiuchow cuisine restaurant.\nLam\'s chefs continue the gastronomic tradition, they also take their family cooking to another dimension. For the Lams, the magical alchemy of Chiu Chow cuisine is a cross-generation journey of the discovery, creation, experiment and refinement of hundreds of mouth-watering delicacies.\nLam\'s chefs source fresh and prime quality ingredients from local markets every day with rare imports directly from Shantou. Lam\'s passion for food motivates them to continuously create innovative dishes as well as unique, homemade dipping sauces to compliment or enhance the taste of the food. Lam\'s kitchen uses ther signature Superlative Broth in cooking that spares the use of MSG. Lam\'s cooking style aims at exposing and enhancing the natural beauty of fresh ingredients with minimal oil and spices. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Wong Nai Chung Road trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3534, 'en_US', 'Lai Bun Fu', 'Master Chef Chung Kin Leung is one of the few Hong Kong chefs who has had the privilege of preparing a gourmet feast for U.S. President George Bush', 'Barbecued Iberico Pork Glazed with Honey, Bird’s Nest with Minced Chicken Soup, Poached Mandarin Fish in Hot Chili Oil', '', 'Lai Bun Fu is a contemporary and luxurious Chinese restaurant; its theme combines old Hong Kong and modern furnishings, with a splash of British Colonial influence, situated in the heart of Central, Hong Kong. Lai Bun Fu stand as the leading culinary ambassador for Hong Kong. They aim at presenting the best cuisine from Hong Kong and the region using only the finest ingredients and unsurpassed culinary skills. At Lai Bun Fu, you will find inspired classic Chinese dishes \'re-visited\' using modern techniques and stylish presentation. The venue can accomodate 52 guests and our VIP dining room is perfect for confidential meetings, corporate entertainment or celebrations with friends and family which can accomodate up to 12 guests. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3535, 'en_US', 'Mark One', 'Mark One quality of ingredients used in class, the restaurant\'s dishes satisfactory performance.', 'Seared Sea cod with Cream Sauce, Black Truffle Scallop French Mud Crab risotto', '', 'Top quality ingredients is used in Mark One , such as fresh oysters, cod, steak, foie gras, Spanish ham, etc., The service is very thoughtful. Mark One serves Italian and French cuisine with a little bit of oriental color. Overall, the restaurant\'s dishes and performance are very good. Sometimes this is the need to make a meal with spiritual ideas, only to see the restaurant is popular and lively. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A, Fortress Hill MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3536, 'en_US', 'The French Table', 'The French Table uses the finest ingredients and pay attention on details, creates innovative and seasonal dishes those are light and refreshing yet rich in taste and flavour.', 'Lobster Risotto, Pressed Duck Breast in Traditional French Style, Roasted Rack of Lamb with Mustard Sauce', '', 'The French Table offers fine French dining with graceful music and comfortable ambience. It is a glamorous restaurant that is perfectly for lover’s dating or friend’s gathering.  Michael, the Executive Chef, uses the finest ingredients and pay attention on details. He creates innovative and seasonal dishes those are light and refreshing yet rich in taste and flavour.  Discreet, well-informed staff fluently recommends dishes without pretention that encourages diners to ask questions and develop their palate on every return. A high quality of service is presented.  An enjoyable experience is always hoped to be provided to every diners. We are looking forward to see you in the French Table! (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A4, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3537, 'en_US', 'Chui Hang Hin Seafood Hot Pot', 'Chui Hang Hin Seafood Hot Pot’s best beef melts in your mouth, fresh meat, worth a try.', 'Penaeus shrimp sashimi, Geoduck sashimi, Hand, cut bovine jugular', '', 'Chui Hang Hin Seafood Hot Pot is located in Tsim Sha Tsui, this restaurant is famous for its hot pot. The restaurant\'s decor to go minimalist style, spacious seating setting so that customers get comfortable feels when they are dining. Chui Hang Hin Seafood Hot Pot’s best beef melts in your mouth, fresh meat, worth a try. The restaurant uses quality materials are high here that eating fried fish that make customers eat enjoyably. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit N2, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3538, 'en_US', 'Ore-no Kappou by Ginza Okamoto', 'Excellent value for Japanese-starred quality food and wine.', 'Grilled Beef Tenderloin Foie gras with Truffle sauce, Mackerel sushi', '', 'Ore-no Kappou by Ginza Okamoto’s first overseas branch, now is setting its outpost in Hong Kong. with\" Ore-no Kappou cooking \"(Ore-no Kappou by Ginza Okamoto) for the first shot, heritage,\" Public-friendly Michelin \"concept, from Japan by Michelin chef and professional products sommelier team to create a new concept of stylish restaurant and bar, offering excellent value for Japanese-starred quality food and wine. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from  Exit D2, Central MTR  Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3539, 'en_US', 'Taku', 'Featuring an array of classic yet outspoken dishes that incorporate modern ingredients.', 'the Snapper Ceviche with a ponzu radish sauce, the Stacked Angus beef rib eye with roasted garlic & teriyaki sauce, Scallop Carpaccio', '', 'Soho’s Japanese dining destination, Taku is known for its traditional shop house exterior. However upon entry you will be pleasantly surprised by the eclectic use of bright accent colours & dark wood features or its interior echoing the eclectic charm of old vs. new & heritage vs. cool. Taku’s Executive Chef’s menu features an array of classic yet outspoken dishes that honour Japanese traditions but incorporate modern ingredients, preparation methods and vibrant garnishes of micro greens and edible flowers. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '9-min walk from Exit A2, Sheung Wan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3540, 'en_US', 'Zenpachi Japanese Cusine & Shabu-Shabu', 'Zenpachi is well known for its excellent quality \'Wagyu\' beef Shabu Shabu and authentic Japanese cuisine including Sushi,Sashimi, and Tempura.', 'A5 wagyu beef hot pot, Hokkaido crab hot pot', '', 'Zenpachi, high level Japanese hot pot restaurants.  Japanese-style decor with tranquil setting, Zenpachi give you a noble style. With a comfort setting and vip rooms popular to business executives, Zenpachi is well known for its excellent quality \'Wagyu\' beef Shabu Shabu and authentic Japanese cuisine including Sushi,Sashimi, and Tempura. Customers can enjoy the highest quality Japanese Wagyu beef. Zenpachi\'s  ingredients all imported from Japan, that customers can feel the authentic Japanese flavor. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit F, Austin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3541, 'en_US', 'Yukimura Japanese Cuisine', 'Omakase featured. Ingredients are delivered within 24 hours of delivery of chilled seafood in Hong Kong.', 'Omakase, Sanma sashimi, Inaniwa udon with Angus beef', '', 'Yukimura Japanese Cuisine is most famous for its Omakase. The restaurant is located in Causeway Bay, the price points of $ 1,000 and $ 1,200 ,two prices. Including appetizers, sashimi, sushi, and food, soup and dessert total of 10 variety of dishes. Ingredients are delivered within 24 hours of delivery of chilled seafood in Hong Kong, which include from the Japanese island of Hokkaido and tokyo Tsukiji fish market, seasonal seafood. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3542, 'en_US', 'Le Pinacle', 'Le Pinacle decoration is Elegant, with the fashion design of the furniture, which show the noble atmosphere.', 'Crab Shell, Crab Meat, Baked, Steamed prawn dumplings, Gravy Angus cubes', '', 'Le Pinacle is located in Sai Wan, they manage the restaurant as a VIP club, the decoration is Elegant, with the fashion design of the furniture, which show the noble atmosphere. Also the wall of the kitchen is made by glasses which shows the works of the chiefs to the guests. The main dishes are abalones, cubilose and sea foods. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Western Street trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3543, 'en_US', 'Tin Heung Lau', 'Tin Heung Lau not only provides traditional Hangzhou food, but also imported different ingredients from all around the world.', 'Chinese Mitten Crab, Dongpo Pork, Superior Shark\'s Fin with Crab Roe soup', '', 'Hangzhou food is one of the famous types of food in China, Tin Heung Lau not only provided the traditional Hangzhou food, but also imported different ingredients from all around the world. Tin Heung Lau focus on the quality of the food and the comfortable environment. The most famous main dishes is stir-fried pork. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '8-min walk from Exit D, Jordan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
