(3934, 'en_US', 'Viva Ana Tapas and Wine Bar', 'Located in central Wan Chai, Viva Ana is a new contemporary Tapas Bar.', '36 Months Iberico Ham, Garlic Prawn, Traditional Spanish Cold Tomato and Cucumber Soup', '', 'Located in central Wan Chai, Viva Ana is a new contemporary Tapas Bar. The stunning Spanish interior design is vividly presented all over Viva Ana. We have more than 30 tapas, traditional Spanish wine, sherry, sangria, featured here. Open kitchen and little Spanish store make Viva Ana a relaxing dining place in this hustling and bustling city. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '6-min walk from Exit B2, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
