(3950, 'en_US', 'Tinello', 'This restaurant features our chef’s own unique interpretation of classic Italian and Mediterranean dishes.', 'Pork Parmesan, Oven baked lamb shanks, Antipasto', '', 'This restaurant features our chef’s own unique interpretation of classic Italian and Mediterranean dishes. This includes steaks, pastas, pizzas and healthy salads. We also have a wide selection of New and Old World wines and beers. Every month we have a special Wine of the Month promotion where you can sample a carefully selected wine for a bargain price. This is an ideal location for a business lunch or just somewhere to relax with friends and family. We serve food all day every day, so pop in any time and we will give you and your guests a meal and experience to remember! (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A1, Wan Chai MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3951, 'en_US', 'Le Souk', 'Chill out and take in the wonderful magical ambience of Le Souk.', 'Seabass tagine, Moroccan seafood paella, Roasted lamb shank, Lamb Mergez and veggies served with cous cous', '', 'Le Souk, specializing in Middle Eastern cuisine, this vibrant and colourfully designed restaurant is ideal for after work drinks as well as an exciting dinner party with friends. Seconds away from the SoHo escalator this is the hottest new restaurant in town, right in the heart of the action. Chill out and take in the wonderful magical ambience of Le Souk. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '7-min walk from Exit C, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3952, 'en_US', 'Arashiyama Japanese Restaurant', 'From Japan to Hong Kong, a variety of seasonal fresh fish and fresh ingredients import daily by air transportation, create all kinds of sashimi, sushi and dishes.', 'Omakase, Grilled Alaskan long crab legs', '', 'Arashiyama Japanese Restaurant located in Tsim Sha Tsui, flourishing with quiet. From Japan to Hong Kong, a variety of seasonal fresh fish and fresh ingredients import daily by air transportation, create all kinds of sashimi, sushi and dishes. Arashiyama also better at a variety of skewers, including: roast eel, grilled fresh abalone, grilled razor, grilled Alaskan long crab legs, grilled black-pork with asparagus rolls. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit N3, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3953, 'en_US', 'Rosticceria Italiana Monteverdi', 'Our complimentary menu, created with our Chef Andrea.', 'Fish Fillet Mint scented and Roasted Bell Peppers, Calf Cheeks Braised in red wine with Red Cabbage and other vegetables, Oven baked pasta with Italian Sausage', '', 'Same Location as the Trattoria, the venue has a more casual set-up, including a nicely decorated open air terrace. Our complimentary menu, created with our Chef Andrea. Here you can buy our home made pasta to cook at home, our sauces, home made Grandmother\'s desserts, cold cuts, cheeses, organic extra vergin olive oil, balsamic vinegar and much more. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Eastern Street trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
