(3962, 'en_US', 'Hawker 18', 'Hawker 18 is inspired by the hawker centres where Singaporeans go for casual, affordable and, most of all, delicious meals.', 'Sambal honey chicken wings, Nonya, style BBQ whole squid, Seafood Laska Lemak', '', 'Hawker 18 is inspired by the hawker centres where Singaporeans go for casual, affordable and, most of all, delicious meals. We believe some of the best cuisine in the world is served up everyday amongst the hustle and bustle of hawker centre life - no frills, no fuss, just great food. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit E, Kwai Fong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3963, 'en_US', 'Metropolitain', 'Friendly service and details make Metropolitain a relaxed and enjoyable place to enjoy a hearty taste of France.', 'Pork Tenderloin w/ Green Peas and Bacon, Whole, GrainMustard Sauce, Sea Bass w/ Aioli Sauce and Steamed Vegetables, Crème Brulée', '', 'Metropolitain serves french cuisine to our guest. Friendly service and details make Metropolitain a relaxed and enjoyable place to enjoy a hearty taste of France. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Western Street trams station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3964, 'en_US', 'Classified (Exchange Square Branch)', 'To revive street-level interaction and neighbourhood sociability.', 'Artisan Cheese Platter, Classified beef burger, Classified breakfast', '', 'When Classified launched in 2006, its founders wanted to create a new dining concept in Hong Kong. Rather than open Classified in a character-free mall, the intention was to revive street-level interaction and neighbourhood sociability. The authentic al fresco style, contemporary design and wide selection of boutique wines, gourmet coffees, specialty cheeses and handmade breads.Classified re-invented the way locals eat out, bringing casual outdoor dining to the streets. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit D2, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3973, 'en_US', 'China House (Kowloon Branch)', 'A unique Chinese Restaurant serves modern Chinese food, decorated as in the roaring 50s & 60s.', 'Roast Whole Peking Duck, Steamed Pork Dumplings Shanghai Style, Braised Duck with Eight Treasures', '', 'A unique Chinese Restaurant serving modern Chinese food decorated as in the roaring 50s & 60s. You could reminiscent the wonderful good old times once again at China House. After you have tried the delicious food you will feel right at home. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit A, Mei Foo MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
