(3975, 'en_US', 'CIAK - In The Kitchen', 'The decoration is simple yet contemporary and the atmosphere is bustling and busy. The food focuses on the tastes of an Italian home and the produce is available to take away.', 'Homemade sausage, Apple Tart, Lemon Tart', '', 'CIAK - In The Kitchen is proud to offer honest and comforting cuisine using top-quality ingredients in a homely environment, as described by the Michelin guide: “The decoration is simple yet contemporary and the atmosphere is bustling and busy. The food focuses on the tastes of an Italian home and the produce is available to take away.” (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit G, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(3976, 'en_US', 'Thai Orchids Café & Bar', 'Associate authentic Thai food with friendly service in a comfortable setting, Thai Orchids is a must-go restaurant for Thai food lovers.', 'Thai prawn salad with lemon grass and chili, Stuffed green mussels in thick curry paste with Thai basil, Curry with bread loaf', '', 'Thai Orchids are set up and located in MegaBox. With an established reputation for its warm atmosphere, friendly service and quality Thai cuisine, Thai Orchids is one of the most popular restaurants chains in Hong Kong specializing in authentic Thai cuisine. Associate authentic Thai food with friendly service in a comfortable setting, Thai Orchids is a must-go restaurant for Thai food lovers. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Wang Tung Street Kowloon Bay stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
