(3978, 'en_US', 'Edo Japanese Restaurant', 'Edo Japanese Restaurant is now opened at J Plus with a new image and you will find the finest Japanese cuisine here with our Master Japanese Chef.', 'Crab Kamameshi, Miyazaki cattle sashimi, sea urchin stuffed with scallop tempura', '', 'Edo Japanese Restaurant which established in 1992 was a top premium Japanese restaurant with the longest history in Macau. There are 7 Edo Japanese Restaurants located in various famous landmarks and luxury hotels in Macau. They include Venetian, Sands Cotai Central, One Central, and International Finance Place in Guangzhou. All the ingredients are imported from Japan directly. Edo Japanese Restaurant is now opened at J Plus 1 floor with a new image and you will find the finest Japanese cuisine here with our Master Japanese Chef. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit F1, Causeway Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
