(4003, 'en_US', 'Festive China', 'Festive China offers a new range of Beijing Cuisine with a touch of imperial dining and a taste of Mongolian flavor, the range of modified Huaiyang cuisine also gives a fresh taste to the menu.', 'Sauteed fresh water shrimps, Stewed spare ribs in sweet and sour sauce', '', 'Festive China, New Interpretation of Huaiyang and Beijing Cuisine. Festive China offers a new range of Beijing Cuisine with a touch of imperial dining and a taste of Mongolian flavor, the range of modified Huaiyang cuisine also gives a fresh taste to the menu. Located at Festival Walk, Festive China offers a stylish and cozy environment for you to kick back and unwind after shopping. From contemporary furnishing like modern Chinese writing brush decorations and western painting to interior ambiance, Festive China offers a brand new dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit C2, Kowloon Tong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4004, 'en_US', 'Jasmine Place', 'All food is cooked in a healthy and refreshing way with no MSG added to present the most original flavours of food in Jasmine Place', 'Boiled sharks fin bone soup with conpoy and bamboo pith, Prawn on egg white custard with \"tai diao\" rice liquor', '', 'Jasmine Place is a restaurant in simple style with class. Birds and flowers hand paintings in Chinese style on the wall receive diners like a private club for the enjoyment of wonderful dishes in a relaxing way. Integrated with traditional and new cooking styles, all food is cooked in a healthy and refreshing way with no MSG added so to present the most original flavours of food. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4005, 'en_US', 'Sichuan Garden', 'Sichuan Garden offers signature dishes from two of China’s major provincial cuisines – spicy Sichuan and delicate Huaiyang.', 'Sliced beef w/ hot chilli', '', 'Sichuan Garden offers signature dishes from two of China’s major provincial cuisines – spicy Sichuan and delicate Huaiyang – in the majestic elegance of a Chinese manor. An overall auburn tone has been adopted in the decor, complemented by timber veneers and discreet chandeliers, projecting a refined and sophisticated air. A taste of Huiyang and Sichuan at a classical Chinese residence offers a dining experience that is elegant, sophisticated and sure to satisfy. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit A3 , Sha Tin MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4006, 'en_US', 'Hunan Garden', 'Hunan Garden, boasting one of the eight major provincial cuisines of China – Hunan Cuisine, has added creative touches to classic Hunan dishes.', 'Steamed fish with Savory Crispy Beans, Smoked Duck', '', 'Hunan Garden, boasting one of the eight major provincial cuisines of China – Hunan Cuisine, has added creative touches to classic Hunan dishes. While hot, spicy and sour are the signature flavours, spiciness is by no means the sole pursuit for Hunan Cuisine. Exhibiting artistry and creativity in the culinary arts, our chef at Hunan Garden utilizes a plethora of techniques which, combined with fresh, seasonal ingredients, take Hunan cuisine to a whole new level. The interior décor of Hunan Garden recreates the breath-taking mountains and waters of Dongting Lake, incorporating in the décor visual concepts inspired by the eight scenic sights of Dongting Lake. Customers may find themselves transported to the picturesque lakeside, taking in the awe-inspiring landscape while savouring the taste of authentic Hunan dishes – a feast for both the eyes and taste buds. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '10-min walk from Exit D1, Tai Koo MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4007, 'en_US', 'House of Beijing (Tsuen Wan Branch)', 'Dining at the elegant House of Beijing is like enjoying home style flavours in a Beijing alley.', 'Barbecued Peking Duck, Braised Shark\'s Fin, Fish, maw, Mushroom & Vegetable, Sauteeed prawns with broad bean and chilli', '', 'House of Beijing offers various Peking style home dishes. Chefs adopt innovative food produces and special cooking techniques to make new appetizers, main courses and noodles in a home dish style. Dining at the elegant House of Beijing is like enjoying home style flavours in a Beijing alley. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '9-min walk from Exit E2, Tsuen Wan West MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4008, 'en_US', 'House of Beijing (Tai Po Branch)', 'Dining at the elegant House of Beijing is like enjoying home style flavours in a Beijing alley.', 'Barbecued Peking Duck, Braised Shark\'s Fin, Fish, maw, Mushroom & Vegetable, Sauteeed prawns with broad bean and chilli', '', 'House of Beijing offers various Peking style home dishes. Chefs adopt innovative food produces and special cooking techniques to make new appetizers, main courses and noodles in a home dish style. Dining at the elegant House of Beijing is like enjoying home style flavours in a Beijing alley. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit A1, Tai Po Market MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4009, 'en_US', 'China Fragrance', 'China Fragrance offers signature dishes combined with the essence of Beijing cuisine, and unique cooking style to give you the most memorable dining experience.', 'Deep, fried Chicken Dices with Hot Chilli, Steamed Fresh Water Fish in Chilli Sacue, Stewed Chicken Wrapped in Lotus Leaves', '', 'China Fragrance offers signature dishes combined with the essence of Beijing cuisine, and unique cooking style to give you the most memorable dining experience. In addition, the décor featuring traditional red lantern along the hallway and elegant Chinese banquet hall, brings you back to the heritage of China in a modern setting, get of taste of the unique sensual experience at China Fragrance now opened in a brand new image. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D, Kwai Fong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4010, 'en_US', 'Oriental Lily', 'Oriental Lily symbolizes the gathering of over 100 types of Peking and Huai Yang dishes together, makes it a wonderful restaurant to experience different kinds of authentic cuisine with a joyous heart.', 'Barbecued Peking Duck, Fried Crispy Conpoy with Prawns & Chill', '', 'Oriental Lily symbolizes the gathering of over 100 types of Peking and Huai Yang dishes together, makes it a wonderful restaurant to experience different kinds of authentic cuisine with a joyous heart. Oriental Lily integrates traditional Peking and Huai Yang cuisines, injecting new elements in food combination and presentation. New stylish home style seafood dishes even make the menu a magic book of writing of the finest cuisines. With the Chinese and Western styles that emphasize flexibility in decoration and professional services, Oriental Lily provides a new dimension of dining experience. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Wang Tung Street Kowloon Bay stop', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4011, 'en_US', 'Shanghai Jade', 'Shanghai Jade presents you with Shanghai cuisine in all its authentic and colourful diversity.', 'Braised lion head minced pork balls with vegetables, Braised superior shark\'s fin with premium sauce, Pan, fried perch fillet with spring onion', '', 'Shanghai Jade, taste the new definition of elegance. From delicate Shanghai furnishing and tableware to interior ambiance, Shanghai Jade offers a dining experience evocative of the elegant colours of Shanghai. True to its name, Shanghai Jade serves dishes and dim sum rivaling the quality of premium jade. With no addition of MSG, honed to perfection with vitamin E rich, cholesterol-free rice bran oil, and prepared with seasonal ingredients and seasoned culinary artistry, we present you with Shanghai cuisine in all its authentic and colourful diversity. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '3-min walk from Exit A, Central MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4012, 'en_US', 'Xi Yue', 'Xi Yue promises you a refreshing taste of scent summer as you enjoy its delicately crafted dishes.', 'Flaming veal shank with chestnuts and red dates in whisky tomato sauce, Steamed lobster in \"Hua Diao\" rice liquor, Tomato puree thicken soup with bird\'s nest', '', 'Enjoy authentic Chinese in the blissful ambience of Xi Yue. The name ‘Xi Yue’, meaning Joy, was inspired by the connotation of August - a month for Joyful Celebration, in Chinese culture. Xi Yue offers a new Chinese dining experience that boasts natural flavors with a particular lightness and freshness of taste, by serving delicate and creatively crafted dishes, healthy greens and tofu, a large selection of tea, special drinks and home-made desserts. Xi Yue promises you a refreshing taste of scent summer as you enjoy its delicately crafted dishes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit A, Quarry Bay MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4013, 'en_US', 'Jasmine Garden', 'Jasmine Garden inherits its acclaimed health elements, taking you to a blooming garden of tastes.', 'Crispy barbecued suckling piglet, Stir, fried clams with chives, preserved meat served with pancakes', '', 'A new addition to jade concepts, Jasmine Garden inherits also its acclaimed health elements. Carefully chosen seasonal ingredients are prepared by master chefs using vitamin-E rich, cholesterol-free rice bran oil, and no MSG is added in the process. The seasoned arts of the Cantonese cuisine is all that is needed to bring out the authentic flavors in the freshest ingredients, taking you to a blooming garden of tastes. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit C2, Mong Kok MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4014, 'en_US', 'Cloudland Chinese Cuisine', 'Sticking with the freshest ingredients without any additives, Cloudland advocates healthy natural food.', 'Baked Crab in beggar\'s style, Pan, fried prawn cake with scallops with salty egg yolk, Deep, fried green crabs with garlic and chili', '', 'Cloudland is a very stylish way of arranging dishes with the owner\'s questing mind for the innovative flavor, while preserving the tradition of Cantonese cuisine. Restaurant stick with the freshest ingredients without any additives, advocates a healthy natural food culture. The restaurant is wide, well lit, decorated with white tone, customer will feel elegant in Cloudland. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '2-min walk from Exit N3, Tsim Sha Tsui East MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4015, 'en_US', 'Hei Sei Ni Jyu Ni Japanese Restaurant', 'Enter the store you can feel a deep sense of Japanese izakaya style.', 'Japan fried oyster, Ox tongue skewer', '', 'Hei Sei Ni Jyu Ni Japanese Restaurant located in Hillwood Road, is a dense diet street with many other popular restaurants. Enter the store you can feel a deep sense of Japanese izakaya style. Enjoy the color, flavor and taste of Japanese cuisine. There are deep-fried food, snacks, sushi, sashimi, burning things, and food, rolls and rice noodles, also have a large selection of drinks, including a large number of carbonated drinks, beer, ice tea, peach tea, lemon tea and oolong tea, frozen drinks like if Well, there is also provided hot green tea. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '4-min walk from Exit D, Jordan MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4016, 'en_US', 'Glasshouse', 'Glasshouse serves an array of old times favorites with fresh ingredients, cooked using an Asian cooking technique with a western twist.', 'Grilled foie gras with tamarind and orange jam, Pad Thai black ink noodles with barbeque pork, tofu, and free range hen egg and soy bean sprouts, Lime tempura smelt fish with spicy kimchi mayonnaise', '', 'Glasshouse, located on IFC rooftop with a stunning Harbor View, a terrace, the design of the Glasshouse takes its inspiration from potting sheds in old country houses; a room filled with wheel barrows, rakes, terracotta pots. \nGlasshouse serves an array of old times favorites with fresh ingredients, cooked using an Asian cooking technique with a western twist.\nAn array of old times favorites prepared with fresh herbs, wholewheat pasta, wild fish, natural grown meats and organic fruit and vegetables. Asian cooking technique with a Western twist. A new age rendition of culinary traditions past, brought forward and influenced by the current spices, and essences that make up local, regional and international dining. The à la carte menu is composed of finger foods, salads and other light mains constructed for a premium, colorful and relaxed dining experience for sharing amongst friends and family. All offerings remain true to the philosophy of incorporating local, regional and international modern flavor palates and ingredients. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '1-min walk from Exit E2, Hong Kong MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
(4017, 'en_US', 'Munch', 'Munch is famous for its high quality dishes made with lots of Organic and All Natural ingredients.', 'Serrano Ham and Melon, Sea Scallop and Monkfish with Sea Urchin Crème Brulee, Poached Halibut with Capsicum Salsa and Basil Tomato Coulis', '', 'Munch Restaurant\'s award-winning chefs will continue to develop innovative Fusion Asian- and Western-style dishes for our customers. Munch is famous for its high quality dishes made with lots of organic and all natural ingredients. In addition to providing delicious food, we all care about your health and that is why we use ingredients that are rich in nutritious organic grains such as millet and buckwheat. Our customers love Munch\'s home-made desserts and our hot request is the Tofu Cheese Cake which is low in cholesterol and rich in nutritious value. Munch Restaurant can serve up to 80 guests . You can hold various parties here ranging from informal gatherings to formal business meetings and anniversary celebrations. (Contents and images are rightfully owned by undefined, if there is any concern, please contact us.)', '5-min walk from Exit B1, Tsim Sha Tsui MTR Station', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
